(209, 'Vit Nam c thm hng hng khng gi r', 'viet-nam-lai-co-them-hang-hang-khong-gia-re', '', '"Tn binh" VietJetAir  chnh thc  ra mt sng nay 2/12, nh du s tham gia vo th trng hng khng  Vit Nam vi m hnh chi ph thp (LCC).    <img src="http://dantri4.vcmedia.vn/L6citQa4PR6kuP9vPSuL/Image/2011/11/Vietjetair2122011_644ee.jpg" border="0" alt="Viet nam co them hang hang khong gia re VietJet" title="Hng hng khng gi r VietJet" width="450" height="204" /><br />VietJetAir s khi  bay vi tn sut 4 chuyn/ngy trn trc chnh H Ni - TPHCM, sau  s  tng dn ln 14 chuyn/ngy v sm b sung cc im n mi bao gm   Nng, Hi Phng, Nha Trang,  Lt. Trong vng my nm ti, VietJetAir  tip tc hng ti m cc tuyn bay quc t ti Macau, Singapore, Trung  Quc, Nht Bn, Hn Quc v Hong Kong.\r\n<p>VietJetAir bao gm hai  c ng chnh l SOVICO Holdings v HDBank. Hng hng khng ny s dng  ton b my bay Airbus A320-200 mi, vi 180 gh bc da cao cp trn mi  my bay.</p>\r\n<p>VietJetAir  khai  trng ng lot h thng thng mi trn ton quc vi cc phng v,  cc i l, cng website bn v www.vietjetair.com v tng i bn v  19001886.</p>\r\n<p>Bn cnh knh thu h l  120 im giao dch ca HDBank, VietJetAir s m rng knh thu h, thanh  ton trn my ATM, internet banking trn h thng cc ngn hng khc.</p>\r\n<p>Vi m hnh LCC,  VietJetAir hng n mc tiu m rng th trng hng khng Vit Nam,  mang li thm mt sn phm bay gi linh hot v hp l, to c hi cho  mi ngi dn c th i my bay, k c nhng ngi c kh nng chi tr   mc bnh dn.</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p align="right">A.H</p>', '', 1, 6, 0, 38, '2012-02-02 06:23:52', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-02-02 06:23:52', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 65, '', '', 0, 37, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(207, 'Bn v gi r, VietJet ht khch t xe khch', 'ban-ve-gia-re-vietjet-hut-khach-tu-xe-khach', '', 'VietJet, hng hng khng gi r mi  hot ng ti th trng Vit Nam t thng 12/2011, c th tng gp i  s my bay ca mnh ln 6 chic vo cui nm nay khi hng d kin s ht  khch t nhng chuyn xe khch Bc Nam ko di tn 40 gi.<img src="http://dantri4.vcmedia.vn/L6citQa4PR6kuP9vPSuL/Image/2012/01/Vietjet122012_059e0.jpg" border="0" alt="Hng khng gi r VietJetAir ht khch t xe khch" title="Hng khng gi r VietJetAir" width="450" height="319" /><br />Chia s vi Bloomberg  qua in thoi, Ph Tng gim c ca VietJet ng Pritam Singh ni:  Rt nhiu ngi ngh rng i my bay t v i xe khch (xe but) th  r hn nhiu. Nhng chng ti ang tm cch tn cng vo phn khc th  trng ny,  li ko khch hng s dng hng khng gi r thay v i  xe khch.\r\n<p>Bi trn chng ng t  TPHCM i H Ni, mt chuyn bay ca VietJet ch mt khong 2 gi trong  khi i bng tu ha l 30 - 42 gi v i bng xe khch l 34 - 40 gi.</p>\r\n<p>Cn v gi v, trn  trang web ca nh ga H Ni, gi v tu ha 1 chiu t TPHCM i H Ni  l 486.000 ng/v (gh cng). Cn gi v xe khch i t TPHCM ra H Ni  r nht ca Cng ty Vinamotor cng vo khong 400.000 ng.</p>\r\n<p>Trong khi , mc gi  v trung bnh ( bao gm c thu) ca VietJet vo khong 1,03 triu  ng/chiu (49 USD), r hn khong 25% so vi gi v r nht c bn  trn trang web ca hng hng khng quc gia Vietnam Airlines.</p>\r\n<p>VietJet cng c  nh  cnh tranh vi hng hng khngVietnamAirlinestrn cc chuyn bay quc  t ngay trong qu 3/2012 khi d bo tng trng kinh t kh quan (vo  khong 6% nm nay) s thc y nhu cu i li ca ngi dn.</p>\r\n<p>ng Paul Stoll, gim  c iu hnh ca Cng ty c phn qun l khch sn quc t Celadon cho  rng, th trng hng khng gi r s rt pht trin ti Vit Nam nu  cc hng hng khng ny c  vn v tin hnh cc chin dch marketing  c hiu qu. Tuy nhin, cnh tranh s rt khc lit.</p>\r\nLi Trn', '', 1, 6, 0, 59, '2012-02-02 06:06:02', 62, '', '2012-02-02 06:18:53', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-02-02 06:06:02', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 6, '', '', 0, 740, 'robots=\nauthor=');
