(69, 'Sn bay quc t Ni Bi bc b pht', 'san-bay0noi-bai-buc-be-phot', '', '<h2 class="Lead"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Cn ma ln xy ra chiu (11/5) khin cho b pht trn sn bay Ni Bi (H Ni) bt np, cc cht thi  y phun tro v chy lnh lng ra bi  my bay, theo phn nh ca c gi VnExpress.</span> <br /><br /></h2>\r\n<p class="Normal">Mt c gi phn nh qua ng dy nng, sn bay Ni Bi lc 5h chiu chng kin cnh kinh hong. Cn ma ln xy ra trong vng 20 pht  khin b pht t ti sn bay bt np. Cc loi cht thi chy ra khin cho mi hi thi bc ln nng nc khp ni.</p>\r\n<table style="width: 1px;" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src="http://vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3b/a2/9b/49/phan.jpg" border="0" height="350" width="480" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="Image">Cc cht thi ny trn ra sn st ch my bay  ti Ni Bi, lc chiu ngy 11/5. <em>nh do c gi cung cp.</em></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p class="Normal">Mt c gi cho bit mt chic my bay cha n gi ct cnh  phi ng ca khoang sm hn thng l  trnh mi hi thi  sn bay. Chic b pht ny t  v tr cu 9 ca sn bay. Khi np b pht b bc, cc loi cht thi, gm c phn ngi  b nc ma cun tri chy ra tn v tr ca cu 7, cu 19 v cu 20.</p>\r\n<p class="Normal">Trao i vi <em>VnExpress.net</em>, n v qun l sn bay Ni Bi tha nhn c s c bt np b pht xy ra chiu nay do ma ln.</p>\r\n<table style="width: 1px;" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src="http://vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3b/a2/9b/49/phan1.jpg" border="0" height="309" width="480" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="Image">Mt gc khc  sn bay Ni Bi cng trn ngp cht thi v bc mi hi thi. <em>nh do c gi cung cp.</em></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p class="Normal">ng cho bit cn ma xy ra ch trong vng 20 pht nhng kh ln khin cho p lc nc mnh. H thng ng cng b bc, km theo np b pht cng b bt, khin cc cht thi trn ra ngoi. Cc nhn vin mi trng ang s dng my  ht cn nc v y np li.</p>\r\n<p class="Normal">V lnh o ny cho bit rt nhiu trn ma ln xy ra nhng y l ln u tin, b pht b bc. "Chng ti rt ngc nhin v iu ny, c th l h thng ng ng xung cp v  n lc cn sa cha", v lnh o ny ni.</p>\r\n<p class="Normal">y khng phi l ln u tin sn bay Ni Bi chng kin cnh cht thi b tro ra khi ma. Theo phn nh ca mt s nhn vin lm vic ti y rt nhiu ln h phi chu cnh c sn bay bc mi hi thi. "Mi ln ma n l chng ti li chu trn. Thm ch c nhng ngy nng th mi hi cng bc ra t h thng ng ng v b pht", nhn vin  y phn nh.</p>\r\n<p class="Normal">Nm 2008, nh ga sn bay Ni Bi cn xy ra cnh <span class="Normal">dt mi khi tri ma</span>.</p>', '', 1, 11, 0, 44, '2011-05-14 09:15:24', 62, '', '2011-06-04 05:23:59', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-05-14 09:15:24', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 2, 0, 6, '', '', 0, 184, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(70, 'Jetstar Pacific m li ng bay H Ni- Nha Trang', 'jetstar-pacific-mo-lai-duong-bay-ha-noi-nha-trang', '', '<h2 class="Lead"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"> cnh tranh vi "ng ln" Vietnam Airlines vo dp cao im h, hng hng khng gi r Jetstar Pacific s m li ng bay H Ni - Nha Trang t ngy 24/5 n 29/10. </span></h2>\r\n<p class="Normal">Trong giai on t ngy 24/5 n 31/5, Jetstar Pacific s khai thc vi tn sut mt chuyn kh hi mi ngy vo bui sng. T 1/6 n 29/10, hng tng tn sut ln 2 chuyn mt ngy.</p>\r\n<table style="width: 1px;" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src="http://vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3b/a2/99/5a/jetstar.jpg" alt="Jetstar Pacific m ng bay H Ni - Nha Trang vo dp h. nh: Kin Cng" border="1" height="350" width="450" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="Image">Jetstar Pacific m ng bay H Ni - Nha Trang vo dp h. nh: <em>Kin Cng</em></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p class="Normal">Hin tuyn H Ni - Nha Trang ch c duy nht Vietnam Airlines khai thc. n ma h, khi nhu cu tng cao, Jetstar Pacific mi m li ng bay trong thi gian ngn. H nm ngoi, hng hng khng gi r cng thc hin m ng bay ny.</p>\r\n<p class="Normal">"Ty tnh hnh th trng, sau ngy 29/10, hng s c k hoch c th v ng bay H Ni - Nha Trang, d kin s khai thc thng l hng ngy tuyn ny trong thi gian ti", i din Jetstar Pacific cho bit.</p>\r\n<p class="Normal">Tng thi gian bay gia H Ni v Nha Trang vo khong 1h45 pht bay. T sn bay Cam Ranh v thnh ph Nha Trang khong 35 km bng ng b. Gi v tuyn ny hin nay khong hn mt triu ng mt v.</p>', '', 1, 11, 0, 44, '2011-05-14 09:17:31', 62, '', '2011-06-04 05:23:44', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-05-14 09:17:31', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 2, 0, 5, '', '', 0, 166, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(130, 'iu kin 1', 'iu-kin-1', '', '<h2>Vietnam Airlines: mc tiu tr thnh hng hng khng 4 sao</h2>\r\n<table border="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div><img src="http://giavemaybayre.com.vn/stores/images/news/eda_t1297181180_1Mow.jpg" alt="" width="150" /></div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>Ph Tng Gim c Tng Cng ty Hng khng Vit Nam (Vietnam Airlines) Trnh Hng Quang cho bit, mt trong nhng nhim v trng tm ca hng trong nm nay l tip tc nng cao cht lng dch v, p ng ngy cng tt hn nhu cu ca hnh khch.</p>\r\n', '\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><span style="display: block; margin-bottom: 6px;"> </span></p>\r\n<div>Thi gian qua, <a title="v my bay, v my bay gi r, t v my bay, lin h mua v" href="http://giavemaybayre.com.vn/" target="_blank">Vietnam Airlines</a>  u t mnh vo nng cao cht lng phc v thng qua vic t chc <a title="v my bay, v my bay gi r, t v my bay, lin h mua v" href="http://giavemaybayre.com.vn/" target="_blank">bn v in t</a>, lm th tc chuyn bay qua mng internet... Mc tiu ca hng  ra l tr thnh hng <a title="v my bay, v my bay gi r, t v my bay, lin h mua v" href="http://giavemaybayre.com.vn/" target="_blank">hng khng</a> t tiu chun "4 sao", n nm 2020, l mt trong s 10 hng hng khng c a chung nht chu  v cht lng dch v hnh khch. Ti khu vc ng Nam , Vietnam Airlines phn u l hng ln th 2 khu vc vo nm 2020.  hin thc ha mc tiu, ngoi vic nng cao cht lng, Tng Cng ty cn tip tc thc hin  n hin i ha i bay v d kin n nm 2020 s c 163 chic hin i nh Boeing 787, Airbuss A350; m rng mng ng bay ti 65 im trn khp th gii... Hin, Vietnam Airlines ang s hu i bay gm 70 chic vi  tui khai thc trung bnh 6,5 nm.</div>', 1, 8, 0, 51, '2011-06-29 09:31:07', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-06-29 09:31:07', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_ic