(71, 'Hng khng p dng ph ph thu nhin liu', 'hnag-khong-ap-dung-phi-phu-thu-nhien-lieu', '', '<p></p>\r\n<p><strong>Gi du  th gii lun bin  ng theo chiu hng tng do tnh hnh bt n ti  mt s khu vc ti  trung ng  khin cc hng hng khng phi p dng  v tng ph ph  thu nhin liu vo gi v my bay. </strong></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<table class="sgtoimageleft" style="width: 229px; height: 171px;" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="left">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img class="sgtoimageleft_popup" src="http://www.thesaigontimes.vn/Uploads/Articles/52766/e0841_airasiaonline_200.jpg" border="0" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="sgtoimageleft">AirAsia thng bo p dng ph ph thu nhin liu vo gi v my bay t ngy 3-5 - nh: Mng Bnh</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p>Ngy 3-5, AirAsia bt u p dng tr li khon ph ph nhin liu   cho tt c cc ng bay ni a v quc t, sau hn 2 nm tp on hng   khng gi r ny b ph ph xng du t gi v my bay.</p>\r\n<p>AirAsia cho rng hng phi p dng ph ph thu xng du do gi nhin   liu my bay  tng cao, vt hn 140  la M/thng. Mc gi ny cao   hn nhiu so vi thi im cui nm 2008 khi hng b ph ph thu nhin   liu v gi du th gii lc  gim mnh, c lc xung gn 30  la   M/thng do khng hong ti chnh ton cu.</p>\r\n<p>AirAsia thng bo hng s p dng mc ph thu nhin liu 10 ringit   (gn 70.000 ng) cho cc chuyn bay c gi bay t hn 2 ting, 20   ringit cho cc chuyn bay t 2 n 3 ting, 30 ringit cho cc chuyn bay   di hn 3 ting, v t 50-90 ringit cho cc chuyn bay di do AirAsia X   thc hin t Kuala Lumpur n chu  v chu u.</p>\r\n<p>AirAsia v cc hng thnh vin l Thai AirAsia v Indonesia AirAsia   ang thc hin cc chuyn bay t Kuala Lumpur (Malaysia), Bangkok (Thi   Lan) v Jakarta (Indonesia) n Vit Nam, vi cc chuyn bay gia H  Ni  - Kuala Lumpur v TPHCM - Jakarta c gi bay hn 2 ting.</p>\r\n<p>AirAsia l hng hng khng thc hin cc chuyn bay quc t n Vit   Nam mi nht cng b p dng ph ph thu nhin liu. Trc , cc hng   hng khng truyn thng nh Singapore Airlines, Thai Airways, Malaysia   Airlines, Jetstar Airways cng  cng b p dng v iu chnh tng  mc  ph ny nh l mt trong cc bin php i ph vi gi nhin liu  tng  cao.</p>\r\n<p>Theo Reuters, vo thng 4 va qua, hng hng khng Singapore Airlines   cng b tng thm mc ph thu nhiu liu t 4-32  la M ty thuc  vo   di ca mi chng v hng gh, p dng cho cc v my bay xut  sau  ngy 21-4 ca hng v SilkAir do gi nhin liu  tng hn 30% k  t  u nm n nay.</p>\r\n<p>Hng hng khng Thai Airways cng p dng mc ph xng du mi t 28    la M/chng cho cc v bn ra cch nay hn mt thng. y l mc  thp  nht m hng p dng cho cc chuyn bay c thi gian bay di 2  ting,  gm cc chuyn bay gia Bangkok v TPHCM v H Ni.</p>\r\n<p>Trong ln gp bo ch tai TPHCM vo thng 4-2011, Gim c ca   Malaysia Airlines ti Vit Nam, ng Zuraidi Saisi cho bit vic p dng   ph ph thu xng du l mt bin php bt buc m cc hng hng khng   phi p dng trc tnh hnh gi du th gii tng mnh khin gi xng   my bay tng theo. Tuy nhin, ng khng cho bit c th mc ph ph   nhin liu m hng ang p dng cho cc chuyn bay gia Kuala Lumpur v   Vit Nam.</p>\r\n<p>Theo Hip hi vn ti hng khng quc t IATA, gi nhin liu my bay    t 140,2  la M/thng tnh n thi im ngy 22-4-2011, tng   3,5% so vi thng trc  v 47,7% so vi cng k ca nm 2010.</p>', '', 1, 3, 0, 28, '2011-05-14 09:20:23', 62, '', '2011-05-15 04:01:10', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-05-14 09:20:23', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 2, 0, 11, '', '', 0, 332, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(72, 'Gi trn tng, hng khng vn duy tr cc mc v gi r', 'gia-tran-tang-hang-khong-van-duy-tri-cac-muc-ve-gia-re', '', '<p><strong>Cng  vi gi xng du, gi  in v nhiu gi hng ha thit yu khc, gi v  my bay cng rp rnh  tng t sau ngy 27/4. Tuy nhin, cc hng s vn  duy tr cc mc v  gi r  tng kh nng cnh tranh. </strong></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<table style="width: 100%;" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td height="25" valign="top"><br /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td height="18">\r\n<table style="width: 1px;" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="left">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<table style="width: 1px;" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="left">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src="http://images.vnmedia.vn/images_upload/2011/vnm_2011_345346.jpg" border="0" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center"><br /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n<td><br /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p align="justify">Quyt  nh mi ca B Ti chnh v khung gi cc  vn chuyn hnh khch hng  v ph thng trn cc ng bay ni a cn  v th c quyn  chnh  thc c hiu lc t ngy 27/4. Theo , gi  trn trn cc ng bay s  tng ln ti hn 20% so vi mc hin nay.</p>\r\n<p align="justify">C  th, i vi ng bay c c ly di 300km, mc  gi cao nht l 863.636  ng/v (mc c l 682.000 ng); c ly t  300km n di 500km, mc  cao nht l 1.100.000 ng/v (mc b c l  864.000 ng); ng bay c  c ly t 500km n di 850km gi 1.481.818  ng/v (mc c l  1.182.000 ng) ;  c ly t 850km n di  1.000km, mc gi l  1.909.091 ng/v; c ly t 1.000km n di  1.280km l 2.227.273  ng/v v mc gi cho c ly t 1.280km tr ln  ln ti 2.727.273  ng/v. Trong khi theo quy nh trc , th ng  bay t 850km tr  ln u c mc gi trn l 1.819.000 ng.</p>\r\n<p align="justify">Cc  mc gi ni trn cha bao gm thuVAT v cc  loi ph khc. Nh vy  nu tnh thm c thu VAT 10%, gi v my bay  mt chiu tuyn H Ni -  Ph Quc (ng bay di nht) c th ln n 3  triu ng.</p>\r\n<p align="justify">i  din cc hng hng khng nh Vietnam Airlines,  Jetstar Pacific u cho  bit hng ang chun b cho k hoch tng gi  v my bay v s sm cng  b trong thi gian ti. Tuy nhin, c hai  hng u s vn c cc mc gi  a dng theo nhiu tiu chun khc nhau   ph hp vi mi khch hng.  Cc hng v gi r s hu nh khng tng  hoc ch tng cht t.<br /><br />Theo  i din ca hng hng khng  Jetstar, vi chnh sch l hng khng gi  r nn hng lun c rt nhiu  loi mc gi khc nhau, tu thuc theo  thi gian t v, chng trnh  khuyn mi khc nhau. Cc mc gi di  gi trn chim n 90%, do vy,  d gi v c tng th hng khch c nhu  cu mua v gi r vn c nhiu  c hi  la chn mc v ph hp vi  mnh.</p>\r\n<p align="justify">i  din Cc Hng khng cho bit, t cui nm 2010,  cc hng hng khng   nhiu ln  ngh tng mc trn gi v my bay,  thm ch c hng  ngh  tng ti 60%. Theo phn tch cacc hng hng  khng, khong 70% chi  ph ca ngnh hng khng phi tr bng ngoi t:  Mua nhin liu, thu  tu bay, thu phi cng... V th khi USD iu  chnh lp tc chi ph gi  thnh i ln.</p>\r\n<p align="justify">Mi  y, tr li phng vn ca bo Tui tr, ng Lu  Thanh Bnh, Cc ph  Cc Hng khng Vit Nam cho bit, gi xng du th  gii hin nay  hn  mc 105 USD/thng, nhng theo ng Bnh, nu gi  xng du th gii gim,  c quan qun l nh nc cng s iu chnh  gim gi v my bay trn c  s gim st cht ch vic ng k gi ca  cc hng hng khng  m bo  quyn li ca ngi tiu dng.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', '', 1, 3, 0, 28, '2011-05-14 09:22:04', 62, '', '2011-05-15 04:03:18', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-05-14 09:22:04', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 2, 0, 8, '', '', 0, 255, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(73, 'Chp nhn cho hng khng  rp bay ti Vit Nam', 'chap-nhan-cho-hang-khong-a-rap-bay-den-viet', '', '<p><strong>Th trng B GTVT Phm Qu Tiu va c vn bn chp thun v ch trng cho php hng hng khng chuyn ch hng ha ca  rp - X t khai thc cc chuyn bay i, n Vit Nam. </strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table style="width: 250px;" align="right" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src="http://giaothongvantai.com.vn/Thumbnail.ashx/0/250/0/75151BAA5962440C9295477AB9078B0D/Chap_thuan_cho_hang_khong_A_rap_bay_toi_Viet_Nam.jpg" align="absMiddle" border="0" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>Saudi Arabian Airlines Cargo (SV) hon thin th tc xin cp php bay.</p>\r\n<p align="justify">Theo Ph Cc trng Cc Hng khng VN Li Xun Thanh, hin Vit Nam v  rp - X t cha k Hip nh hng khng v cha c bt k hng hng khng no thc hin cc chuyn bay trc tip gia hai nc. Gia khu vc Trung ng v Vit Nam mi c hng hng khng Qatar Airways, Cargolux khai thc.</p>\r\n<p align="justify">Theo k hoch, SV s m 2 ng bay vn chuyn hng ha trc tip t  rp - X t n Vit Nam qua Thng Hi, Trung Quc.</p>\r\n<p align="right">Theo GTVT</p>', '', 1, 11, 0, 44, '2011-05-14 12:36:06', 62, '', '2011-06-04 05:23:32', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-05-14 12:36:06', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 2, 0, 4, '', '', 0, 117, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(74, 'Vietnam Airlines sp c thm 30 my bay mi', 'vietnam-airlines-sap-co-them-30-may-bay-moi', '', '<p></p>\r\n<p><strong>Vietnam Airlines (VNA) s c  Chnh ph bo lnh cho cc giao dch thu, mua hn 30 my bay A321-200  khai thc trong giai on t nm 2011 n ht 2015.</strong></p>\r\n<div style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://vemaybaytructuyen.com/images/stories/vietnam-arlines-ecommerce-large.jpg" border="0" width="374" height="243" /></div>\r\n<p><br />Th tng  c vn bn ng  v vic bo lnh cc giao dch thu mua 8 my bay A321-200 ca VNA.<br /><br />Bn  cnh , VNA cng c duyt phng n mua 26 my bay A321-200 trong  giai on t nm 2011 n 2015. D kin vo cui nm nay, VNA m ng  bay thng t Vit Nam i Anh Quc v M.<br /><br />Vietnam Airlines ang  y mnh tin trnh c phn ha. Mi y, B Giao thng Vn ti cng bo  co Th tng v c ch u thu thu t vn quc t  c phn ho  VNA.<br />Trc , VNA   xut gi gi thu t vn ny l gn 3,9  triu USD. Vietnam Airlines cng  ngh chn 9 nh thu quc t c   iu kin vo danh sch mi thu.</p>', '', 1, 3, 0, 28, '2011-05-14 12:38:32', 62, '', '2011-05-15 04:02:23', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-05-14 12:38:32', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 2, 0, 9, '', '', 0, 314, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(75, 'VNA phn u ng th hai chu ', 'vna-phn-u-ng-th-hai-chau-a', '', '<p><strong>Tng  cng ty Hng khng Vit Nam (Vietnam Airlines - VNA) va  n nhn Hun  chng H Ch Minh do Ch tch nc trao tng. T mt  hng hng khng  nh, hin VNA  c i bay gm 70 chic my bay hin  i vi mng li  79 ng bay quc t v ni a. VNA hin l im  sng ca ngnh. </strong></p>\r\n<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="cls_NewsTitle" colspan="2"><br /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="cls_NewsPublishedDate" colspan="2"><br /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="top">\r\n<table class="tblImageDetail" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="left">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="left" valign="top"><img src="http://www.ven.vn/Portals/0/users/host/042011/VNA-phan-dau-dung-thu-2-cha.jpg" border="0" /><br /><label class="image_desc"></label></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p class="cls_NewsSubject">Tng trng nhiu mt</p>\r\n<div>Trong  nhiu nm qua, vi cht lng dch v ngy cng c nng  cao, VNA   tr thnh mt thng hiu ln, giu sc cnh tranh, vi mt  hnh nh tr  trung, hin i, nng ng. VNA  khng nh c vi  cng chng, vi  bn b quc t sc mnh, tr tu v nng lc ca con  ngi Vit Nam -  pht trin, qun l v iu hnh thnh cng mt hng  hng khng c quy  m ln. Khng nhng hon thnh tt vai tr ca hng  hng khng quc gia,  VNA cn bn b thc hin s mng l mt trong  nhng cu ni vn ha, du  lch quan trng, em bn sc ca Vit Nam n  bn b th gii. y cng  l cu ni u t, xc tin thng mi quan  trng, ng gp vo s pht  trin chung ca t nc trong thi gian  qua.</div>\r\n<div>Trong  nhng thi im kh khn, khi cc doanh nghip v nn kinh  t b nhng  nh hng tiu cc do nhiu nguyn nhn khc nhau, c bit  do khng  hong ton cu nhng tnh hnh ti chnh ca Tng cng ty vn  n nh,  cn i ti chnh v kh nng thanh ton, vic lm thu nhp  ca ngi  lao ng c m bo v khng ngng c ci thin. ng  thi, vn gi  vng v xy dng i ng lao ng c trnh  chuyn mn  cao, tim cn  vi mt bng ca khu vc, c bit l i ng k s,  ngi li my bay  v chuyn gia k thut. C th ni, y l s tng  trng nhiu mt.</div>\r\n<div>Theo  B trng B Giao thng Vn ti H Ngha Dng, VNA lm c  iu ny l  bi: Th nht, u t ng hng  pht trin i my bay  th h mi,  hin i; bc u c c s h tng bo dng, sa cha v  o to tin  tin, h tr cho s pht trin bn vng mai sau. Th hai,  xy dng tm  nhn xa trong chin lc pht trin, c bit trong chin  lc pht  trin ngun nhn lc chuyn ngnh, c trnh  chuyn nghip  cao. Th  ba, c chin lc kinh doanh ng n, qua  pht trin th  trng, bm  st s bin ng  c cc chin thut tip cn ph hp, t   thu ht  thm hnh khch, tng doanh thu.</div>\r\n<div>Nhng  kt qu m VNA t c trong 15 nm qua c  ngha ht sc  quan trng,  khng nhng gp phn vo s pht trin ca ngnh giao thng  vn ti, m  cn gp phn vo cng cuc pht trin kinh t ca cc  vng, min, thc  y giao thng, du lch, n nh chnh tr x hi v  bo v an ninh  quc phng ca t nc. c bit, VNA cn trc tip gp  phn qung b  hnh nh mt t nc Vit Nam i mi y tim nng v  thn thin.</div>\r\n<div>VNA s t doanh thu 7 t USD vo nm 2020</div>\r\n<div>ng  Phm Ngc Minh, Tng gim c Vietnam Airlines cho bit,   t c  con s ny, n nm 2020, Vietnam Airlines s tp trung u t  vo i  tu bay vi 163 chic (cc chng loi) trong  c 2 loi my  bay hin  i nht l B787 ca Boeing v A350 ca Airbus. Cng  l  vic m rng  mng ng bay ti 65 im trn ton th gii. V sn  lng vn chuyn,  c t xp x 35 triu lt khch, 620 nghn tn  hng ha, doanh thu d  kin khong 7 t USD/ nm.</div>\r\n<div>Trong  nm 2010  c 7 ng bay quc t v 4 ng bay ni a  c m hoc  khai thc tr li trong nm 2010. y c coi l nm pht  trin mnh m  v mng ng bay ca Vietnam Airlines.</div>\r\n<div>Trong  vng hn mt nm, t quy m khai thc trung bnh ch khong  225 chuyn  bay/ngy, n cui nm 2010, Vietnam Airlines  tng quy m  ln ti gn  1,5 ln, thc hin trung bnh khong 320 chuyn bay/ngy.  Cng tc khai  thc bay c m bo thng sut, m bo an ton an ninh  vi trn  88.000 chuyn bay trong nm 2010.</div>\r\n<div>Vietnam  Airlines t mc tiu, n 2020, hng s tr thnh 1 trong  10 hng hng  khng c a chung ti chu  v ng th 2 chu .<br /><br /></div>\r\n<table border="1" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td bgcolor="#cccccc">\r\n<div>2010 nm nhiu s kin ng nh ca VNA</div>\r\n<div>VNA  tr thnh thnh vin chnh thc ca Lin minh Hng khng ton  cu  -Skyteam, mt trong 3 lin minh hng khng hng u th gii</div>\r\n<div>Tng doanh thu ca VNAnm 2010 t khong 36.265 t ng, tng 37,6% so vi nm 2009</div>\r\n<div>Cho n hnh khch th 12 triu (tng khi lng vn chuyn hnh  khch 33,7% so vi nm 2009 v vt mc 13,2% so k hoch nm 2010).</div>\r\n<div>Sn  lng gh cung ng (gh lun chuyn ASK) tuy ch tng 24,6%  song sn  lng khch lun chuyn (RPK) tng mnh ti 33,2% so cng k</div>\r\n<div>H s s dng gh c ci thin r rt, t 77,1% (tng 2,6 im so vi k hoch nm v tng 3,6 im so vi nm 2009)</div>\r\n<div>t chng ch FAR 145 ca M v t chc sa cha v bo dng my bay</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', '', 1, 3, 0, 28, '2011-05-14 12:41:09', 62, '', '2011-05-15 04:02:54', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-05-14 12:41:09', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 2, 0, 6, '', '', 0, 329, 'robots=\nauthor='),
