(109, 'Mt thong bun m', 'mt-thoang-buon-me', '', '<div class="travel-subject">\r\n<h1>Mt Thong Ban M</h1>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><img src="http://www.vemaybay.com/upload/du-lich/ban-me-thuot-vietnam-68.jpg" border="0" alt="Ban Me Thuot" vspace="5" width="133" height="90" align="left" style="margin: 5px 12px 0pt 0pt; float: left;" /></p>\r\n<p>Mt vi ngy rong chi khp Ban M (k Lk), ngi ta d b "say" bi hng c ph x ny.<br /> <br /> Bun Ma Thut khng bng by ho nhong, nhng chnh v mc mc m nt Ty Nguyn y  lm lu luyn bao bc chn l khch gn xa.<br /> <br /> <strong>Say c ph</strong><br /> <br /> Khng ch c nhng thng cnh ni ting nh nh Lc Giao, cha Sc t Khi oan, nh y Bun Ma Thut, bia Lc Giao, khu Bit in Bo i - hin l Bo tng cc dn tc Vit Nam... Ban M cn lm ngy ngt bao ngi vi hng v c ph nng nn v m . n y, bn c th gh qua nhiu qun c ph ln ni ting nh P Lang, Thung Lng Hng,  Xanh, v c bit l Lng c ph Trung Nguyn trn ng L Thnh Tng.<br /> <br /> Lng c ph Trung Nguyn ni bt vi nt kin trc, chm khc cng phu, mang m phong cch kin trc c Hi An. Nh c li th khng gian rng ri, thong mt v phong cnh hu tnh, t lu lng c ph Trung Nguyn  tr thnh ni th gin, thng thc c ph tuyt vi cho du khch. Ni ny chia thnh nhiu khu nh c khc nhau. Ti khu nh c th hai, mang ch  Ni kt ni th gii, khch tham quan c c hi khm ph v con ng chinh phc c ph trn th gii. Ring  nh c 3, khng gian mang m phong cch hin i ca phng Ty. Khch tham quan c c hi khm ph v hiu r hn qu trnh chn lc, ch bin, pha ch c o, y ngh thut. y cng chnh l chn thng thc c ph yu thch ca rt nhiu khch tham quan.<br /> <br /> n vi ni ny, du khch s c dp tham quan trung tm qu lu nim, tha h la chn hng trm mn qu c o khc nhau. i din khu ny l nhng thc nc cao nhn to, t cnh snh thng thc c ph ngoi tri, to cm gic mt m trong nhng tra h oi bc.  cng l ni l tng  chim ngng nhng chng trnh biu din ngh thut c t chc thng xuyn. Nm gia trung tm Lng c ph, nh sn di l ni ti hin khng gian hi hp v sinh hot ca nhng tp th gia nh truyn thng ngi  . y l a im thng thc c ph trong khng gian c o ca vn ha  . c bit, bn cn c dp khm ph v tri nghim cc cng on ch bin c ph t m v tinh t.<br /> <br /> Sau khi mc sc say vi hng v c ph ti "ngi lng" c o trn, bn c th tip tc khm ph nhng im du lch ni ting vng ln cn TP. Ci voi  Bn n, ln h Lk cu c v tm sui, tham quan cm thc ray Sp... l nhng tit mc bn khng th b qua. Nhng hy cng i "o b" ci bao t trc .<br /> <br /> <strong>n g tht</strong><br /> <br /> Nu  Si Gn, mun kim mt con g ta ng ngha qu khng phi d, nhng  ln vi Ban M, ln vi ni rng Ty Nguyn, vic n g ta "sing tp th dc" l chuyn nh.<br /> <br /> <input src="http://www.vemaybay.com/public/upload/du-lich/Ga%20La%20Hanh.jpg" type="image" /><br /> G hp l chanh<br /> <br /> Vi nhng ngi trt m v ngt nh nhng, thanh tao, trt ghin ci mu trng mut ca tng s tht g mn dai, mn g hp chanh mi ng l "tuyt nh khoi khu".  thng thc mn ny ng a ch, bn nh gh qua qun G hp chanh  18 Trng Cng nh, TP.Bun Ma Thut. Sut hn 10 nm qua, du khch thp phng u truyn tai nhau v mn g hp chanh thm ngon ti y.<br /> <br /> Ch ch qun tit l:  mn g hp l chanh pht huy ht ci "thn" ca n, g phi l g t, khng qu 1,5kg  khi hp, tht g va chn vn gi c v ngt t nhin.<br /> <br /> G sau khi lm sch, i nc va si, cho 1 t mui, gng, hnh tm ch nh vo  lm dy mi thm ca g.  khong 10 pht, vt g ra v thoa nh nhng ln mnh g hn hp ng, mui, ht nm  g thm gia v. Sau  cho g vo xng hp khong 15 pht na  g chn ti v "ngm" ht ci m  ca gia v. Mn g hp l chanh ny tuy bnh d nhng thng thc n cng i hi c mt ngh thut ch khng phi chuyn chi. Ny nh, ngay khi a g ang trn ng ngao du t di bp ln, mi bn  phi ht ly ht  ci mi thm phng phc ca a tht g n ci hng thoang thong ca l chanh non thi nhuyn.<br /> <br /> Va t a g xung, th gic ca bn li mt phen b khiu khch bi mu tht g trng phau, e p np mnh di lp da vng m, im xuyt thm t gam xanh ca l chanh thi ch. Nhn tay x mt ming tht g, pht thm t mui tiu chanh, t t nhm nhp ci ngt thanh tao, dai dai ca tht ha vi v mn m ca mui tinh, cay nng m p ca tiu v v chua nh nh ca chanh, m bo d dy ca bn d cha n ba vn phi ro ln ng c v khin bn gp lin t t cho n khi 5 ngn tay u m mng v ngp y gia v.  n g ta ngon, bn cng c th gh qua qun Amateur trn ng Trn Ph. Ni ny c kh nhiu mn ngon dn gi, c trng ca ni rng Ty Nguyn, c bit l nhng mn t g. Ring mn g quay lun c qun chm cht s 1, vi phong cch quay kiu Bc Kinh m  hng v.</p>', '', 1, 11, 0, 43, '2011-05-23 03:46:27', 62, '', '2011-05-23 03:50:07', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-05-23 03:46:27', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 2, 0, 5, '', '', 0, 0, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(110, ' nng', 'a-nng', '', '<div>\r\n<h1>Khu du lch B N - Ni Cha</h1>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><img style="float: left; margin: 5px 12px 0pt 0pt;" src="http://www.vemaybay.com/upload/du-lich/da-nang-vietnam-21.jpg" alt="Da Nang" align="left" border="0" height="90" vspace="5" width="133" />\r\n<p>B N - Ni Cha l khu du lch sinh thi-ngh dng l tng  min Trung, thuc a phn huyn Ha Vang, thnh ph  Nng, cch trung tm thnh ph khong 30km v hng Ty Nam,   cao 1.487m so vi mc nc bin, kh hu quanh nm mt m, nhit  trung bnh t 17  C - 20  C.  B N mt ngy c 4 ma ring bit: Bui sng tit xun, bui tra vo h, bui chiu se se sang thu v m v lnh gi nh gia ng.<br /> <br /> B N c coi l l phi xanh, l hn ngc qu v kh hu m thin nhin ban tng cho  Nng. Du khch n B N khng ch c tn hng khng kh trong lnh, xanh, sch p m cn c chim ngng nhng cnh quan p m him vng ngh mt no c c.<br /> <br /> Vo nhng ngy tri quang my tnh, du khch c th thu gn trong tm mt c mt vng khng gian rng ln nh thnh ph  Nng, vnh Vng Thng vi ng vin hnh vng cung t chn o Hi Vn n bn o Sn Tr, bi bin M Kh, non nc Ng Hnh Sn, sng Thu Bn un quanh nhng cnh ng tr ph, C Lao Chm gia nhp nh sng bic... Thin nhin nh mt bc tranh thy mc k th.<br /> <br /> u th k 20,  phc v cho nhu cu ngh ngi ca ngi Php ti min Trung, nhiu nh ngh, bit th, khch sn  mc ln sut dc cc trin ni, trn nh Ni Cha v nh B N. Lc  B N nhanh chng tr thnh mt trong nhng ni ngh mt ni ting v ln nht ng Dng, thu ht nhiu du khch ngang tm vi Le Bockor (Campuchia), Cap Saint Jacques (Vng Tu), Tam o, Sapa. Sau  do chin tranh tn ph, ni y tr nn hoang ph v b lng qun theo thi gian.<br /> <br /> Nhng nm gn y,  Nng  dn khi phc v tn to mt s khu bit th c kiu Php, khu vn ho Pht gio, hm ru v hng lot khch sn, bit th, qun bar, sn tennis, cu lng, bida...&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br /> <br /> Mt bn sao ca cha Linh ng  Ng Hnh Sn c xy dng  y. Trn ni cao, cha Linh ng v cng linh thing, nhng nt kin trc tinh t ca cha lm cho khng kh thin mn thm thanh tnh, lng ngi vn cnh cha thm thanh tao.<br /> <br /> Cm gic mt mi dng nh tan bin khi du khch c chim ngng tng Pht Thch Ca to thin thuc vo hng ln nht chu . Tng Pht l thin cao 30m uy nghi gia bn b lng lng my tri, gi ni. Bn cnh cha Linh ng vn cn  nhng hm ru ca ngi Php nay vn c s dng  chng ct ru v lun m ca cho du khch vo tham quan, nhm nhp mt cht men cay  si lng.</p>\r\n<p><br /> B N c h ng thc vt phong ph v a dng. Trong nhng cnh rng nguyn sinh i ngn l ni c tr ca 256 loi ng vt, trong  c 61 loi th, 178 loi chim v 17 loi b st. H thc vt  y c 543 loi gm 136 h v 379 chi. B N l ni c nhiu loi ng vt qu him c tr nh tr sao, gu en chu , vn bc m hung... Nm 1986, B N  c Chnh ph cng nhn l khu d tr thin nhin, i tng bo v l rng nhit i v nhiu loi ng thc vt qu him. <br /> <br /> Vi nhng u th tuyt diu , Khu du lch B N  c tp trung xy dng li thnh khu ngh dng v du lch cao cp, c tnh cnh tranh cao trong khu vc, c bit u t vo h thng cp treo, khu lu tr, khu vui chi gii tr...<br /> <br /> Di chn ni B N l dng sui M thu ht du khch n ngh ngi vo ma h nng bc. Cng  y thc Tc Tin cao 9 tng, ng t di chn thc trng ln nh mt mi tc ca nng tin bng bnh h o. Thin nhin hoang s  B N rt hp dn v quyn r. Mt s bit th ti B N cng  c trng tu v xy mi vi y  tin nghi hin i; h thng khch sn, nh hng, sn tennis v nhiu loi dch v khc sn sng phc v du khch chu o.<br /> <br /> n vi B N, du khch s cm nhn c cm gic nh i lc trong my, lng thng gia sng ging sn ni v ngt ngy trong ting ht vo von, lnh lt ca cc loi chim.<br /> <br />  ln c nh B N, trc y du khch phi vt qua 15km ng quanh co, un ln. Nay vi h thng cp treo hin i ch mt 15 pht. Theo xc nhn ca Hip hi Cp treo th gii, tuyn cp treo ny  c lp 02 k lc th gii,  l tuyn cp treo mt dy di nht th gii (5.042,62m) v c  cao chnh lch gia ga trn v ga di ln nht th gii (1.291,81m).<br /> <br /> Khi i cp treo, du khch s c dp khm ph ton cnh B N t trn cao v ngm hnh nh trn cc cabin, mi hnh nh mang mt c im ring ca B N nh:<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; K lc th gii v  di ca cp treo 1 dy;<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; K lc th gii v cp treo c  cao chnh lch ln nht gia 2 ga;<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Kh hu giao chuyn t ma H sang ma ng khi i trn cp;<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Kh hu chuyn i 4 ma trong ngy;<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Thc Tc Tin;<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Cha Linh ng;<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Ni Cha - Ngun gc ca tn gi B N;<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Hoa o chung - l biu tng ca B N; <br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Khu du lch c kh hu vng ni gn thnh ph bin nht (cch  Nng khong 30 km). <br /> <br /> B N nay  tr thnh nim t ho cho ngi dn Vit Nam ni chung v  Nng ni ring. Mt m ngh li  B N l dp  du khch nghe hi th ca ni rng v sng gia thin nhin hoang d. Hy mt ln n vi B N  qun i nhng mt mi ca i thng v tn hng nhng giy pht th gin thn tin.<br /> <br /> B N, mt im du lch hp dn mi khi ai  c dp n vi thnh ph  Nng.<br /> <br /> ----------------------------<br /> <br /> Thng tin thm:<br /> <br /> + Gi cp treo mi bao gm hai tuyn cp treo (Tuyn th 1 v tuyn th 2) nh sau:<br /> - Ngi ln: 160.000 VND/ngi;<br /> <br /> - Tr em (t 1m  1.3m): 120.000 VND/ngi.</p>\r\n<p>Ghi ch: 8 ngi/Cabin; Tr em di 1m c i min ph vi iu kin phi c ngi ln i cng.</p>\r\n<p><br /> + Qu khch c th ngh ti cc khu ngh trn ni vi gi t 450.000 ng/phng/m nh:<br /> -&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Khu bit th Hong Lan<br /> -&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Khu bit th Vng Nguyt<br /> -&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Khch sn Morin<br /> -&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Khch sn L Nim<br /> -&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Khu ngh dng B N By Night<br /> <br /> Xin lu tr  cha Linh ng cng l la chn ca nhiu du khch khi cc khu ngh  y  kn phng.<br /> &nbsp;<br /> + Ti y cn thng xuyn t chc cc m la tri, qung b cc c sn vng ni v to iu kin gip du khch i tham quan d ngoi.</p>\r\n</div>', '', 1, 11, 0, 43, '2011-05-31 05:04:12', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-05-31 05:04:12', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 4, '', '', 0, 6, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(111, 'Thng tin du lch Hi An', 'thong-tin-du-lch-hi-an', '', '<div>\r\n<h1>C Lao Chm  o xanh quyn r</h1>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><img style="float: left; margin: 5px 12px 0pt 0pt;" src="http://www.vemaybay.com/upload/du-lich/hoi-an-vietnam-18.jpg" alt="Hoi An" align="left" border="0" height="90" vspace="5" width="133" />\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial;" face="Arial">Cch Ca i khong 15km, cch ph c Hi An khong 18km v pha ng, C Lao Chm (x o Tn Hip, thnh ph Hi An, tnh Qung Nam) l mt cm o bao gm 8 o ln, nh ni tip nhau theo hnh cnh cung tri rng trn din tch bin 15km,  l: hn Lao, hn Di, hn M, hn Kh M, hn Kh Con, hn L, hn Tai, hn ng v c khong hn 3.000 c dn sinh sng. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial;" face="Arial">Theo cc nh a cht, C Lao Chm l phn ko di v pha ng nam ca khi  hoa cng (granit) Bch M - Hi Vn - Sn Tr c hnh thnh cch y khong 230 triu nm. H thng t gy ny  to iu kin cho s m rng cc thung lng, lm nn nhiu h cha nc trn sn i v hng trm hang, hc su. <br /> <br /> Nhng ngy nng p, t Ca i phng tm mt, du khch s nhn thy C Lao Chm ging nh vin ngc xanh sm lp lnh gia bin khi. Nu theo thuyn du lch i t ph c Hi An qua nhng xm lng dc sng Thu Bn ra Ca i, du khch s thy C Lao Chm n hin pha xa xa vi v p lung linh huyn o <br /> <br /> Vi khong 1.500ha rng t nhin, 6.700ha mt nc, 165ha rn san h (gm 188 loi, 61 ging thuc 13 h khc nhau, c a vo danh sch bo v), hn 200 loi c xut hin trong 500ha rong, to, c bin cng cc loi sinh vt y dy c nh: thn mm, gip xc, da gai, giun cng 12 loi th, 13 loi chim, 130 loi b st v 5 loi lng c, hai trong s  c tn trong Sch  Vit Nam l chim yn v kh ui di, C Lao Chm c nh gi l ni c s a dng sinh hc him c trn th gii. <br /> <br /> Sng ti C Lao Chm, ch cn mt ngy thi, du khch cng cm thy mt iu rt khc bit,  l c ngm nhn nhng ch kh ui di nghch ngm nhng rt thn thin vi ngi, i khi vo sng sm hay chiu ti chng xung n st bin chi a.<br /> </span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial;" face="Arial">Nu c dp i tu vng qua pha ng o hn Lao, du khch va c dp c ngm nhn nhng vch  dng ng cao n 100m thng xuyn b sng v to thnh thp, tng,  chng, thc nc,   v cc mch nc ngm thnh hnh cc bn c, ra , u ngi... va c dp c ngm nhn nhng t Yn bm chnh vnh trn vch  trng ging nh nhng chic tai mu trng hay ngm nhn nhng n chim yn nh bay ti tp t ca hang ra bin. Theo truyn thuyt ngi dn ni y k li, loi chim ny ho thn t nng Yn, mt c gi lng bin sng vi cha m gi, bng gp cn hng thu cun tri lng mc, ch gia nh nng sng st tri dt vo o nh, cha m nng u ngt i v i kht, kit sc.  cu cha m, nng l i khp o tm thc n, nc ung nhng ch tm thy mt lt khoai kh nh nm mc kt trong khe , bn em v mm cho cha m. Cu c cha m th nng cht. Ba nm sau trn o xut hin mt loi chim nh c quanh qun trn m nng,  l loi chim yn. <br /> <br /> Du khch cng c th tham gia mt s tour du lch khc nh: tour Khm ph C Lao Chm, tour Ln bin ngm san h, xem c nhiu mu sc  bi Bc, Hn Di, tour vt bin tham quan lng chi bi Hng hoc c th tm bin v tn hng v p hoang s, tinh khit ti cc bi bin nh: bi ng, bi Chng... hay tham gia cc loi hnh th thao bin nh: lt vn, d bay, cho thuyn kayak, th diu, ua thuyn...<br /> <br /> Ti C Lao Chm, du khch cn c dp c tm hiu v gi tr vn ha ca nhng di tch thuc nn vn ha Sa Hunh, Chmpa, i Vit, c lin quan n qu trnh c tr ca c dn c cch y khong 3.000 nm, tham quan h thng hn 20 cng trnh kin trc c gm: nh, lng, miu, cha, ging c ca c ngi Chm v ngi Vit c xy dng cch y vi trm nm nh: cha Hi Tng, ging lng, lng ng, miu B, miu T ngh yn. c bit, du khch s c bit v k thut khai thc nc ngt ca c dn Chm c v bit v mi giao lu, bun bn gia C Lao Chm vi cc nc thuc Trung Cn ng, ng Nam  v n  cch y 1.000 nm trong hnh trnh con ng t la trn bin.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial;" face="Arial">C Lao Chm c du khch yu thch khng ch vng bin ni y c cnh sc thin nhin ti p, c nhiu loi hi sn nh: tm hm, c hng, hi sm, ngc trai, i mi, cua , mc, vy c, bo ng, c hng, c m, yn so, c x c v lu gi c mt kho tng vn ha - lch s gi tr trng tn t hng nghn nm m cn bi s nng hu v phong cch thn thin vi mi trng ca ngi dn a phng. Di s hng dn, qun l ca chnh quyn, ngi dn C Lao Chm tun th quy nh khng s dng ti ni lng, khng x rc...  gi cho mnh t xanh ny mi sch, p.<br /> <br /> T nm 2004, C Lao Chm  tr thnh khu bo tn bin di s gip  ca Chnh ph an Mch. Nm 2006, C lao Chm c cng nhn l di tch lch s vn ha quc gia. Thng 5/2009, C lao Chm chnh thc c y ban UNESCO cng nhn l Khu D tr sinh quyn th gii.</span></p>\r\n</div>', '', 1, 11, 0, 43, '2011-05-31 05:04:43', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-05-31 05:04:43', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 3, '', '', 0, 0, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(112, 'Thng tin du lch Ph Quc', 'thong-tin-du-lch-phu-quc', '', '<div>\r\n<h1>Du lch Ph Quc</h1>\r\n</div>\r\n<img style="float: left; margin: 5px 12px 0pt 0pt;" src="http://www.vemaybay.com/upload/du-lich/phu-quoc-vietnam-15.jpg" alt="Phu Quoc" align="left" border="0" height="90" vspace="5" width="133" />\r\n<p align="&quot;\\&quot;justify\\&quot;&quot;">Ph Quc h<span face="&quot;\\&quot;Arial\\&quot;&quot;">ay cn gi l o Ngc, l hn o ln nht ca Vit Nam, cng l o ln nht trong qun th 22 o ti Kin Giang, nm trong vnh Thi Lan.</span></p>\r\n<p align="&quot;\\&quot;justify\\&quot;&quot;"><span face="&quot;\\&quot;Arial\\&quot;&quot;">Ph Quc rng 573km2, dn s khong 100.000 ngi vi kh hu l tng v ti nguyn du lch phong ph... tt c to cho o mt thin ng v du lch rng, bin, sinh thi, vn ha...</span></p>\r\n<p align="&quot;\\&quot;justify\\&quot;&quot;"><span face="&quot;\\&quot;Arial\\&quot;&quot;">o Ph Quc ni ting l mt thng cnh tuyt p cn nguyn vn nt thin nhin hoang s. n y, du khch khng ch c ho mnh trong bin xanh, ngm nhng cnh rng nguyn sinh vi nhiu loi chim th v k hoa d tho, m cn c ving thm Dinh Cu, cha Sng Hng, nh thng nc mm, vn tiu, c s nui cy Ngc Trai, sui Tranh </span></p>\r\n<p align="&quot;\\&quot;justify\\&quot;&quot;"><span face="&quot;\\&quot;Arial\\&quot;&quot;">Ngoi ra, du khch cn c thng thc cc hi sn qu him nh bin mai, hi sm hay con nhum, mt loi c gai, rut n bo nh gch cua v ng qun mua v cho gia nh nhng chai nc mm thm ngon. Ph Quc s em n du khch nhng ngy ngh dng tuyt vi v th v.</span></p>', '', 1, 11, 0, 43, '2011-05-31 05:10:08', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-05-31 05:10:08', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 2, '', '', 0, 0, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(113, 'Hng dn du lch  Nng', 'hng-dn-du-lch-a-nng', '', '<div style="padding-bottom: 10px; padding-top: 20px;">\r\n<div style="padding-bottom: 3px;">\r\n<h2>i khi no?</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><center>\r\n<div style="text-align: left;"></div>\r\n<center>\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img alt=" Nng v m" src="http://du-lich.chudu24.com/f/d/090217/danang-ban-dem-2.jpg?c=1&amp;w=450" width="450" />\r\n<p> Nng v m</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</center></center>\r\n<p> Nng nm trong vng kh hu nhit i gi ma in hnh, nhit  cao v t bin ng. Kh hu  Nng l ni chuyn tip an xen gia kh hu min Bc v min Nam, vi tnh tri l kh hu nhit i in hnh  pha Nam. Mi nm c 2 ma r rt: ma ma ko di t thng 8 n thng 12 v ma kh t thng 1 n thng 7, thnh thong c nhng t rt ma ng nhng khng m v khng ko di.</p>\r\n<p>Thnh ph  Nng khng c thi gian qu nng, nhit  trung bnh 28-30C  vo thng 6, 7, 8. Cc thng ma ng nh 12, 1, 2 thch hp cho du lch v lc ny nhit  ch vo khong 18-23C. Ring vng rng ni B N   cao gn 1.500 m, nhit  trung bnh khong 20C c th gi l Thin ng du lch mi ca Vit Nam.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div style="padding-bottom: 3px;">\r\n<h2>i nhng u?</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<p>Thnh ph  Nng nm bn dng sng Hn; pha ng vn ra bin ng vi nhng bi bin di tm tp v bn o Sn Tr cn rt hoang s; pha Bc v pha Ty c bao bc bi o ni cao. o Hi Vn cheo leo him tr l ranh gii t nhin gia thnh ph v tnh Tha Thin-Hu.</p>\r\n<p>Ngoi s u i ca thin nhin cho  Nng, thnh ph cn c bao bc bi 3 di sn vn ha th gii: Hu, Hi An, M Sn. Xa hn mt cht na l di sn thin nhin th gii Vn Quc gia Phong Nha - K Bng. V th  Nng c xem l im trung chuyn quan trng trn con ng di sn min Trung.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>&nbsp;<strong> Ng Hnh Sn</strong> (cn gi l Non Nc)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<br /> Nm cch trung tm thnh ph khong 5 km v hng ng Nam. Ng Hnh Sn bao gm 6 ngn ni: Kim Sn, Mc Sn, Thy Sn, Dng Ha Sn, m Ho Sn v Th Sn tng trng cho 5 yu t ca v tr (Ng hnh). Trong lng ni c nhiu hang ng p v nhiu cha chin. Di chn ni cn c lng ngh  Non Nc ni ting. Bn cnh l bi bin Non Nc cn kh hoang s.<br />\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img alt="Ng hnh sn" src="http://du-lich.chudu24.com/f/d/090217/800px-ngu_hanh_son_toan_canh.jpg?c=1&amp;w=450" width="450" />\r\n<p>Ng hnh sn</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br />\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; B N - Ni Cha</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>L mt khu ngh mt cch trung tm thnh ph 40 km v pha Ty Nam. c v nh  Lt ca min Trung, v cng nh  Lt, B N - Ni Cha c xy dng thnh ni ngh ngi cho cc quan chc ngi Php trong thi k Php cn  h Vit Nam. Sau khi thc dn Php rt khi ng Dng, khu ny b b hoang v b tn ph nhiu bi chin tranh v thi gian. Gn y, thnh ph  Nng cho ti to li v hi vng trong tng lai B N - Ni Cha s li tr thnh mt khu ngh dng cao cp.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Bn o Sn Tr</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>Cn c ngi M gi l Ni Kh , l ni m  Nng vn ra bin ng xa nht. Ni y l khu bo tn thin nhin vi nhiu ng thc vt qu him. Di chn bn o Sn Tr l khu du lch Sui  v nhiu bi bin p nh: Bi Bt, Bi Rng, Bi Bc, Bi Nm.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp; Bi bin M Kh</strong> - bi bin p nht   Nng</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<br />\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp;&nbsp; o Hi Vn</strong> (c mnh danh l "Thin h  nht Hng quan")</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>L ni dy Trng Sn nh ra bin. Cheo leo v him tr, o Hi Vn khng ch l ranh gii gia hai min Nam - Bc m cn l mt chng tch hng hn cho thi k "mang gm i m ci" ca ngi Vit. Ngy nay, hm Hi Vn xuyn qua lng ni gip cho giao thng gia hai min tin li hn bao gi ht. ng hm di nht ng Nam  ny  phn no t du chm ht cho tm quan trng ca con o  i vo huyn thoi. Tuy vy, ng o Hi Vn vn c khch du lch a thch v cnh sc thin nhin rt k th.</p>\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img alt="Bn o Sn Tr" src="http://du-lich.chudu24.com/f/d/090217/bandaosontra.jpeg?c=1&amp;w=450" width="450" />\r\n<p>Bn o Sn Tr</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp;&nbsp; Bi bin</strong>\r\n<p> Nng ni ting vi nhng bi bin ct vng cn hoang s chy di hng cy s, nc trong xanh v m p quanh nm. Bi bin M Kh ca  Nng  c tp ch Forbes (M) bnh chn l mt trong 6 bi bin quyn r nht hnh tinh.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Bi bin Nam </li>\r\n<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Bi bin Xun Thiu</li>\r\n<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Bi bin Thanh Bnh</li>\r\n<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Bi bin M Kh</li>\r\n<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Bi bin Bc M An</li>\r\n<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Bi bin Non Nc</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Thnh in Hi</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>L ni  li du tch ho hng v mt thi chng thc dn Php ca nhn dn  Nng di s ch huy ca Nguyn Tri Phng. y cng l n ly quan trng gp phn nh bi cuc tn cng ca thc dn Php vo  Nng nhng nm 1858 - 1860. Mt tng i uy nghi ca Tng qun Nguyn Tri Phng  c dng ti y,  ghi nh mt giai on lch s ho hng ca thnh ph.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>Bo tng Ngh thut iu khc Chmpa</strong> (thng gi l C vin Chm)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>L ni lu gi c mt nn vn ha Chm rc r vi nhng pho tng c, nhng linh vt ca Vng quc Chm - pa hng mnh mt thi. y l bo tng c o v duy nht ca th gii v nn vn ha Chm.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp;&nbsp; nh Hi Chu <br /> </strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>Nm ti kit 42, ng Phan Chu Trinh, thuc T 6, phng Hi Chu 1, qun Hi Chu, l nh c nht ti  Nng. Trong nh th 42 bi v ca 42 tc h. 42 tc h ny u t thn Hiu Hin, x Hi Chu, huyn Ngc Sn, ph Tnh Gia, Thanh Ha, theo vua L Thnh Tn vo Nam t nm Tn Mo (1471). Nm 1719, Cha Nguyn Phc Chu trong 1 chuyn tun du phng Nam  gh qua v ngh li  nh ny. Sau ny, khi cha bng h, ngi dn trong vng  lp bi v th cha ti y. nh c B vn ha thng tch cng nhn l di tch lch s vo ngy 12/7/2001/.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; nh Ni Nam</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Nay  khi ph Nam Sn, phng Ha Cng, qun Hi Chu. nh c xy dng nm t T (1905). Ngy 4/1/1999 nh c B vn ha thng tin cng nhn l di tch lch s cp quc gia.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp; nh Tu Loan</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>Hin  ti thn Ty Loan, x Ha Phong, huyn Ha Vang. c xy dng vo nhng nm cui th k XVIII, c th l vo nm Thnh Thi th nht (1889). Cng nh nh Ni Nam v B Bn, nh Ty Loan th Thnh hong bn x v cc v tin hin, hu hin ca lng. Ngy xa, hng nm nhn dn t chc l t Xun vo 14 - 15 thng 2 m lch v t Thu vo 14 - 15 thng 8 m lch ti nh. Hin nay, nh Ty Loan l ngi nh duy nht cn gi c 15 sc phong t thi Minh Mng n Bo i.</p>\r\n<p>Thnh ph  Nng l mt im dng chn l tng, du khch c th thng thc nhng giy pht tuyt vi trn nh ni, trong rng su hay bn b sng, b bin; cng c th hng th nhng dch v vi cht lng quc t khi ngh ngi ti cc khu du lch ca thnh ph.</p>\r\n<p> Nng, vi nh hng l mt trung tm dch v, du lch ca min Trung, ca c nc v xa hn na l khu vc, quc t. Hng lot khu du lch  v ang c xy dng, hi ha vi thin nhin nhng cng khng km phn hin i. T nhng khu ngh dng cc k sang trng mang tiu chun 4 - 5 sao nh Furama, Sandy Beach, Sn Tr Resort &amp; Spa... hay nhng khu du lch sinh thi trong lnh nh Sui Lng, B N, Sn Tr, Non Nc...</p>\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src="http://du-lich.chudu24.com/f/d/090217/mykhe.png?c=1&amp;w=450" alt="Bi bin M Kh" width="450" />\r\n<p>Bi bin M Kh</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\nTnh n nm 2008, trn a bn  Nngc 45 d n du lch c UBND TP c ch trng cho php u t vi tng vn u t gn 2 t USD. Trong  c 33 d n trong nc vi tng vn u t trn 15.000 t ng v 12 d n nc ngoi vi tng vn 763 triu USD, thu ht nhiu tp on ln nh VinaCapital, Indochina Capitalu t vo cc sn golf, khch sn, resort cao cp.\r\n<p>Ni n  Nng khng th khng nhc n dng sng Hn th mng v cu Sng Hn - cy cu quay u tin  Vit Nam - nim t ho ca ngi dn thnh ph. Cu Sng Hn l biu tng cho sc sng mi, l kht vng i ln ca thnh ph c xy dng bng s ng gp ca mi ngi dn.</p>\r\n<p>Dng nh mi v p nn th ca ng sng Hn ch c bc l mt cch hon m nht trong khng gian cu Sng Hn lng gi v mt ri. Cu Sng Hn khng ch to thm thun li cho giao thng vn ti, du lch, khi dy tim nng kinh t ca mt vng t rng ln  pha ng thnh ph m cn l mt du n vn ho ca ngi  Nng hm nay gi li mun i con chu mai sau.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div style="padding-bottom: 3px;">\r\n<h2>n, i li bng g?</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src="http://du-lich.chudu24.com/f/d/090217/1-suong-som-ba-na-le-quang-bao1.jpg?c=1&amp;w=450" alt="B  N trong sng" width="450" />\r\n<p>B N trong sng</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\nThnh ph  Nng c sn bay quc t phc v cc ng bay ni a v mt s tuyn quc t nh Thi Lan, Singapore, Hn Quc. Tuy ch l sn bay quy m nh, nhng sn bay quc t  Nng hin nay vn l cng hng khng quan trng nht cho c min Trungv Ty Nguyn.\r\n<p> Nng cn thun tin cho giao thng ng bin vi hai cng ln l cng sng Hn v cng Tin Sa.</p>\r\n<p>ng b n  Nng c hai tuyn ng quc l 1A, con ng huyt mch Bc Nam v Quc l 14B, ni  Nng vi cc tnh Nam Trung B v Ty Nguyn Vit Nam.</p>\r\n<p>Ngoi ra, vi vic a vo s dng hm ng b Hi Vn xuyn qua ni ni lin thnh ph v tnh Tha Thin-Hu, giao thng trn quc l 1A tr nn thun tin hn bao gi ht. Thi gian lu thng c rt ngn, ti nn giao thng vn thng xuyn xy ra trn o Hi Vn c gim thiu.</p>\r\n<p> Nng c h thng taxi, honda phc v vic i li thun tin, h thng  th   Nng cng c ci tin kh p v thun li vi nhiu con ng ln nh Bch ng, in Bin Ph.</p>\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src="http://du-lich.chudu24.com/f/d/090217/deo-haivan.jpg?c=1&amp;w=450" alt="o Hi Vn" width="450" />\r\n<p>o Hi Vn</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n nng cn c tuyn ng st huyt mch Bc - Nam chy dc thnh ph vi tng chiu di khong 30 km. Trn a bn thnh ph hin nay c 5 ga: Ga  Nng, Ga Thanh Kh, Ga Kim Lin, Ga Hi Vn Nam v Ga Ha Chu. Ga  Nng l mt trong nhng ga trng yu trn tuyn ng st Bc - Nam. Tuy nhin, ga nm  trung tm thnh ph nn thng gy ra tc nghn giao thng,  nhim mi trng cng cc t nn x hi.</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div style="padding-bottom: 3px;">\r\n<h2>Mua sm, gi c</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img alt="Cu sng Hn" src="http://du-lich.chudu24.com/f/d/090217/cau_song_han-quang_nam.jpg?c=1&amp;w=450" width="450" />\r\n<p>Cu sng Hn</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\nNgoi nhng im du lch hp dn vn t lu tr thnh th mnh, vi tm im ca 3 di sn vn ho th gii: thnh a M Sn, ph c Hi An v c  Hu,  Nngtr thnh im n v trung chuyn ca khch du lch trong v ngoi nc.\r\n<p>L u mi cng bin, cng hng khng, ng b, ng st nn  Nng lun c mt lng lu khch ln, v th, ngnh kinh doanh khch sn v l hnh pht trin mnh m ti y. Vi cc dch v hon ho v phong cch phc v ng cp quc t, cc khch sn cao cp ca  Nng  tr nn quen thuc i vi gii doanh nhn v khch du lch n  Nng vi gi t 150USD tr ln cho 1 m.</p>\r\n<p>i vi gii du lch bnh dn, cc khch sn hng va y  tin nghi km theo nhiu dch v tin ch rt c a chung vi gi khong 15USD tr ln cho 1 m.</p>\r\n<p>Cc khch sn, nh ngh y  tin nghi, con ngi  Nng nng m, mn khch  v ang to nn mt hnh nh p v mt thnh ph hin i, mt im du lch khng th b qua trong chuyn i ca cc l khch, gi c m thc   Nng cng khng phi l qu t, c bit c nhiu qun hng bn c sn, r nhng li kh ngon.</p>\r\n<p> Nng hin c 2 ch ln nht nm  trung tm thnh ph l ch Hn v ch Cn; cng nhng siu th ln mi m trong vng vi nm tr li y nh siu th  Nng, siu th Metro, i siu th BigC, siu th Intimex, siu th Rosa Bi Th, siu th Nht Linh, siu th i Dng... y l nhng trung tm thng mi ch yu ca  Nng</p>\r\n<p> Nng c nhiu mn n c sn nh m Qung, bnh trng cun tht heo, Bnh xo, tht b thui, bn ch c, bn mm, bnh kh m, nc mm Nam .. c th mua v lm qu biu.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div style="padding-bottom: 3px;">\r\n<h2>Lu  khc</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;Sn phm  m ngh Non nc c bn rt rng ri ti Lng  Non nc (di chn ni Ng Hnh Sn thuc phng Ha Hi, qun Ng Hnh Sn, thnh ph  Nng) v hu nh ti tt c cc khch sn trn a bn thnh ph.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; gm s cn by bn dc ng L Dun t s 123 - 129 hoc ng ba Ni Thnh_ Trng N Vng.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;Khng ch gi gn nhng l hi truyn thng, ngi  Nng  to cho mnh mt l hi mi da trn nn truyn thng l L hi ua thuyn. L hi ny c t chc no ngy quc khnh 2/9 hng nm trn dng sng Hn vi hng chc i ua ca cc a phng trong v ngoi thnh ph.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '', 1, 11, 0, 43, '2011-05-31 05:10:34', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-05-31 05:10:34', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 1, '', '', 0, 0, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(115, 'Hnh khch nh tip vin b pht 5 triu ng', 'hanh-khach-anh-tip-vien-b-pht-5-triu-ng', '', '<div></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2>Hnh khch nh tip vin b pht 5 triu ng</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<h4>Cng v Hng khng min Nam va ra quyt nh x pht hnh chnh 5 triu ng i vi ng Barnes Graeme ngi Australia v  la ht v nh tip vin Vietnam Airlines trn my bay.</h4>\r\n<p>Theo ng hn sng 2/6, hnh khch ngi Australia - ng Barnes Graeme  c mt ti Cng v Hng khng min Nam  k vo bin bn x pht. ng Barnes b xc nh  gy ri trn my bay khi la ht, nh hnh khch v c tip vin.</p>\r\n<table style="width: 1px;" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src="http://vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3b/a2/a9/7f/tiep-vien.jpg" height="319" width="480" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Hnh khch ngi Php vit th xin li lnh o Vietnam Airlines v cu ni a "c bom trong hnh l". nh: <em>Hong H.</em></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>Tha nhn mnh mt kim sot v c hnh vi gy ri, v khch ny  xin li t bay, ng thi chp nhn np pht s tin 5 triu ng theo quy nh. Nh chc trch hng cho rng ng Barnes t thi  rt hp tc, tha nhn li. V khch ny  c tr li h chiu ngay sau bui lm vic.</p>\r\n<p>ng Barnes Graeme tham gia chuyn bay VN 780 ca Vietnam Airlines t Melbourne v TP HCM chiu 1/6. Khi my bay ct cnh c vi gi, ng Barnes Graeme ku au rng v xin chai ru nh  ung cho d ng. Ung ru xong, ng khch ny bt u la ht khin hnh khch ngi bn cnh  ngh tip vin can thip. Th nhng, ng Graeme khng ngng la ht m cn tho ng h eo tay nm vo u hnh khch ngi bn cnh.</p>\r\n<p>Tip vin n khuyn gii cng b nh gy thng tch nh. Nhn thy ng Barnes Graeme  mt kim sot, phi hnh on quyt nh tri tay ng vo gh  tip tc hnh trnh. Khi my bay h cnh, lc lng an ninh sn bay buc phi p gii v khch ny xung.</p>\r\n<p>Cch y hai tun, nh chc trch hng khng cng quyt nh x pht mt hnh khch ngi Php 15 triu ng v cu ni "c bom trong hnh l". V khch ny l ng Mariano Jean Agostini  np pht, ng thi c th xin li gi lnh o Vietnam Airlines.</p>\r\n<p>Theo mt nhn vin an ninh hng khng c hai trng hp hnh khch b pht trn u l ngi nc ngoi. H c  thc v vn  an ton trn my bay nn tun th quyt nh x pht. C 2 v vic trn u c coi l hy hu khi ng Barnes ngi Australia b tc dng ph ca thuc lm cho mt kim sot. Cn Mariano Jean Agostini ngi Php l nhc cng i cng mt ca s ngi Vit. Do thy n ca s ny bun, ng Mariano  by tr cho c ny ngc nhin bng cch ni "c bom trong hnh l". Tnh c, mt n hnh khch khc i qua nghe thy  bo vi phi hnh on.</p>\r\n<strong></strong>', '', 1, 11, 0, 44, '2011-06-04 04:31:03', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-06-04 04:31:03', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 22, '', '', 0, 9, 'robots=\nauthor=');
