(116, 'ng  Lut Cnh tranh b li dng ', 'ng--lut-cnh-tranh-b-li-dng-', '', '<div></div>\r\n<strong>Lin quan n vic hng Hng khng Jetstar Pacific n 170 t ng tin xng ca Cng ty Xut nhp khu hng khng Vit Nam (Vinapco), u tun ny hai bn  t c tha thun v cch x l n v cung ng nhin liu trong thi gian ti. </strong>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Theo , Vinapco ng  khoanh n  Jetstar tr dn theo tin  cam kt vi iu kin phi c bo lnh ca n v ch qun l Tng cng ty u t v Kinh doanh vn nh nc (SCIC) hoc ca t chc tn dng trc thi hn cui l 4-6-2011. Vn  t ra l nu n thi im  m Jetstar vn khng tm c n v ng ra bo lnh v tip tc chy  tr n th cch x l s nh th no cho hp tnh hp l?</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://vemaybaytructuyen.com/images/stories/vietnam-arlines-ecommerce-large.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Trc y, vo nm 2009, Vinapco  tng mt ln ngng cung cp xng cho Jetstar v hng ny vi phm hp ng khi khng thanh ton s tin xng n khong 50 t ng. Th nhng, lc  Vinapco  b Hi ng cnh tranh quc gia x pht hn 3,3 t ng do b quy l li dng v tr c quyn  n phng thay i hoc hy b hp ng  giao kt m khng c l do chnh ng theo khon 3, iu 14, Lut Cnh tranh.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Phi chng vic x pht Vinapco trc y  v ng cho hu chy? Jetstar bit rng, Vinapco khng c php ngng cung cp xng my bay cho mnh nn c v t khng thanh ton tin mua xng? Hnh vi y li c php lut tha nhn th chc chn cc hng hng khng khc cng noi gng Jetstar. iu g s xy ra khi Vinapco b chim dng ht vn lu ng v khng th nhp c xng v cung cp? Vinapco l doanh nghip c quyn trong lnh vc cung ng xng, du cho my bay. iu  hon ton ng trc y hai nm theo quy nh ti iu 12 Lut Cnh tranh.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Song, vn  quan trng hn li l, Vinapco - di gc  l mt php nhn trong kinh doanh - c t mnh to ra th c quyn  khng? Cu tr li l khng. V tr c quyn ca Vinapco hon ton do Nh nc to ra. Nu nh Vinapco l mt cng ty ln  thc hin hnh vi thu tm cc Vinapco khc v tr thnh doanh nghip c quyn th x pht Vinapco l hon ton hp l. Song, Vinapco hin nay khng lm c iu . V vy, pht Vinapco l cha pht ng th phm to ra th c quyn.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Hn na, hin nay  nc ta, cn rt nhiu doanh nghip ang c th c quyn, in hnh l ngnh in lc. Bt k mt h tiu th in no chm thanh ton tin in, th s b thng tay ct in, bt k  l in dng cho sn xut hay sinh hot. X pht Vinapco nh  nu trn, liu Hi ng cnh tranh quc gia c x pht c ngnh in vi mt li tng t hay khng?</p>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;">Ban hnh v a Lut Cnh tranh vo cuc sng, x pht Vinapco  chng minh cho s nghim minh ca php lut l ng. Song,  n lc cn c ch ti x l nhng trng hp li dng quy nh ca Lut Cnh tranh  chy  thanh ton n nh trng hp ca Jetstar.</div>', '', 1, 11, 0, 44, '2011-06-04 04:32:58', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-06-04 04:32:58', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 21, '', '', 0, 24, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(117, 'Rm r m ng bay mi', 'rm-r-m-ng-bay-mi', '', '<div></div>\r\nNgoi vic m rng mng bay trong nc v quc t, cc hng hng khng ca Vit Nam cn tng cng khuyn mi  kch thch nhu cu i li ca hnh khch.\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><strong></strong>\r\n<p>Ch trong vng 3 thng, Hng hng khng Quc gia VN (Vietnam Airlines)  cng b khai trng ti 8 ng bay mi trn trc quc t v ni a, tng gp i so vi cng thi im nm ngoi. Bn cnh , hng cng ti khi ng chng bay  ngng khai thc trc   p ng nhu cu i li ca khch hng.</p>\r\n<table style="width: 1px;" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src="http://vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3b/a2/a9/12/Air-Mekong.jpg" height="325" width="450" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>T 1/6, Air Mekong bt u khai thc ng bay thng TP HCM - Quy Nhn. nh: AMK.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p> chun b cho k hoch m rng mng li bay, hng vn chuyn ny  k mt lot cc hp ng tn dng tr gi nhiu triu la  mua sm my bay v ng c. Tng gim c Phm Ngc Minh ni rng trong vn chuyn hng khng an ton cn phi c u tin hng u. Vic sm mi trang thit b tu bay, mc ch chnh l m bo cc chuyn bay c cht lng.</p>\r\n<p>Mt ngun tin ca Vietnam Airlines tit l khi mt s nc i mt vi tnh hnh khng hong, thit b, my mc c bn ra th trng vi gi r, hng  tn dng c hi  mua sm phc v k hoch m rng mng bay.</p>\r\n<p>Theo k hoch, vo ma thu nm nay, hng khai trng tip ng bay thng xut pht t H Ni, TP HCM i Vng quc Anh. ng thi, tin ti mc tiu c ng bay thng ti th trng s mt - M. Hin Vietnam Airlines c 36 ng bay ni a, 46 ng bay quc t.</p>\r\n<p>D mi tham gia th trng cha c mt nm, song Hng hng khng t nhn Air Mekong cng bt u khng nh c s hin din nht nh ca mnh trn th trng ni a. Ch trong vng 2 thng qua, Air Mekong  tuyn b khai trng n 4 ng bay ni a, xut pht t H Ni hoc TP HCM i Ph Quc, Cn o, Quy Nhn v Pleiku.</p>\r\n<p>Vic lin tc m cc ng bay mi ca Air Mekong cng khng ngoi mc tiu tng th phn cng sm cng tt khi th trng vn cn ca. Hin Air Mekong  m trn 15 ng bay ni a... Trong k hoch ca mnh, hng t tham vng pht trin thm 10 my bay mi trong nm 2011, 14 my bay trong nm 2012, 18 my bay trong nm 2013 v 20 my bay khc na trong nm 2014.</p>\r\n<p>T u nm n nay, Jetstar Pacific Airlines l hng hng khng duy nht khng khai trng thm ng bay mi no. Tuy nhin, trong giai on cao im nht hng  ti khi ng li ng bay H Ni - Nha Trang v thc hin khai thc trong khong 5 thng. Sau ngy 29/10 ti, hng s c nh gi hiu qu ng bay ny  a ra quyt nh c khai thc lu di ng bay ny hay khng. Mt i din ca Jetstar Pacific chia s v l gi r nn hng phi cn nhc rt k cc khon chi ph  m gi v lun thp nht th trng.</p>\r\n<p>Cc Hng khng VN d bo, nm 2011, cc hng vn chuyn s t khong 17,5 triu lt khch, tng gn 21% so vi nm 2010. Do vy, vic m cc ng bay mi ca cc hng hng khng c coi l bc i n u th trng khi nhu cu i li bng ng hng khng c d bo l s pht trin mnh trong thi gian ti.</p>\r\n<p>Ngoi vic m rng mng li ng bay, cc hng hng khng cng lin tc tung ra cc chnh sch khuyn mi, gim gi v.</p>\r\n<div>Theo , c mi ln khai trng ng bay mi khng ch Vietnam Airlines m hng t nhn Air Mekong cng tung ra chiu thc khuyn mi gim gi v t 30% n 50%. Thm ch, c thi im, nh bay cn mnh tay gim gi ti 70%, ng thi p dng chiu thc min ph cho mt ngi cng bay. Jetstar Pacific duy tr chnh sch bn v gi r vo th 6 hng tun. ng thi nh k hng thng, hng cng a ra cc t gim gi kh mnh tay, p dng cho cc hnh khc c lch trnh i li xa ngy.</div>\r\n<div align="right">Theo Vnexpress</div>\r\n</div>', '', 1, 11, 0, 44, '2011-06-04 04:35:17', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-06-04 04:35:17', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 20, '', '', 0, 22, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(118, 'Air Mekong khai trng ng bay TP H Ch Minh - Quy Nhn - TP H Ch Minh.', 'air-mekong-khai-trng-ng-bay-tp-h-chi-minh-quy-nhn-tp-h-chi-minh', '', '<div></div>\r\nNgy 1/6/2011, ti sn bay Ph Ct, UBND tnh Bnh nh v Cng ty CP Hng khng Mekong (Air Mekong)  phi hp t chc L khai trng ng bay TP. H Ch Minh - Quy Nhn  TP. H Ch Minh ca Air Mekong.\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><strong></strong>\r\n<p>Tham d bui l c Tng Kim Ton Nh Nc Vng nh Hu, B Th Tnh y Bnh nh Nguyn Vn Thin, i din cc Tng cng ty Cng Hng Khng Min Bc, Trung, Nam, Ngn hng BIDV cng cc s ban ngnh tnh Bnh nh, cc c quan bo ch v cc doanh nghip trn a bn Tnh.</p>\r\n<p>ng bay TP. H Ch Minh - Quy Nhn - TP. H Ch Minh ca Air Mekong c khai thc hng ngy vi gi bay thun tin: xut pht t TP. H Ch Minh lc 8 gi 40, xut pht t sn bay Ph Ct, Bnh nh lc 10 gi 15, thi gian bay l 1 gi. Air Mekong  chnh thc trin khai bn v t ngy 15/05/2011 trn ton h thng vi 12 mc gi cho 2 hng dch v hng Deluxe v hng ph thng. c bit gi hng ph thng thp nht l 650.000 VN (cha bao gm ph v thu VAT).</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img alt="Air Mekong khai trng ng bay TP H Ch Minh - Quy Nhn - TP H Ch Minh, Du lch, " src="http://24hcm02.24hstatic.com:8008/upload/2-2011/images/2011-06-02/1306980213-2.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p>Trong hai chuyn bay ca ngy u tin, cng vi khch mi ca Air Mekong, c bit c s tham gia ca hn 50 thiu nhi di 12 tui c hng min hon ton tin v my bay. y l mn qu y  ngha nhn ngy Quc t Thiu nhi dnh cho cc chu. Khi c hi cm gic ln th 2 c i my bay, trong  ln ny c i Air Mekong t TP. H Ch Minh ra Quy Nhn, chu T Quc Long 11 tui chia s cm gic v s m i ca tu bay v khng kh m m ca gia nh chu khi 4 ngi c ngi c mt hng gh trn my bay. Long thch nht cm gic ct cnh nhanh ca my bay c in hnh su u .</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img alt="Air Mekong khai trng ng bay TP H Ch Minh - Quy Nhn - TP H Ch Minh, Du lch, " src="http://24hcm02.24hstatic.com:8008/upload/2-2011/images/2011-06-02/1306980213-1.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p>Cng trong dp ny, Air Mekong phi hp vi Ngn hng BIDV v khu ngh dng 4 sao Royal Resort ti Quy Nhn p dng chng trnh khuyn mi ln cho khch i ngh ti Quy Nhn. Theo , t ngy 01/06/2011 n 31/07/2011, bt k hnh khch no i my bay ca Air Mekong t TP. H Ch Minh n Quy Nhn lm th tc nhn phng ti Royal Resort s c gim gi 50% tin phng. Ngoi ra, nu nhm t 5 phng s c min ph xe n mt chiu v nhm t 10 phng c min ph xe 2 chiu a, n sn bay n thnh ph Quy Nhn.  nhn cc u i ny khch cn xut trnh th ln my bay Air Mekong cng ngy lm th tc nhn phng ti Royal Resort.</p>\r\n<p>Mc tiu ca Air Mekong l mang li cho khch hng cc chuyn bay An ton  <em><strong>Tin cy  Tin ch  ng gi.</strong></em></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<hr color="maroon" width="85%" />', '', 1, 11, 0, 44, '2011-06-04 04:36:15', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-06-04 04:36:15', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 19, '', '', 0, 12, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(119, 'Jetstar Pacific pht trin i my bay ln 15 chic', 'jetstar-pacific-phat-trin-i-may-bay-len-15-chic', '', '<div></div>\r\nHng hng khng gi r Jetstar Pacific cho bit nm 2014, hng s pht trin i my bay hin c ln 15 chic, bao gm ton b my bay Airbus A320, nhm tit kim chi ph bo dng, tit kim nhin liu v nng cao h s khai thc tu bay v cht lng phc v hnh khch.\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><strong></strong>\r\n<div>\r\n<div id="ctl00_mContent_pnImgCaption">\r\n<div>\r\n<div id="NeedChangeContent"></div>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img id="ctl00_mContent_imgImage" src="http://www.vietnamplus.vn/avatar.aspx?ID=94347&amp;at=0&amp;ts=300&amp;lm=634425187682870000" /></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div align="left"><br /> chun b cho k hoch pht trin i my bay ny, hng  tin hnh tuyn dng 17 k s bo dng my bay ngi Vit Nam. Va qua, 17 k s ny  c Cc Hng khng Vit Nam cp Giy php hnh ngh Cat B (VAR66 Licences), trong  3 k s  hon thnh xut sc k thi CRS (Certificate Release to Service - Chng ch xc nhn phc v) di s st hch kht khe ca cc chuyn gia nc ngoi  chnh thc m nhn vai tr k s trnh  Cat B ti Jetstar Pacific.\r\n<p>Hin nay, Jetstar Pacific c 22 k s ngi nc ngoi v 3 k s Vit Nam m nhim vai tr k s Cat B; 14 k s ngi Vit Nam sau khi tch ly  S kinh nghim thc t (Experience Book) s tham gia cc k thi CRS  m nhim vai tr k s Cat B ti Hng trong thi gian t 1-2 nm ti.</p>\r\n<p>Theo k hoch, n nm 2014, Jetstar Pacific s c 50% i ng k s l ngi Vit Nam,  nng lc m nhim cc v tr quan trng trong cng tc bo dng my bay.</p>\r\n<p>Cng vi vic nng cp trnh  cho cc k s, th my ngi Vit Nam, chng trnh ni a ha i ng phi cng ca Jetstar Pacific  bc u thu c nhng kt qu tch cc. Hin ti,  c 3 phi cng Vit Nam lm vic cho Jetstar Pacific. D kin, t nay n ht nm 2011, s c khong 10 phi cng Vit Nam do hng u t v c i hc  nc ngoi tr v phc v trn cc chuyn bay ca Jetstar Pacific.</p>\r\n<p>Jetstar Pacific hin ang khai thc i my bay 7 chic phn lc tm trung gm 2 chng loi Boeing 737-400 v Airbus A320, vi cc ng bay gia Thnh ph H Ch Minh-H Ni,  Nng, Hu, Vinh, Hi Phng, v gia H Ni- Nng./.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div align="right">(Theo TTXVN/Vietnam+)</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<hr color="maroon" width="85%" />', '', 1, 11, 0, 44, '2011-06-04 04:36:58', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-06-04 04:36:58', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 18, '', '', 0, 17, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(120, 'Vinapco tip tc thc n Jetstar Pacific', 'vinapco-tip-tc-thuc-n-jetstar-pacific', '', '<div></div>\r\nHm nay, hp ng cung cp nhin liu bay k gia Jetstar Pacific v Vinapco ht hn km theo khon n ln ti 173 t ng. Vinapco yu cu Jetstar Pacific phi c n v bo lnh nu mun tip tc mua xng.\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><strong></strong>\r\n<p>Cng ty TNHH Mt thnh vin - Vinapco cho bit tnh n chiu 31/5, Hng gi r Jetstar Pacific vn cha thanh ton khon n trn 173 t ng tin xng du. Trong khi , 31/5 l ngy cui hp ng cung cp nhin liu bay k kt gia 2 bn ht hiu lc. Sau thi im ny, cng dn cc khon li, s n s nhiu hn na.</p>\r\n<table style="width: 1px;" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src="http://vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3b/a2/a7/f8/jets.jpg" height="343" width="450" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Jetstar Pacific l hng hng khng gi r u tin ca Vit Nam. nh: Hong H.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;Trc , ngy 25/5, Cc Hng khng VN  c cuc hp gia cc bn  gii quyt vn  n nn. C quan ny  ngh Vinapco v Jetstar Pacific tip tc hp tc, thc hin hp ng mua bn xng du. Gim c Vinapco - Trn Hu Phc cho bit ti bui lm vic ny, cng ty cng cam kt tip tc cung cp nhin liu, vi iu kin l Jetstar Pacific phi c bo lnh ngn hng hoc cng ty m SCIC.</p>\r\n<p>Ngoi ra, Vinapco cng chp nhn khoan s n 173 t ng li, vi iu kin l, Jetstar Pacific phi tr li sut ngn hng v c bo lnh ngn hng. "Ti cuc hp, i din hng hng khng chp nhn c 2 iu kin trn. Th nhng hn mt tun tri qua, h vn cha a ra c n v bo lnh", ng Phc ni.</p>\r\n<p>ng Phc cho bit Vinapco a ra thi hn mi n ngy 4/6, Jetstar Pacific phi c bo lnh ngn hng. Trong trng hp hng vn chuyn ny khng p ng c yu cu trn, Vinapco s ngng k hp ng. "Ni l vy, nhng trong tnh hung Jetstar Pacific khng c kh nng thanh ton cc khon n trn, chng ti cng khng bit phi x l th no", ng Phc than th.</p>\r\n<p>Trong khi , Vinapco vn cn mt khon n ng cha i c ca Indochina Airlines, c khong 25 t ng.</p>\r\n<div>Nm 2009, Vinapco <a href="http://vnexpress.net/gl/kinh-doanh/2008/04/3ba00e69/">tng b pht 3,3 t ng</a>, tng ng vi 0,05% doanh thu cng ty. Quyt nh ny c Hi ng Cnh tranh a ra sau ng mt nm Vinapco ngng bn xng cho Hng hng khng Pacific Airlines c nay l Jetstar Pacific Airlines.</div>\r\n<div align="right">Theo Vnexpress</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<hr color="maroon" width="85%" />', '', 1, 11, 0, 44, '2011-06-04 04:37:35', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-06-04 04:37:35', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 17, '', '', 0, 17, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(121, 'Hnh khch b tri tay v nh tip vin Vietnam Airlines', 'hanh-khach-b-troi-tay-vi-anh-tip-vien-vietnam-airlines', '', '<div></div>\r\n<span style="font-size: 12pt;">Mt ngi nc ngoi b tri tay v nh hnh khch ngi bn cnh v tip vin phc v ca Vietnam Airlines trn chuyn bay t Australia v Vit Nam hm nay. </span>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;">\r\n<table style="width: 1px;" align="left" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src="http://vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3b/a2/a8/da/Vietnam-Airlines-250.jpg" alt="Hnh khch gy ri khng phi l chuyn him trong cc chuyn bay ng di." border="1" height="195" width="250" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Hnh khch gy ri khng phi l chuyn him trong cc chuyn bay ng di.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>Theo ngun tin t Vietnam Airlines, hnh khch tn Barnes Graeme, 53 tui, ngi Australia bay t Melbourne v TP HCM chiu nay. Khi my bay ct cnh c vi gi, ng Barnes ku au rng v xin tip vin chai ru nh  ung cho d ng.</p>\r\n<p>t pht sau , hnh khch ny bt u la ht. N hnh khch ngi gn  bo vi tip vin v  ngh c can thip. Khi tip vin n, yu cu hnh khch gi trt t v ngi vo v tr, ng Barnes tip tc la ht v tho ng h eo tay nm vo u mt n hnh khch ngi Australia c mt gn . Nam tip vin lm nhim v khuyn gii cng b nh, gy thng tch nh.</p>\r\n<p>Theo lnh ca c trng, ng Barnes cng mt s thnh vin trong gia nh c a xung khoang di ca my bay.</p>\r\n<p>Vn theo Vietnam Airlines, do v khch tip tc la li v  trong tnh trng mt kim sot, phi hnh on quyt nh tri tay ngi ny vo gh my bay  tip tc hnh trnh.</p>\r\n<p>Chiu nay, khi my bay h cnh xung sn bay Tn Sn Nht, TP HCM, lc lng an ninh v cng an ca khu ln p gii hnh khch ny. ng Barnes  k vo bin bn xc nhn hnh vi gy ri. Hnh khch ny cho rng, tc dng ph ca thuc ng kt hp vi ru  khin ng mt kim sot.</p>\r\n<p>Cng v hng khng Tn Sn Nht sau khi gi li h chiu, giy t ty thn  cho php ng Barnes v.</p>\r\n<p>Mt lnh o ca Vietnam Airlines cho hay, chuyn hnh khch ung ru say, la li hoc nh nhau trn chuyn bay vn thng xy ra trn cc chng bay di. Tuy nhin, vic hnh khch mt kim sot n  phi tri tay li l chuyn hn hu xy ra trn cc chuyn bay ca hng.</p>\r\n<p>Ngy mai, nh chc trch hng khng s lm vic vi hnh khch  ra quyt nh x pht.</p>\r\n<p align="right"><strong>Hng Anh</strong></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<hr color="maroon" width="85%" />', '', 1, 11, 0, 44, '2011-06-04 04:38:02', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-06-04 04:38:02', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 16, '', '', 0, 21, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(122, 'Jetstar cng b dch v check-in t phc v 100% ', 'jetstar-cong-b-dch-v-check-in-t-phc-v-100-', '', '<div></div>\r\nNgy 30/5, Hng hng khng gi r Jetstar cng b i tin phong trong dch v check-in t phc v 100%, hon thin dch v cung cp th ln my bay qua tin nhn, trm t phc v u tin trn th gii ti cc sn bay ni a txtrylia v New Zealand.\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><strong></strong>\r\n<p>Jetstar ang p dng tiu chun bay mi trong cc dch v chm sc khch hng ti cc sn bay, gip cho vic du lch bng ng hng khng tr nn tin li v t rm r hn. Jetstar hin l hng hng khng c u tin mang li dch v t lm th tc check-in hon chnh ti mng li 18 sn bay ni a vi ba chn la dch v bao gm: Check-in trc tuyn (Web check-in); Trm my t phc v ti sn bay - Self Service Kiosks (hin ang c mt ti tc c cc sn bay); Cung cp th ln my bay qua tin nhn SMS  SMS Boarding Pass (dch v mi ti Jetstar). Nhng dch v trn c p dng song song vi cc phng php check-in truyn thng ti cc quy dch v.</p>\r\n<div style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://tintucimg.vnanet.vn/2011/05/30/17/06/je_w_400.jpg" /></div>\r\n<div align="center">nh: Internet</div>\r\n<p> gip cho qu trnh lm th tc d dng hn na, Jetstar cng va cng b dch v check-in t ng, qua vic cho php hnh khch c th ng k check-in trc v nhn li th ln my bay bng tin nhn SMS hoc bng email 24 ting trc chuyn bay. Thay th tin trnh lm th tc trn gi l mt bc t ph quan trng ca Jetstar, gip nng cao tri nghim du lch cho hnh khch.</p>\r\n<div>Gim c iu hnh Jetstar Group, ng Bruce Buchanan pht biu rng Jetstar  u t vo cc cng ngh dch v t phc v hin i nht v thn thin vi hnh khch  ngy cng nng cao tri nghim ti cc sn bay, duy tr s n nh cc lch bay ng gi  mc cao nht, v t c hiu qu trong vic s dng c s h tng sn bay t tin  gi cho gi v lun r. C khong 75% hnh khch ni a ca Jetstar chn cc dch v t phc v nh l check-in trc tuyn (Web check-in) ti trang web Jetstar.com hoc Trm t phc v (Self Service Kiosks). Thm vo , dch v th nghim cung cp th ln my bay qua tin nhn SMS (SMS Boarding Pass) gn y  gip tng lng hnh khch chn cc dch v t phc v ln thm 10%.</div>\r\n<div align="right">Theo Tintuc</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<hr color="maroon" width="85%" />', '', 1, 11, 0, 44, '2011-06-04 04:39:14', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-06-04 04:39:14', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 15, '', '', 0, 121, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(123, 'Vietnam Airlines i nh ga ti sn bay Frankfurt  PDF.', 'vietnam-airlines-i-nha-ga-ti-san-bay-frankfurt-pdf', '', '<div></div>\r\n<strong>Bt u t 29/5, Vietnam Airlines chuyn sang khai thc ti nh ga T2 thuc sn bay quc t Frankfurt (c), tin nghi hn so vi nh ga T1 ang c khai thc trc . </strong>\r\n<div id="ctl00_mContent_pnAvatar">\r\n<div>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img id="ctl00_mContent_imgImage" src="http://vov.vn/avatar.aspx?ID=175408&amp;at=0&amp;ts=306&amp;lm=634422839665170000" /></p>\r\n<div id="ctl00_mContent_pnImgCaption">\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Sn bay quc t Frankfurt</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Ti nh ga T2 ny, hnh khch s c hng nhng dch v v tin nghi tt hn so vi nh ga T1, nh khu vc lm th tc rng ri v b tr ring tng khu vc cho hng hng khng, tin nghi trang thit b mi, v tr phng ch v ca ln tu bay (boarding) thun tin hn.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Khi c nhu cu ni chuyn gia nh ga T1 v T2, hnh khch c th s dng xe but (Shuttle Bus  10 pht/chuyn) hoc tu tc hnh (SkyLine  thi gian ch tu v thi gian i tu khong 5 pht).</p>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;">Vietnam Airlines hin khai thc cc chuyn bay thng t Vit Nam i c, vi tn sut 7 chuyn/tun, s dng loi my bay thn rng Boeing 777 loi trn 300 gh./.</div>', '', 1, 11, 0, 44, '2011-06-04 04:39:56', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-06-04 04:39:56', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 14, '', '', 0, 119, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(124, 'Vietnam Airlines tng chuyn TP HCM- Singapore ', 'vietnam-airlines-tng-chuyn-tp-hcm-singapore-', '', '<div></div>\r\nNgy 27/5, Vn phng Khu vc min Nam Vietnam Airlines cho bit, nhm p ng nhu cu i li ca hnh khch tuyn TP HCM Singapore v ngc li tng cao, Vietnam Airlines s tng 3 chuyn/tun vo cc ngy th t, th su v ch nht trong thi gian cao im h 2011 t 15/6 n 31/8. T , nng tng s chuyn bay ln 17 chuyn/tun i vi hnh trnh TP HCM Singapore v ngc li.\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><strong></strong>\r\n<div id="ctl00_mContent_pnAvatar">\r\n<div>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img id="ctl00_mContent_imgImage" src="http://vov.vn/avatar.aspx?ID=175248&amp;at=0&amp;ts=306&amp;lm=634421059129830000" /></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Theo  s c thm 3 chuyn/tun vo cc ngy th 4, th 6 v ch Nht</p>\r\n<p align="justify">Ngoi tng chuyn ng bay, Vietnam Airlines cng s m thm ng bay mi H Ni Kuala Lumpur, tng tn sut H Ni Singapore t 16/6 v tng tn sut H Ni  Bangkok t ngy 16/7 sp ti./.</p>\r\n<p>TTXVN</p>\r\n</div>', '', 1, 11, 0, 44, '2011-06-04 04:40:57', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-06-04 04:40:57', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 13, '', '', 0, 134, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(125, 'Vietnam Airlines vay 7 triu USD  mua ng c my bay', 'vietnam-airlines-vay-7-triu-usd--mua-ng-c-may-bay', '', '<div></div>\r\n<strong>Hp ng tn dng tr gi 7 triu la M va c Hng hng khng Quc gia VN (Vietnam Airlines) k kt vi Ocean Bank. Khon tin ny d kin s c s dng  mua ng c d phng cho my bay Airbus A321 </strong>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><strong><br /></strong></div>\r\n<table style="width: 1px;" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src="http://vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3b/a2/a5/bf/may-bay.jpg" height="288" width="420" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Vietnam Airlines d kin s m rng i bay ln n 115 chic vo nm 2015 v 170 chic vo nm 2020. nh:H,A.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>Tng gim c Vietnam Airlines Phm Ngc Minh cho bit, khon u t mua ng c d phng cho my bay s gip hng ch ng trong cc hot ng kinh doanh, khai thc dch v vn chuyn.</p>\r\n<p>Hin Vietnam Airlines l mt trong nhng hng hng khng c i tu bay tr v hin i nht trong khu vc. Hng ang vn hnh trn 80 ng bay ti 20 im n trong nc v 26 im n quc t vi hn 300 chuyn bay mi ngy.</p>\r\n<p>Thi gian qua, Vietnam Airlines  k nhiu hp ng mua mi nhm nng cp i tu bay hin ti, p ng mc tiu pht trin v m rng mng ng bay trong nc cng nh quc t.</p>\r\n<div>Vietnam Airlines d kin s m rng i bay ln n 115 chic vo nm 2015 v 170 chic vo nm 2020.</div>', '', 1, 11, 0, 44, '2011-06-04 04:42:14', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-06-04 04:42:14', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 12, '', '', 0, 134, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(126, 'Vietnam Airlines c ch tch mi', 'vietnam-airlines-co-ch-tch-mi', '', '<div></div>\r\n<strong>ng Phm Vit Thanh, Ph tng gim c Vietnam Airlines s gi v tr Ch tch Hi ng Thnh vin, thay cho ng Nguyn S Hng. </strong>Theo quyt nh s 766 do Th tng k ban hnh ngy 23/5, ng Phm Vit Thanh s m nhn v tr Ch tch Vietnam Airlines k t ngy 1/6 ti.\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;">\r\n<table style="width: 1px;" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src="http://vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3b/a2/a3/27/Vietnam-Airlines.jpg" height="266" width="400" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>ng Phm Vit Thanh s gi v tr Ch tch Hi ng Thnh vin Vietnam Airlines t 1/6. nh: Hong H.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>ng Nguyn S Hng nguyn Ch tch Hi ng qun tr Vietnam Airlines s ngh hu theo ch .</p>\r\n<div>Cng trong ngy 23/5, Th tng cng k quyt nh b nhim nhn s  mt s n v khc nh i Truyn hnh Vit Nam, Tp on Ha cht Vit Nam... Trong  c ng Trn Dng Trnh, Gim c Trung tm Nghin cu ng dng Khoa hc K thut truyn hnh gi chc Ph tng gim c i truyn hnh VN. ng Nguyn Quc Tun, Ch tch Hi ng qun tr gi chc Ch tch Hi ng thnh vin Cng ty TNHH mt thnh vin Tp on Ha cht Vit Nam.</div>\r\n<div align="right">Theo vnexpress</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<hr color="maroon" width="85%" />', '', 1, 11, 0, 44, '2011-06-04 04:43:02', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-06-04 04:43:02', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 11, '', '', 0, 119, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(127, 'V Jetstar Pacific n xng du: C quan chc nng c  ging ho?  PDF.', 'v-jetstar-pacific-n-xng-du-c-quan-chc-nng-co-y-ging-hoa-pdf', '', '<div></div>\r\n<strong>Lin quan n vn  n qu hn cha thanh ton ca Jestar Pacific, c quan chc nng  c vn bn cho  kin. </strong>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><strong><br /></strong></div>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;">\r\n<div>Theo , Cc Hng khng Vit Nam (B Giao thng Vn ti) v Cc Qun l cnh tranh (B Cng Thng)  chnh thc c cng vn phc p vn bn ca Cng ty TNHH mt thnh vin Xng du Hng khng Vit Nam (Vinapco) lin quan n vic  ngh ngng cp nhin liu cho Jetstar Pacific khi n v ny vn khng tr n theo yu cu.</div>\r\n<div><strong>Thnh ch?</strong></div>\r\n<div><strong><br /></strong></div>\r\n<div>Trong cng vn gi c Vinapco v Jetstar Pacific, Cc Hng khng  ngh Jetstar Pacific khn trng thanh ton cng n cho cng ty ny theo hp ng hai bn  k kt.</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://tamnhin.net/Uploaded/vanthangnguyen/Images/thang%205/jet.jpg" height="365" width="487" /></div>\r\n<div>V u n ni n n vy?</div>\r\n<div>Trng hp pht sinh vng mc  ngh Cng ty xng du Hng khng v Jetstar Pacific nn m phn, tho thun nhm trnh tnh trng p dng bin php ngng cung cp dch v gy nh hng n vic vn chuyn hnh khch hng khng.</div>\r\n<div>Cc Qun l cnh tranh th c  kin nh sau: vic gii quyt cng n gia hai bn cn thc hin theo quy nh ca php lut hin hnh v cc iu khon v gii quyt tranh chp trong hp ng do cc bn tho thun k kt. Trong trng hp cn thit, doanh nghip c th thc hin quyn khi kin theo quy nh ca php lut  bo v quyn v li ch hp php ca doanh nghip.</div>\r\n<div>Tuy nhin, trong trng hp khi tranh chp pht sinh, hai bn nn tch cc gii &nbsp;quyt trn tinh thn thng lng.</div>\r\n<div>Chiu ngy 23/5, i din Jetstar Pacific cho bit n v ny  c vn bn gi Vinapco  ngh n cui thng 6/2011 s thanh ton khon n ny do hng ang gp mt s kh khn. Trn thc t 170 t ng ch l s tin nhin liu m hng ny s dng trong mt thng m thi.</div>\r\n<div>Quan im ca Vinapco</div>\r\n<div>Gn y nht vo ngy 13/5, Vinapco  tip tc c cng vn yu cu Jetstar Pacific phi thanh ton ton b s tin n qu hn v li chm tr trc ngy 20/5. Theo Vinapco, tnh n ngy 12/5, tng s n qu hn ca Jetstar Pacific vo khong 170 t ng. Tnh n hn cht ngy 20/5, s tin ny ln ti 173 t ng.</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://tamnhin.net/Uploaded/vanthangnguyen/Images/thang%205/jet1.JPG" /></div>\r\n<div>Vinapco bn khon vi khon n 173 t?</div>\r\n<div>Nh cung ng xng du Vinapco ny cn ra ti hu th nu hng hng khng ny cha thanh ton c n v li sut chm tr, n v ny s p dng vic thu tin trc khi tra np nhin liu nh iu khon trong hp ng hai bn  k kt.</div>\r\n<div>Sau , trong vn bn gi Cc Hng khng, Cc Qun l cnh tranh v B Ti chnh hm 17/5, cng ty ny cho rng thi gian qua, Hng hng khng Jetstar Pacific lin tc vi phm iu khon thanh ton tin mua nhin liu Jet A1. Vinapco  nhiu ln c cng vn  ngh hng vn chuyn ny thanh ton cc khon tin n, th nhng Jetstar Pacific khng c phn hi. Vinapco cho rng vic n s tin ln nh vy  trc tip uy hip n an ton vn ca cng ty.</div>\r\n<div>Do , Vinapco  ngh c quan chc nng cho php cng ty c ngng bn nhin liu cho Jetstar Pacific ti tt c cc sn bay cho n khi hng hng khng ny thc hin y  cc ngha v thanh ton.</div>\r\n<div>Trn thc t y khng phi l ln u tin Jestar Pacific b thc n tin xng du. Nm 2008, Vinapco do khng i n c  n phng ngng cung cp xng du du khin 5.000 hnh khch ca Jestar Pacific b nh hng. Vinapco sau   b tuyn pht 3 t ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<hr color="maroon" width="85%" />', '', 1, 11, 0, 44, '2011-06-04 04:43:48', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-06-04 04:43:48', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 10, '', '', 0, 160, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(128, 'Jetstar Pacific c th b ct nhin liu v n tin xng du', 'jetstar-pacific-co-th-b-ct-nhien-liu-vi-n-tin-xng-du', '', '<div></div>\r\n<strong>Cng ty TNHH mt thnh vin Xng du Hng khng Vit Nam (Vinapco) va ra ti hu th cho Jetstar Pacific v chuyn thanh ton tin mua xng du. </strong>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;">\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://img.news.zing.vn/img/575/t575280.jpg" alt="Jetstar Pacific c th b ct nhin liu v n tin xng du" align="middle" border="0" hspace="0" /></p>\r\n<p>Theo cng vn ca Vinapco, hng Jetstar Pacific lin tc chm thanh ton tin mua nhin liu bay ca Vinapco. Cho n ngy 12/5/2011, tng s tin Jetstar Pacific n Vinapco ln ti khong 170 t ng.</p>\r\n<p>Trong khi Vinapco thng xuyn phi i vay vn  nhp nhin liu bay Jet A1, vic chm thanh ton ca Jetstar khin cho chi ph li vay ca Vinapco tng cao, nh hng n kt qu kinh doanh ca Vinapco, cng vn i n ca Vinapco nu r.</p>\r\n<p>ng ch , Vinapco  ra mt ti hu th cho Jetstar Pacific phi thanh ton tin n, tin pht chm tr trc ngy 20/5/2011. Nu hng hng khng ny khng thc hin, cng ty Vinapco tuyn b s p dng hnh thc thu tin trc khi np nhin liu cho hng bay ny theo hp ng  k gia 2 bn. iu ny ng ngha vi vic, hng Jetstar nu khng tr tin s b ngng cung cp nhin liu bay.</p>\r\n<p>Nm 2009, Vinapco cng  n phng ngng cung cp nhin liu cho Jetstar v cng ty ny  b Hi ng Cnh tranh Quc gia x pht vi s tin trn 3 t ng.</p>\r\n<p>Theo SGTT</p>\r\n</div>', '', 1, 11, 0, 44, '2011-06-04 04:44:45', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-06-04 04:44:45', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 9, '', '', 0, 138, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(129, 'Hnh khch thm nhiu la chn khi mua v Jetstar Pacific  PDF.', 'hanh-khach-them-nhiu-la-chn-khi-mua-ve-jetstar-pacific-pdf', '', '<div></div>\r\n<strong>Bt u t hm nay (17/5), hng hng khng gi r Vit Nam - Jetstar Pacific s thc hin vic chuyn i v m rng h thng gi v, chnh sch thng mi theo phng thc mi. C th: ba loi gi v mi c tn gi Starter, Starter Plus v Starter Max s c s dng v thay th cho 3 loi gi v Jetsaver Light, Jetsaver v Jetflex hin ti ang c p dng. </strong>\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="100%"></td>\r\n<td align="right" width="100%"></td>\r\n<td align="right" width="100%"></td>\r\n<td align="right" width="100%"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<table style="width: 927px; height: 804px;">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="top"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="top">\r\n<div>\r\n<p>Theo , ngoi vic c nhiu mc gi v c phn phi t thp n cao theo m hnh hng khng gi r, hnh khch s bt u la chn chuyn bay vi mc gi c bn thp nht hin c trn h thng (loi v Starter) bao gm ch ngi v 7kg hnh l xch tay  tit kim. Sau , ty nhu cu hnh khch c th ch ng la chn hnh l k gi vi mc cn linh hot 15, 20, 25, 30, 35, 40 kg, hoc c th la chn thm gi dch v gia tng khc km theo  c&nbsp; cc iu kin linh hot nh: c php thay i ngy, c hon v, c la chn ch ngi trn my bay...</p>\r\n<div>\r\n<table align="center" border="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img alt="Giao din trang bn v mi ca " src="http://123.30.188.50/images/stories/2011/05/17/website%20jetstar%201.jpg" align="middle" border="0" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>Giao din mi ca Jetstar Pacific c thit k n gin, tin <br />li hn cho ngi s dng.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Vi chnh sch sn phm mi, mt h s t ch c nhiu khch i cng nhau th mi hnh khch c th la chn dch v hnh l k gi vi cc mc cn khc nhau. Mi hnh khch c chn ti a 40kg hnh l k gi. Trong trng hp khch  mua v vi mc hnh l k gi thp hn 40kg, c th ng k la chn thm s cn (kg) pht sinh theo s cn cn li. Khch ng k hnh l k gi sm s nhn c mc ph r hn so vi ti sn bay.</p>\r\n<p>ng T Hu Thanh - Ph Tng Gim c Thng mi Jetstar Pacific cho bit: "S thay i ny s gip khch hng tip cn thm cch thc mua v mi tit kim hn, st vi nhu cu hn so vi cch mua v trn gi theo kiu truyn thng trc y".</p>\r\n<p>Trong thi gian chuyn i, hnh khch nu c cc pht sinh c th lin lc vi Jetstar Pacific bng qua a ch email: <a href="mailto:ykienkhachhang@jetstarpacific.com.vn">ykienkhachhang@jetstarpacific.com.vn</a>, hoc lin hn vi tng i 19001550 hot ng 24/7  c h tr.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', '', 1, 11, 0, 44, '2011-06-04 04:45:42', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-06-04 04:45:42', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 1, '', '', 0, 138, 'robots=\nauthor=');
