(213, 'Jetstar Pacific tung ra 50.000 v my bay gi r', 'jetstar-pacific-tung-ra-50000-ve-may-bay-gia-re', '', 'Hng hng khng gi r Jetstar  Pacific va chnh thc cng b thc hin chng trnh bn 50.000 v my  bay gi r t 250.000 ng. y l t bn v gi r ln nht ca hng  t u nm 2009.\r\n<div>Thi gian m bn bt u t6h  sng ngy 18/2 v kt thc vo lc 23h59ngy 22/2. V my bay do h  thng my tnh t ng phn phi trn cc chuyn bay c ngy khi hnh  trong giai on t 3/3 n 21/5.<img src="http://www.namhung.us/images/plg_imagesized/210-jpa20111_52ceb.jpg" border="0" alt="Pacific tung 50000 v my bay gi r" title="Pacific tung 50000 ve may bay gia re" width="400" height="300" style="border: 0pt none;" /></div>\r\n<div>c bit, phm vi bn v ln ny c Jetstar Pacific m rng n  tt c cc knh bn, bao gm: Trang web jetstar.com, cc Phng v, i  l ca Jetstar Pacific trn ton quc v Tng i 19001550 (hoc 08.3  9550 550).</div>\r\n<div>Vic thanh ton phi c thc hin ngay ti thi im t ch.</div>\r\n<div>Mc gi m bn trn cc tuyn bay nh sau:</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<table style="text-align: center;" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="193">\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Tuyn bay (gia/v)</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="99">\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Gi t</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="193">\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">TPHCM -  Nng</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">TPHCM - Hu</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">H Ni -  Nng</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="99">\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">250.000 VN</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="193">\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">TPHCM - H Ni</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">TPHCM - Hi Phng</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">TPHCM - Vinh</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">H Ni - Cn Th </span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="99">\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">500.</span><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">000 VN</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>V hn ch bn i vi cc chuyn bay trong thi gian t 28/4- 3/5/2009.</div>\r\n<div>C cu gi v ca Jetstar Pacific bao gm 3 nhm gi chnh, c  phn phi t thp n cao ti tt c cc knh bn  khch hng la  chn.</div>\r\n<div>Nhm gi JetFlex cho php thay i ngy bay min ph, dnh cho  nhng hnh khch cng v c k hoch i li hay thay i; Nhm gi tit  kim JetSaver dnh cho nhng hnh khch n nh k hoch i li  tit  kim chi ph; c bit, vi nhng hnh khch ch mang di 7kg hnh l  xch tay c th la chn loi gi v JetSaver Light  c th tit kim  thm t nht 50.000 ng/chng ni a, 320.000 ng/chng quc t.</div>\r\n<div><span style="font-weight: bold;">Phc Hng</span></div>', '', 1, 6, 0, 59, '2012-02-02 06:31:23', 62, '', '2012-02-02 06:34:43', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-02-02 06:31:23', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 0, 0, 4, '', '', 0, 710, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(214, 'Hng hng khng gi r Tiger Airways thu tm hng bay Indonesia', 'hang-hang-khong-gia-re-tiger-airways-thau-tom-hang-bay-indonesia', '', 'Hng hng khng gi r Tiger Airways  ca Singapore va cho bit  mua li 33% c phn hng hng khng PT  Mandala Airlines ca Indonesia. y l mt phn trong k hoch m rng  hot ng ca hng ti khu vc.<br /> <img src="http://dantri4.vcmedia.vn/L6citQa4PR6kuP9vPSuL/Image/2012/01/Tigerairway122012_583a9.jpg" border="0" alt="Hng khng gi r Tiger Airways thu tm hng bay Indonesia" title="Hang khong gia re Tiger Airways &quot;thau tom&quot; hang bay Indonesia" width="400" height="267" /><br /> y l mt phn trong k hoch m rng hot ng ca hng ti khu vc.  Theo tin t hng AFP,  v thu tm c phn ny s a Tiger Airways tr thnh c ng ln th  hai ca Mandala trong bi cnh hng hng khng ca Indonesia buc phi thc hin cc bin php ti c cu ti chnh. Thng 1 nm ngoi, Mandala b nh bay v nhng khon n khng l.\r\n<p>C ng ln nht hin nay ca Mandala l cng ty u t Saratoga Group c tr s ti Indonesia, nm gi 51,3% c phn. S c phn 15,7% cn li nm trong tay cc c ng khc v ch n ca Mandala.</p>\r\n<p>Tuyn b ca Tiger  Airways cho hay, khon u t vo Mandala s do mt cng ty con thuc  ton quyn s hu ca hng l Roar Aviation nm gi.</p>\r\n<p>Tiger Airways - cng ty  thuc quyn s hu mt phn ca Singapore Airlines - hy vng Mandala s  c cp php bay tr li vo thng ti v cc chuyn bay s c ni  li t thng 4 nm nay.</p>\r\n<p>Mandala Airlines thuc quyn s hu ca qun i Indonesia  cho ti nm 2006, nm m hng ny c chuyn giao cho cc nh u t  thuc khu vc t nhn. Sp ti hng ny s p dng m hnh nh bay gi  r ca Tiger Airways v s dng phi i bao gm cc my bay Airbus A320.</p>\r\n<p>Tuy s lng my bay  trong phi i, cc tuyn bay v im n c th sp ti ca Mandala cha  c cng b, hng ny c mc tiu bay ti cc im n Indonesia v  quc t trong bn knh 5 gi bay.</p>\r\n<p>Ngoi cc tuyn bay ni  a  Australia, Tiger Airways ang tm cch m rng hot ng  khu  vc chu . Nm ngoi, cng ty ny  pht hnh s chng quyn tr gi  126 triu USD  c vn phc v cho k hoch ny, bao gm vic mua my  bay.</p>\r\n<p>Thng v mua c phn  ca Mandala din ra khi chnh Tiger Airways ang phi cht vt ci thin  uy tn  b suy gim. Nm ngoi, nh chc trch Australia  buc Tiger Airways phi nh bay 6 tun v nhng lo ngi v an ton.</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p align="right">Phng Anh</p>', '', 1, 6, 0, 38, '2012-02-02 07:33:04', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-02-02 07:33:04', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 62, '', '', 0, 33, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(215, 'Vinalines thot l ngon mc', 'vinalines-thoat-lo-ngoan-muc', '', 'Nm 2012, Tng Cng ty Hng hi Vit  Nam (Vinalines) t mc tiu tng li nhun cao gp i nm 2011, tuy  nhin iu c ny ch c th t c khi bin khng cn bo t,  th trng vn ti bin m dn ln v kinh t trong nc sm c phc  hi.<a href="http://dantri.com.vn/c76/s76-515840/Thanh-tra-Vinalines-sau-tuyen-bo-lo.htm"><strong> </strong></a>\r\n<div>Trong nm 2011, ngoi c sc v  v chm tu Vinalines Queen th nhiu ngi  phi ngc nhin trc  vic Vinalines cng b khon li nhun 62 t ng/24.700 t ng doanh  thu c nm. Trong khi trc  vi hm tu bin quc gia Vit Nam nhng 6  thng u nm Vinalines  bo l ti 660 t ng, v vy lnh o mt  cng ty con ca Tng Cng ty 91 ny cn cho rng Vinalines kh c th  thot khi cnh ln u tin thua l sau 15 nm thnh lp.</div>\r\n<div><img src="http://dantri4.vcmedia.vn/zBWMWGSUq5Jhg0bdkuZf/Image/2011/10/VNL1_bf6ed.jpg" border="0" width="400" align="middle" style="margin: 5px;" /></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-family: Tahoma; font-size: 10pt;">Tu Vinalines</span></div>\r\n<p>Vinalines khng a ra bt k l gii no cho vic thot l ngon mc  trong bn bo co tng kt nm 2011 v trin khai kt hoch nm 2012,  nhng nhiu ngi d on rng s cu cnh chc chn khng n t lnh  vc vn ti bin.</p>\r\n<p>L do l tng sn lng vn ti ca i tu Vinalines c t 36,8  triu tn/nm, ch tng 1% so vi thc hin nm 2010, tng 2% vi k  hoch nm 2011. i tu ca ton Tng Cng ty hin t khong 3,4 triu  tn (bao gm c i tu trng ti 795 ngn tn chuyn giao t Vinashin).  Trong s ny, nhiu tu c gi tr ln c u t gn y ang ht sc  cht vt trong vic tm kim ngun hng.</p>\r\n<p>Trao i vi bo gii, ng Trn Thin - Gim c Cng ty Vn ti Bin  ng ni: p lc i vi doanh nghip vn ti bin l rt ln bi vi  mc li sut ln ti 23-24%/nm, vic tr li, gc cho khon vay u t  30 - 40 t ng cho mt tu c 20.000 tn  ngn gn ht doanh thu kinh  doanh tu.  l cha k n vic ngay c cc tu ang c cho thu  hn nh cng b i tc p thu di gi thnh.</p>\r\n<p>Trong khi , tri ngc vi khi vn ti bin, khi cng nm nay li  ng vai tr ch yu trong vic cn bng li nhun cho Vinalines. Lnh  o Vinaline cho bit tng sn lng hng thng qua cng do Vinalines  qun l c t hn 64 triu tn, tng 10% so vi thc hin nm 2010 v  4% so vi k hoch nm 2011.</p>\r\n<div>Mc d tc  tng trng kinh t nm 2011 thp hn so vi nm  2010 nhng hot ng XNK vn t mc tng trng tt trong  c mt s  mt hng nh c ph, cao su, hng dt may, g, thy sn, go, st thp,  my mc thit b,  in t to iu kin thun li  cc cng hon  thnh k hoch v sn lng - i din Vinalines cho hay.</div>\r\n<div><span style="font-weight: bold;">Mc tiu tng gp i li nhun</span></div>\r\n<p>Nm 2012, Vinalines phn u tng doanh thu t 27.200 t ng, tng  10%; tng li nhun t 120 t ng, tng 93% so vi thc hin nm 2011.  Mc li nhun ny ch bng 1/8 nm 2009 nhng l p lc rt ln i vi  Vinalines v th trng vn ti bin vn tim n nhiu kh khn, kinh  t th gii bt n v hin tng tha cung trng ti cha kp iu chnh  cho ph hp nhu cu th trng s tip tc gy sc p ln mc cc vn  ti bin.</p>\r\n<p>Ngoi vic cu cho gi cc vn ti khng tip tc tt gim,  Vinalines cng cn phi mong cho hot ng xut nhp khu trong nc gia  tng  to chn hng n nh cho khi cng bin - u tu ca hot  ng kinh doanh ca Vinalines nm 2012.</p>\r\n<p> trnh phi neo thuc qu ln vo s phc hi ca th trng vn  ti bin, Vinalines   ra mt lot gii php trong  u tin l  vic y nhanh tin  thc hin cc d n u t  a vo khai thc  ng b, to ngun thu nh: Cng Ci Cui G 2 (Tp.Cn Th); Cng Si Gn  - Hip Phc G 1; Cng container quc t Cng Si Gn - SSA, NM sa  cha tu bin Vinalines pha Nam (B Ra - Vng Tu); cng Sn Tr (  Nng); Bn s 2 cng Ba Ngi (Khnh Ho); cng Nm Cn (C Mau); Bn 2,  3, 4 cng Ci Ln, Cng tng hp nh V, Kho bi container Vinalines  ti Hi Phng</p>\r\n<p>Cng vi , vic thc hin  n sp xp i mi v pht trin doanh  nghip Tng Cng ty giai on 2011 - 2015 sau khi c Th tng Chnh  ph ph duyt cng s l mt nhim v trng tm ca Vinalines.</p>\r\n<p>Mc tiu ca Vinalines trong 6 thng u nm 2012 l hon thnh vic  c cu, sp xp li cc doanh nghip hch ton ph thuc theo hng tinh  gn, chuyn mn ha, ng thi tin hnh cc th tc chuyn i mt s  doanh nghip sang hot ng theo m hnh cng ty c phn v cng ty TNHH  mt thnh vin.</p>\r\n<p align="right"><span style="font-weight: bold;">Qunh Anh</span></p>', '', 1, 6, 0, 38, '2012-02-02 07:39:05', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-02-02 07:39:05', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 61, '', '', 0, 38, 'robots=\nauthor='),
