(217, 'V my bay ni a Vietnam Airlines tng kch trn 20%', 've-may-bay-noi-dia-vietnam-airlines-tang-kich-tran-20', '', 'Hng hng khng Quc gia Vit Nam  (Vietnam Airlines) cho bit s iu chnh gi v my bay ni a bt u  t 15/12 ti y. Theo , mc tng ti a so vi gi hin ti ca hng  ny i vi hng ph thng l 20% v hng thng gia l 5%.<a href="http://dantri.com.vn/c76/s76-543453/Ve-may-bay-noi-dia-sap-tang-len-muc-cao-nhat-5-trieu-dongluot.htm"><strong> </strong></a>\r\n<div><img src="http://dantri4.vcmedia.vn/zBWMWGSUq5Jhg0bdkuZf/Image/2011/10/veVNA1_532f8.jpg" border="0" width="400" align="middle" style="margin: 5px;" /></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-family: Tahoma; font-size: 10pt;">Gi v my bay ni a ca Vietnam Airlines bt u tng t 15/12</span></div>\r\n<div>Nh vy, ch t ngy sau khi cc B, ngnh thng nht tng gi trn  v my bay, Vietnam Airlines l hng hng khng u tin cng b mc  tng c xy dng trn c s khung gi cc vn chuyn chia theo gii  hn 5 c ly ng bay ni a.</div>\r\n<p>Trong , ng bay trc c nhu cu i li cao gia TP.HCM v H Ni,   Nng, Vietnam Airlines p dng mc tng gi ti a 15%; trn ng  bay n cc a phng c c ly ngn c th linh hot s dng cc phng  tin giao thng khc p dng mc tng ti a 20%.</p>\r\n<p>Tuy nhin, Vietnam Airlines cho bit s tip tc thc hin chnh sch  a dng ha gi v, m rng di gi nhm p ng nhu cu a dng ca  khch hng. Bn cnh mc gi trn theo quy nh ca B Ti chnh,  Vietnam Airlines cn xy dng nhng mc gi mang tnh cnh tranh, thp  hn gi trn n hn 50%, v vy hnh khch sm c k hoch i cng tc,  du lch hay i vic ring u c th tm mua c cc v my bay khc  nhau vi mc gi hp dn.</p>\r\n<p>C ti 10 mc gi khc nhau trong di gi p dng trn cc ng bay  ni a. V d, trn ng bay H Ni i TP.HCM, chng bay c tn sut  khai thc cao nht, tuy mc gi cao nht hng ph thng p dng l  2.560.000 ng nhng hnh khch c th tm mua c nhiu loi v khc  nhau vi mc gi thp nht l 1.050.000 ng (ch bng 41% so vi mc  gi cao nht) ty thuc vo thi im mua v v thc hin hnh trnh.</p>\r\n<p>Vic p dng khung gi trn mi cho php Vietnam Airlines tng bc  xy dng gi v ni a trn c s cung cu ca th trng (gim gi v  khi nhu cu i li thp v ngc li), p ng tt hn nhu cu i li  ngy cng a dng ca nhiu i tng khch hng - i din Vietnam  Airlines cho hay.</p>\r\n<p align="right"><span style="font-weight: bold;">Qunh Anh</span></p>', '', 1, 6, 0, 38, '2012-02-02 07:54:28', 64, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-02-02 07:54:28', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 60, '', '', 0, 40, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(218, 'V my bay ni a sp tng ln mc cao nht 5 triu ng/lt', 've-may-bay-noi-dia-sap-tang-len-muc-cao-nhat-5-trieu-dong-luot', '', '<div style="margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font: normal normal 700 19px/23px ''Times New Roman''; color: #004175; background-color: #ffffff; padding: 0px;"><span style="color: #5f5f5f;">Thng tin t B GTVT cho bit, cc ngnh lin quan va thng nht tng gi v my bay hng ph thng ni a. Mc gi cao nht trn chng bay ni a di nht l H Ni - Ph Quc s tng ln trn 5 triu ng/lt ( bao gm thu v ph ph).</span></div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 15px; margin-right: 10px; margin-bottom: 3%; margin-left: 0px; font: normal normal 500 12pt/18px ''Times New Roman''; line-height: 20px !important; font-size: 12pt; background-color: #ffffff; padding: 0px;">\r\n<div style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"><img src="http://dantri4.vcmedia.vn/zBWMWGSUq5Jhg0bdkuZf/Image/2011/11/VNA2011_1e373.jpg" border="0" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;" /><br style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;" /><span style="font-family: Tahoma; font-size: 10pt; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">V my bay ni a tng mc cao nht l 5 triu ng/lt</span></div>\r\n<div style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">Vic tng gi v my bay ny nm trong t tng mc gi trn c Chnh ph ng  v nguyn tc. C th, vi ng bay di 300 km n di 850 km, gi trn khong 2,5 triu ng; t 500 km n di 850 km l 2,55 triu ng; t 850 km n di 1.000 km l 3 triu ng.</div>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 3%; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 3%; margin-left: 0px; font-size: 12pt; padding: 0px;">ng bay ng khch nht hin nay H Ni - TPHCM (t 1.000 km n di 1.280 km) gi trn cha c thu l 3,84 triu ng (c thu hn 4 triu ng); ng bay xa nht H Ni - Ph Quc (t trn 1.280 Km) mc trn cha thu 4,725 triu ng. y l mc tng kh cao so vi hin nay.</p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 3%; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 3%; margin-left: 0px; font-size: 12pt; padding: 0px;">Nhiu kh nng cao gi v mi ny s chnh thc c p dng t t cao im i li Tt Nguyn n ti y. Ring gi v bn hng thng gia khng b kim sot nn c th tng gim theo nhu cu.</p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 3%; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 3%; margin-left: 0px; font-size: 12pt; padding: 0px;">Trao i vi PV<span style="font-style: italic; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">Dn tr</span> , B trng B GTVT inh La Thng cho bit: Vic tng gi trn v my bay c nh hng theo c ch th trng, tuy nhin ch nh hng  1 mc  va phi  lm sao duy tr c mc tiu kim ch lm pht v m bo thc y pht trin. Cn nu th theo th trng m tng gi cao qu th s khng duy tr c mc tiu kim ch lm pht v dn ti suy thoi, v th phi hi ha v mc tng gi v.</p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 3%; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 3%; margin-left: 0px; font-size: 12pt; padding: 0px;">c bit, vi khung gi trn v my bay c, cc doanh nghip vn ti hng khng thu khng  b chi dn ti thua l v ngng bay (Indochina Airlines) hoc ct gim my bay.</p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 3%; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 3%; margin-left: 0px; font-size: 12pt; padding: 0px;" align="right"><span style="font-weight: bold; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">Qunh Anh</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />', '', 1, 6, 0, 38, '2012-02-02 08:05:23', 64, '', '2012-02-02 08:09:23', 64, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-02-02 08:05:23', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 2, 0, 59, '', '', 0, 40, 'robots=\nauthor=');
