(219, 'Ngi cao tui c gim 15% gi v my bay', 'nguoi-cao-tuoi-duoc-gian-15-gia-ve-may-bay', '', 'Tng Cng ty Hng khng Vit Nam (Vietnam Airlines) cho bit s gim 15% gi v my bay ni a cho nhng hnh khch t 60 tui tr ln bt u t hm nay (15/8).<br />Theo , ng vi mc trn gi v my chng di 300 km c gi 863,636, ngi cao tui c gim cn 734,091/ngi/lt; t 300km n di 500 km gi v 1,100,000 gim cn 935,000; t 500 km n di 850 km gi 1,481,818 gim cn 1,259,545;<br /><br />Chng bay t 850 km n di 1.000 km l 1,909,091 th v dnh cho ngi cao tui l 1,622,727; t 1.000 km n di 1.280 km gi 2,227,273 gim cn 1,893,182; t 1.280 km tr ln c gi 2,727,273 gim 2,318,182 cho ngi cao tui.<br /><br />Khi mua v, khch hng cn xut trnh chng minh th nhn dn hoc cc giy t tng t chng minh l cng dn Vit Nam t  60 tui tr ln. Chnh sch ny ch p dng khi xut v ti cc phng v ca Vietnam Airlines trn ton quc.<br /><br />c bit, chnh sch gim gi v my bay cho ngi cao tui c thc hin nhm hng ng ch trng ca Chnh ph v vic phng dng, chm sc ngi cao tui Vit Nam.\r\n<div style="margin-top: 15px; margin-right: 10px; margin-bottom: 3%; margin-left: 0px; font: normal normal 500 12pt/18px ''Times New Roman''; color: #000000; line-height: 20px !important; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 12pt; padding: 0px;">\r\n<p style="margin-top: 3%; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 3%; margin-left: 0px; font-size: 12pt; padding: 0px;" align="right"><span style="font-weight: bold; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">Qunh Anh</span></p>\r\n</div>', '', 0, 6, 0, 38, '2012-02-02 08:07:47', 64, '', '2012-02-02 09:59:32', 64, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-02-02 08:07:47', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 3, 0, 58, '', '', 0, 3, 'robots=\nauthor='),
