443.jpg" border="0" alt="Cch mi mua v my bay gi r ti Vit Nam " /></span></div>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 13px;">Chia  s vi bo ch, ng T Hu Thanh - Ph Tng Gim c Thng mi Jetstar  Pacific cho bit: S thay i ny s gip khch hng tip cn thm  cch thc mua v mi tit kim hn, st vi nhu cu hn so vi cch mua  v trn gi theo kiu truyn thng trc y."<br /><br />"Chng ti k</span> vng<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 13px;"> s i mi sn phm ny s tip tc gp phn tit kim chi ph i li cho khch hng v x hi" - ng Thanh ni. <br /><br />Jetstar  Pacific cng khuyn co hnh khch nn tm hiu k iu kin ca mi  loi sn phm  c la chn ph hp v tit kim nht theo nhu cu ca  mnh. Trong th</span>i gian<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 13px;"> chuyn i, nu c cc pht sinh, hnh khch c th lin lc vi  Jetstar Pacific qua a ch email ykienkhachhang@jetstarpacific.com.vn,  hoc lin hn vi tng i 19001550 hot ng 24/7  c h tr. <br /><br />Theo ng Thanh, i vi nhng hnh khch  mua v s vn c bo m cc quyn li v iu kin v nh trc y. </span></p>\r\n<div style="text-align: right;"><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 13px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 13px;">Nguyn Phan </span></strong></span></div>\r\n</div>', '', 1, 6, 0, 59, '2012-02-02 12:12:10', 62, '', '2012-02-02 12:15:48', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-02-02 12:12:10', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 0, 0, 2, '', '', 0, 748, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(231, 'Ngi Vit Nam ti Nht Ban c tr gi v my bay trc tip', 'nguoi-viet-nam-tai-nhat-ban-duoc-tro-gia-ve-may-bay-truc-tiep', '', 'Ngi Vit Nam ti Nht Bn mun hi hng c th trc tip mua v gim gi 50% ti cc i l v vn phng ca Tng Cng ty Hng khng Vit Nam (Vietnam Airlines) hoc i s qun Vit Nam ti Nht Bn.<br /><img src="http://image.tin247.com/dantri/110322121056-589-16.jpg" border="0" alt="Ngi Vit Nam ti Nht Ban c tr gi v my bay trc tip" title="nguoi viet nam tai nhat ban duoc tro gia ve may bay truc tiep" width="450" height="310" /><br />Ngi Vit Nam ti Nht Ban c tr gi v my bay trc tip<br />Vietnam Airlines m rng chnh sch v gim gi 50% cho ngi Vit Nam ti Nht Bn<br /> <br />Trc , do vic mua v my bay ti Nht Bn gp nhiu kh khn nn Vietnam Airlines  c chnh sch gi c bit cho phep khach hang tai Vit Nam mua ve cho ngi thn (la cng dn Vit Nam) tai Nht Ban v nc trn cac hanh trinh t Tokyo, Osaka, Nagoya v Fukuoka v Ha Ni hoc TPHCM.<br /><br />Tuy nhin, hin Vietnam Airlines m rng chnh sch gi c bit ny, to iu kin thun li  cng dn Vit Nam ti Nht Bn c th mua v theo mc gi ny ti cc Vn phng ca Hng  bn thnh ph trn hoc ng k thng qua i s qun Vit Nam  Tokyo.<br /><br />Do yu cu v mt th tc, thi gian trin khai gp v cc yu t k thut lin quan, mc gi h tr c bit ny khng p dng trn website ca Vietnam Airlines v khng trin khai cho h thng i l.<br /><br /> nh gi chnh xc nhu cu thc t v xy dng phng n phc v ti u, Vietnam Airlines khuyn ngh khch hng mua v trc tip ti cc phng v v vn phng ca hng ti Vit Nam v Nht Bn.<br /><br />Hnh khch mun bit nhng thng tin chi tit c th lin h:<br /><br />- Ti Vit Nam: 84-4-38320 320 (H Ni), +84-8-38320 320 (TPHCM), +84-511 3 832 320 ( Nng)<br /><br />- Ti Nht Ban: +81-335081481 (Tokyo), +81-647080900 (Osaka), +81-924730500 (Fukuoka), +81-525835171 (Nagoya).<br /><br />\r\n<div style="text-align: right;"><strong>Qunh Anh</strong></div>', '', 1, 6, 0, 38, '2012-02-02 12:17:04', 62, '', '2012-02-02 12:19:17', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-02-02 12:17:04', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'sho