(239, 'Kim tra khn cp v my bay Boeing 737 ti Vit Nam', 'kiem-tra-khan-cap-vo-may-bay-boeing-737-tai-viet-nam', '', 'Cc Hng khng Lin bang M (FAA) va gi ch lnh khn cp cho Cc Hng khng Vit Nam yu cu kim tra v cu trc ca loi my bay Boeing 737-300, 737-400 v 737-500, trong  c my bay ca hng hng khng Jetstar Pacific ang khai thc.<br /><br />Ch lnh ca FAA va a ra l yu cu bt buc i vi cc loi my bay c ng k quc tch M (quc gia ch to) v c khuyn co p dng i vi cc quc gia khai thc phi kim tra k thut my bay t pha ngoi v, c bit ti cc cht c inh tn kt ni gia cc b phn ca thn my bay.<br />Ti Vit Nam, Jestar Pacific l hng hng khng duy nht ang khai thc loi my bay Boeing 737 vi 5 chic Boeing 737 - 400 c sn xut t nhng nm 1992 - 1996.<br /> <img src="http://image.tin247.com/dantri/110407114854-920-998.jpg" border="0" alt="Kim tra khn cp v my bay Boeing 737 ti Vit Nam" title="Kim tra khn cp v my bay Boeing 737 ti Vit Nam" width="450" height="594" /><br />Kim tra khn cp v my bay Boeing 737 ti Vit Nam<br />My bay ca Jestar Pacific phi kim tra cu trc theo yu cu ca FAA<br /><br />i din Cc Hng khng Vit Nam cho bit: Chng ti  gi vn bn  ngh Jetstar Pacific phi tun th ch lnh khn cp ca FAA theo ng thi hn 5 ngy m FAA yu cu.<br /><br />Vic kim tra cu trc c thc hin bng thit b chuyn dng kim tra bng sng siu m nn khng gy ph hu. Trng hp pht hin my bay c hin tng bt thng s phi bo co ngay vi FAA  c hng dn cch kim tra k thut t bn trong.<br /><br />Ngun tin t Jestar Pacific, sng nay 7/4, hng ny ang kim tra v ca 2 my bay theo yu cu t Cc Hng khng Vit Nam v FAA.<br /><br />My bay ca chng ti lun c bo dng v kim tra m bo an ton bay, nhng quy nh ca hng khng th gii l khi c khuyn co th cc hng u phi tun th. Chng ti lun chp hnh y  quy nh ngnh hng khng - i din Jestar Pacific cho bit.<br /><br />Hin cc nh ch to my bay loi Airbus, ATR, Fokker cha c yu cu kim tra nn i bay ny ca cc hng hng khng Vit Nam vn ch thc hin bo dng, sa cha nh bnh thng.<br /><br />Trc , my bay Boeing 737 - 300 ca cc hng hng khng M lin tip phi h cnh khn cp do gp phi cc s c lin quan n cu trc my bay.  trnh nhng trng hp tng t xy ra, Cc Hng khng Vit Nam  xc tin xy dng hin k hoch tng cng vic kim tra t xut v an ton bay ca cc hng hng khng ni a.<br /><br />Qunh Anh', '', 1, 6, 0, 38, '2012-02-02 12:41:49', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-02-02 12:41:49', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 39, '', '', 0, 38, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(240, 'Vit Nam s kim tra t xut  an ton ca my bay', 'viet-nam-se-kiem-tra-dot-xuat-do-an-toan-cua-may-bay', '', 'Lin quan n cc s c mt an ton va xy ra vi my bay Boeing 737 - 300 ca hng khng M, Cc Hng khng Vit Nam s tin hnh r sot ton b my bay v kim tra t xut v an ton bay ca tt c cc hng hng khng Vit Nam.<br /><br />y c cho l nhng ng thi mi nht ca hng khng Vit Nam vi cc bin php d phng nhm gii quyt nhng vn  bt thng v an ton bay v trnh nhng s c nh  xy ra vi my bay Boeing 737 - 300 ca M.<br /> <img src="http://image.tin247.com/dantri/110405220927-121-656.jpg" border="0" alt="Vit Nam s kim tra t xut  an ton ca my bay" title="Vit Nam s kim tra t xut  an ton ca my bay" width="450" height="297" /><br />S kim tra t xut  an ton ca my bay Vit Nam<br />Vic kim tra cc my bay s c thc hin theo yu cu k thut c th ca c quan chuyn mn<br /><br />ng Li Xun Thanh - Ph Cc trng Cc Hng khng Vit Nam cho hay: Cc cha gi thng bo ti cc hng hng khng Vit Nam nhng s tng cng kim tra t xut v an ton bay. Trc mt, nu c yu cu v kim tra, r sot th s tp trung v vn  bo dng, yu cu bt thng an ton bay.  phc v cho vic kim tra v an ton bay i vi cc my bay ca Vit Nam, Cc ang yu cu c quan chuyn mn l Phng Tiu chun v An ton Bay ra a mt yu cu v tiu chun k thut c th i vi cc hng hng khng ang khai thc cc loi my bay tng t v ban hnh hnh trong mt vi ngy ti y.<br /><br />V  an ton ca cc loi my bay ca Vit Nam ang khai thc, ng Thanh nh gi: Hin cc hng hng khng vn tun th theo ng chng trnh bo dng ca cc nh ch to. T trc n nay my bay ca Vit Nam cha c biu hin g bt thng v v nh my bay  M. Thc t, yu cu k thut ca n v chuyn mn a ra ch l bin php tng cng t xut, vn  quan trng nht l cc hng phi tun th theo yu cu bo dng ca cc nh ch to.<br /><br />Tuy nhin, ng Thanh cho rng: Cc s c lin tip xy ra i vi my bay ca M khin bt k quc gia no cng phi quan tm v soi vo hot ng bay ca quc gia mnh  a ra nhng gii php v cch thc qun l ph hp nhm tht cht vn  an ninh hng khng .<br /><br />c bit, i bay ca cc hng hng khng Vit Nam ang khai thc c khong 100 chic nhng ch c Boeing737-400, khng c my bay loi Boeing 737-300. Tui th chung ca my bay Vit Nam vn cn tr, tui th trung bnh khong 6-7 nm, cao nht l Airbus A320 khong 14 - 15 nm. Vic kim tra ny c th s thc hin i vi ton b cc loi my bay hoc ring my bay Boeing.<br /><br />Trc , ch trong 3 ngy nhng c ti 5 my bay loi Boeing 737 - 300 v Airbus A320ca hng khng M phi h cnh khn cp do my bay b thng l, chp in, chm trn vi chim tri v khi bc ln t bung li.<br /><br />\r\n<div style="text-align: right;"><strong>Qunh Anh</strong></div>', '', 1, 6, 0, 38, '2012-02-02 12:44:01', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-02-02 12:44:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 38, '', '', 0, 36, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(241, '''Gi v my bay c th tng thm 22,7%''', 'gia-ve-may-bay-co-the-tang-them-22', '', 'Cc trng Cc Qun l Gi, B Ti chnh - Nguyn Tin Tha khng nh tng trn gi v my bay l khng th ng v cc hng hng khng ang gp l. Phng n gi  c cn nhc vi mc tng d kin l 22,7%.<br /><br />- Va qua, cc hng hng khng   ngh iu chnh gi trn v my bay, vi nhim v l c quan thm nh, Cc Qun l Gi c quan im g?<br /><br />- Hin ti, tt c cc hng hng khng u c vn bn  ngh iu chnh trn ti a gi v my bay trn trc ni a. Trong , c hng  ngh iu chnh tng trn 20%, c hng  ngh tng 40-50%. Chng ti cho rng, vic cc hng hng khng  ngh tng gi v l ph hp vi tnh hnh thc t. Vn  l c quan chc nng s iu chnh  mc tng bao nhiu v thi im no p dng. Ci ny ang c chng ti cn nhc k.<br /><img src="http://image.tin247.com/vnexpress/110402124735-184-206.jpg" border="0" alt="ng Nguyn Tin Tha, Cc trng Cc Qun l Gi, B Ti chnh" title="ng Nguyn Tin Tha, Cc trng Cc Qun l Gi, B Ti chnh" width="320" height="490" /><br />ng Nguyn Tin Tha, Cc trng Cc Qun l Gi, B Ti chnh. nh: Nht Minh<br /><br />S d chng ti ng tnh vic tng gi trn v my bay ni a l v trong chi ph cu thnh gi v  c rt nhiu yu t thay i theo hng tng. Chng hn nh cc chi ph tc ng bi t gi chim 71% tng chi ph ca cc hng vn chuyn, nh chi ph nhin liu, thu mua tu bay, sa cha bo dng, i tu my bay, thu phi cng nc ngoi... Va qua, Vit Nam cng iu chnh t gi, tng 9,3% so vi trc. Bn cnh , gi du (chim 36% chi ph ton mng bay) cng tng khong 31%. Ngoi ra, n gi thu tu bay cng tng 1%, cn chi ph i tu tu bay cng tng 28%...<br /><br />- Nguyn tc  tng trn ti a gi v my bay ni a l g, tha ng?<br /><br />- Nguyn tc  chng ti s dng lm cn c tng trn gi v my bay ln ny l tin dn n xa bao cp, b p chi ph sn xut  doanh nghip c li. Ring khung c ly ng bay ngn s c chng ti thc hin m theo l trnh thch hp, tin ti bo m nguyn tc b p chi ph sn xut  cc hng hng khng c th m bo hot ng v kinh doanh bnh thng.<br /><br />i vi cc ng bay c nhiu hng hot ng (t 2 hng tr ln), ngha l  c cnh tranh, trc mt cha b c gi trn th chng ti s ni rng khung.<br /><br />Cc th, chng ta s iu chnh gi trn  b p cc yu t u vo c cho l tng do khch quan, bt kh khng v nm ngoi tm kim sot ca doanh nghip nh gi nhin liu bay, xng du, thu tu bay, phi cng nc ngoi... Cn cc chi ph khc c th tc ng lm tng chi ph vn ti m doanh nghip kim sot c th h phi ch ng tit gim chi ph, m bo n nh (nh chi ph in nc, qun l, nhn cng...).<br /><br />Trn c s , chng ti tnh ton, tng mc tng trn theo t l thch hp cho tng c ly vn chuyn, khong cch ca ng bay. Trong , ng bay ngn s c t l iu chnh cao hn cc ng bay tm trung v tm xa  gim l cho doanh nghip. V khi cn i c chi ph, gim p lc l s khuyn khch c cc hng hng khng tham gia khai thc dch v vn chuyn. y l cc nguyn tc m Cc Qun l Gi, Cc Hng khng VN v V qun l ngnh ca B Giao thng Vn ti thng nht trong cuc hp mi y  bo co ln lnh o cp cao.<br /><br />-  gim p lc l cho doanh nghip, khuyn khch cnh tranh, ti sao chng ta khng b ngay trn gi v my bay nh cc hng hng khng  ngh?<br /><br />- Quan im ca chng ti l s tin ti xa b gi trn i vi cc ng bay  c cnh tranh. Theo , chng ti ch kim sot gi trn i vi cc ng bay cn v th c quyn. Tuy nhin, mc gi trn ny cng phi tha mn nguyn tc m bo b p chi ph vn ti trn tt c cc tuyn bay ni a, to iu kin cho cc hng hng khng khai thc trn tt c cc trc bay. T , to ra s cnh tranh gia cc hng vn chuyn trn th trng ni a. Tuy nhin, mun lm c iu ny, chng ta phi tin hnh sa Lut Hng khng v thc t phi c s cnh tranh thc s trn cc ng bay ny.<br /><br />- Vic tng gi v my bay c xem l khng th ng, vy cc c quan lin b  thng nht mc tng l bao nhiu, tha ng?<br /><br />- Vi nguyn tc trn v cn c vo cc yu t chi ph trong gi thnh vn ti v bin ng ca cc yu t u vo th mc tng bnh qun m chng ti d tnh l 22,7%. Mc tng 22,7% ny c chng ti cn c vo rt nhiu yu t, c cu gi thnh, chi ph u vo ca doanh nghip... Trong , nh hng ca t gi n chi ph vn ti tng 9,2%, chi ph nhin liu 7,5%, lng thu phi cng nc ngoi tng 1,5... v nhiu yu t khc na. Mc tng ny  c cc chuyn gia ca Lin b Ti chnh - Giao thng Vn ti r sot k.<br /><br />Hin nay, B Giao thng Vn ti ang kim tra li ln cui kt qu ca T thm nh  c vn bn gi lnh o B Ti chnh x l theo ng quy nh.<br /><br />Hng Anh', '', 1, 6, 0, 38, '2012-02-02 12:47:10', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-02-02 12:47:10', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 37, '', '', 0, 38, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(242, 'Khng tng gi trn v my bay qu 25%', 'khong-tang-gia-tran-ve-may-bay-qua-25', '', 'Lin b Giao thng vn ti v Ti chnh va c cuc hp xem xt  ngh tng gi trn v my bay ca cc hng hng khng trong nc, theo  gi trn v my bay khng tng qu 25%.<br /><br />ng Trn Ngc Thnh - V trng V Vn ti, B Giao thng vn ti cho bit trn Dn Vit rng, lin b Giao thng vn ti v Ti chnh va c cuc hp xem xt  ngh tng gi trn v my bay ca cc hng hng khng trong nc. Ti cuc hp, cc  kin u nht tr rng, vic tng gi v phi m bo ba tiu ch l quyn li ca ngi dn, bnh n gi c v tho g kh khn cho doanh nghip.<br /><br />Da vo ba tiu ch trn, lin b ang tip tc tnh ton  a ra mt mc tng hp l nht vo cui thng ny. ng Trn Ngc Thnh cng cho hay, mc tng khng c qu cao v khng th theo ng  xut ca mt s doanh nghip l t 25-60% so vi gi hin ti.<br /><img src="http://image.tin247.com/vietnamnet/110328191449-171-553.jpg" border="0" alt="Khng tng gi trn v my bay qu 25%" title="Khng tng gi trn v my bay qu 25%" width="480" height="270" /><br />Khng tng gi trn v my bay qu 25% (nh minh ha. nh Dn Vit)<br /><br />ng Trn Ngc Thnh cng cho hay trn bo Cng an nhn dn rng, trong bi cnh nh nc iu chnh t gi gia USD v VN, gi nhin vt liu v gi dch v ti cng hng khng u tng cao th vic iu chnh gi trn v my bay l hp l v cn thit. Tuy nhin, mc iu chnh c th cn cn nhc  m bo ba tiu ch l quyn li ca ngi dn, bnh n gi c v tho g kh khn cho doanh nghip.<br /><br />Trc , Cc Hng khng Vit Nam v nhiu hng hng khng ni a  gi vn bn  ngh tng gi trn v my bay nhm tho g kh khn cho doanh nghip do bin ng t gi.<br /><br />D kin n cui thng 4, mc gi mi s chnh thc c p dng nu phng n ny c B Ti chnh duyt. Gi cao nht ( bao gm c thu v ph) hin nay i vi chng bay trc H Ni - TP.HCM nm trong c ly 850km tr ln l 2,03 triu ng.<br /><br />Thu Ha (tng hp)', '', 1, 6, 0, 38, '2012-02-02 12:49:21', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-02-02 12:49:21', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\