(246, 'VietJetAir bn 2.000 v my bay gi 10.000 ng', 'vietjetair-ban-2000-ve-may-bay-gia-10000-dong', '', 'T 8h ngy 14/12, hng hng khng gi r VietJetAir s trin khai bn 2.000 v my bay vi gi 10.000 ng mt lt cho chng H Ni - TP HCM hoc ngc li.<br /><br />Chng trnh ny ch p dng cho phng thc mua v trn website ca hng v thanh ton bng th Visa hoc Master Card.<br /><br />Trc , t ngy 5 n 11/12, hng ny  p dng gi v my bay t 100.000 ng trn tuyn H Ni - TP HCM hoc ngc li cho tt c cc chuyn bay ca hng khi hnh t ngy 25/12 n 30/4. i din ca VietJetAir cho bit, tnh n 23h59 pht ngy 11/12 sau khi chng trnh khuyn mi kt thc,  c 2.036 v gi r 100.000 ng c bn.<br /><img src="http://image.tin247.com/vnexpress/111213122500-520-791.jpg" border="0" alt="VietJetAir bn 2.000 v my bay gi 10.000 ng" title="VietJetAir bn 2.000 v my bay gi 10.000 ng" width="480" height="320" /><br />V my bay vi gi 10.000 ng mt lt p dng cho chng H Ni - TP HCM hoc ngc li.<br /><br />S lng v r ca VietJetAir c bn ch yu thng qua website ca hng, mt s qua tng i 1900 1886 v c m t ng ngu nhin trn h thng cho tt c cc ngy trong tun, ty thuc vo tnh trng ca chuyn bay. C ch phn phi v t ng ngu nhin trn h thng  gp phn to c hi bnh ng cho tt c cc khch hng, trnh trng hp cc i l gom v.<br /><br />Theo thng k ca h thng t ch VietJetAir, sau hn 5 gi u tin thc hin chng trnh khuyn mi, 659 v my bay r gi 100.000 ng  c bn. S lng ny tng ln 1.237 v 1.581 v cho 2 ngy v 4 ngy sau .<br /><br /> m bo hiu qu kinh doanh, trn mi chuyn bay ch c mt t l nh s v khuyn mi vi gi c bit thp, hnh khch mua v cng sm th v cng r. Trn mi chuyn bay ca VietJetAir, tt c cc hnh khch u c phc v nh nhau, bt k mua v gi no.<br /><br />VietJetAir l hng hng khng t nhn u tin ca Vit Nam c cp php bay trong nc v quc t, hot ng theo m hnh hng khng gi r. Hng hin khai thc dng tu bay Airbus A320 mi, c trang b gh da cao cp trn 3 trc ng ni a chnh ca Vit Nam l TP HCM,  Nng v H Ni. T gia nm 2012, VietJetAir c k hoch m rng mng ng bay ti cc tnh thnh khc ca Vit Nam v cc im n trong khu vc.<br /><br />K Du