(260, 'Tiger Airways: Hng hng khng gi r ca Singapore', 'tiger-airways-hang-hang-khong-gia-re-cua-singapore', '', 'Tiger Airways l hng hng khng gi r c tr s ti Singapore. Trung tm chnh ca hng l sn bay Singapore Changi.<br />Tiger Airways hp thnh mt t chc cht ch t thng 9/2003, hin nay, y l hng hng khng dn dng vi gi v my bay r ln nht  Singapore. Nm 2006, tng cng s hnh khch ca hng l 1,2 triu, tng 75% so vi nm ngoi.<br />y l hng u tin m cc chuyn bay t sn bay Budget Terminal in Changi nhm tit kim chi ph v c cu chi ph nh hng Ryanair. Mc d phi i mt vi s cnh tranh trong nc, nhng hng vn tp trung m hnh tuyn bay t Singapore c bn knh 5 gi bay.  vt qua s cnh tranh ny, Tiger Airways ang c gng mua li cc hng trong nc  tr thnh hng hng khng ca c chu  trong thi gian ti.<br /> <img src="http://pilot.vn/upload/files//2009/06/23/Tiger%20Airways.jpg" border="0" alt="Tiger Airways: Hng hng khng gi r ca Singapore" title="Tiger Airways: Hng hng khng gi r ca Singapore" width="447" height="284" /><br />Tiger Airways: Hng hng khng gi r ca Singapore<br /><br />Hng  m cc tuyn n n  t thng 10/2007, Malaysia l mc tiu tip theo. Tuy nhin, k hoch thnh lp mt trung tm  Manila (Clack)  b tr hon.<br /><br /><strong>Lch s Tiger Airways</strong><br /><br />Sau khi st nhp vo ngy 12/12/2003, Tiger Airways bt u bn v t ngy 31/8/2004. y l thi im kh khn  hng bc vo nn cng nghip hng khng bi hng phi i mt vi gi nhin liu tng cao, vi th trng cnh tranh khc lit. Tiger Airways cng phi tr chm thu nhin liu nh cc hng khc.<br /><br />i vi mt hng hng khng nhn c s u t nh Singapore Airlines (SIA) th Tiger Airways chn cc im n sao cho khng b trng vi SIA. Trc y, Macao cng l mt im ca SIA tuy nhin n l ca SilkAir, cng ty con ca hng, cho n cui nm 2004. Ba thng sau, Tiger Airways m cc tuyn bay ca ring mnh vo ngy 25/3/2005. Sau khi SilkAir dng dch v bay n Krabi do ng t  vng n  Dng nm 2004, Tiger Airways  m dch v n y vo ngy 7/10/2005.<br /><br />Cui thng 7/2005, hng thng bo bt u hot ng cc tuyn t Macao n Manila (Clack) t ngy 30/10/2005. Nhiu ngi cho rng ng thi ny chng t hng s thit lp mt trung tm th 2 ngoi Singapore.<br /><br />Ngy 21/9/2005, hng a ra bng bo co hot ng ca nm u tin. Trong , tng s hnh khch l 500 ngn ngi vi 5.000 lt bay, s chuyn bay thnh cng t 98.7%, ct cnh thnh cng l 94%, h cnh an ton l 90%. Hng c c 4 chic my bay v m tng cng 9 tuyn bay (4 chuyn ca ring hng) trong sut nm u.<br /><br />Ti thi im ny, hng hy vng n cui nm 2006, tng ln 9 chic Airbus A320, s hnh khch l 3 triu ngi. Hng cng hi vng m thm 6 tuyn bay hoc nhiu hn ch yu l n Trung Quc v n , cc chuyn bay n min Nam Trung Quc bt u vo thng 4 nm ny. Vo ngy 26/3/2006, khi Tiger Airways tr thnh hng u tin m tuyn bay t sn bay Changi, Budget Terminal, hng  dng cc chuyn t Singapore n Swisspop.<br /><br />Theo thng bo vo ngy 21/2/2006, Tiger Airways l hng hng khng gi r u tin c s cho php ca chnh quyn Trung Quc m cc chuyn bay n vi thnh ph pha Nam nh: Hi Khu, Qung Chu, Thm Quyn. Theo lch trnh, chuyn bay u tin n Thm Quyn l vo ngy 15/4, n Hi Khu vo ngy 26/4 v n Qung Chu vo ngy 27/4/2006. V ca cc chuyn ny c bt u bn vo ngy 24/2/2006. Hng nhn nh y l cc tuyn y tim nng, khng y 3 thng s lng chuyn bay n Hi Khu v Qung Chu tng ln ng k. Vy l hy vng ca Teger Airways  thnh hin thc.<br /><br />Thng 6/2006, hng dng cc chuyn bay n  Nng. Ngy 20/7/2006, cc phng tin truyn thng cho bit hng c  nh tng t 15 n 20 tuyn nhm thit lp trung tm th 2 vo cui nm. Mt s vng theo k hoch ca hng l Trung Quc, Nam n , Campuchia v Brunei. Cc k hoch khc ca hng cng c nu ra cng thi gian ny. Hng cho bit t sau khi chuyn Budget Terminal vo thng 3/2006, s hnh khch tng ln 81% trong 3 thng 4-5-6 so vi cng k nm trc.<br /><br />Vo gia nm 2007, k hoch hp tc vi hng hng khng South East Asian tm dng.<br /><br />Hng Tiger bt u dch v bay t Singapore n Perth t ngy 23/3/2007.<br /><br />Hng hng khng gi r Tiger Airway c mt khp chu .<br /><br /><strong>Tiger Airways Australia:</strong><br /><br />Ngy 9/2/2007, Tiger Airways tuyn b chnh thc hng tr thnh hng hng khng gi r ln th 3  c so vi Virgin Blue v Qantas/Jetstar. Tiger Airways Australia s s dng mng li chuyn bay ni a trn ton nc c  m rng phm vi quc t bng cc im l Darwin, Perth, v Melbourne.<br /><br />Ngy 16/3/2007, hng c s chp thun ca Chnh ph c thnh lp cng ty con mi v Tiger Airways Australia Pty Ltd. Tiger Airways Australia bt u hot ng t ngy 23/11/2007, hin nay hng  c mng li bay n tng vng ca c. Ngy 31/7/2008, Tiger Airways Australia thng bo ngng cc tuyn bay t sn bay quc t Darwin vo ngy 25/10/2008 v chi ph hot ng v nhin liu  y bin n tr thnh sn bay t  nht trong mng li ca hng nhng ha hn s hot ng tr li nu gi nhin liu gim. Ngy 5/8/2008, hng thng bo Adelaide l trung tm hot ng th 2 ca mnh.<br /><br /><strong>Incheon Tiger Airways:</strong><br /><br />Ngy 5/11/2007, Tiger Airways thng bo bt u m hng hng khng  Hn Quc bng ngn sch ca hng. Hng s tham gia vo mi quan h hp tc gia Tiger Aviation and Incheon Metropolitan City  m cc tuyn bay n Nht Bn, Trung Quc, Mongolia v vng pha ng nc Nga. Hng s t trung tm ti sn bay Incheon  Seoul v hi vng s i vo hot ng nm 2009.<br /><br /><strong>Qun l vic hp tc:</strong><br /><br />Tiger Airways thuc s hu hon ton ca Tiger Aviation. Cng ty c thnh lp nm 2007  qun l c 2 hng Tiger Airways v cng ty con Tiger Airways Australian  c. Cc c ng ca Tiger Airways gm Singapore Airlines (49%), i tc Indigo ca Bill Franke (24%), nh u t Irelandia Tony Ryan (16%) v Temasek Holdings (11%).<br /><br />Hng pht hnh c phiu u tin vo cui nm 2007.<br /><br />Mi nm tng kt ti chnh, hng u thng k cc thit hi, ch mi c mt bng bo co li nhun vo ngy 31/3/2008. Hng thit hi 37,4 triu (tng li nhun 75 triu) theo bo co ngy 31/3/2006 v 14,3 triu (tng li nhun 171,2 triu) theo bo co ngy 31/3/2007. Theo bo co ngy 31/3/2008, li nhun ca hng l 37,8 triu (li tc 237 triu).', '', 1, 6, 0, 38, '2012-02-03 17:34:53', 62, '', '2012-02-03 17:39:12', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-02-03 17:34:53', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 2, 0, 19, '', '', 0, 61, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(261, 'Air Mekong chnh thc ct cnh khai thc ng bay ni a', 'air-mekong-chinh-thuc-cat-canh-khai-thac-duong-bay-noi-dia', '', '<div>Cng ty C Phn hng khng Mekong  (Air Mekong) ngy 8/10  chnh thc tham gia khai thc trn th trng  hng khng ni a Vit Nam bng vic khai trng 2 chuyn bay H Ni -  Ph Quc v TPHCM - Ph Quc.</div>\r\n<div>ng Trng Thnh V -  Gim c Thng mi v Dch v Air Mekong cho bit: Air Mekong l hng  hng khng truyn thng, hng phc v hai hng dch v Hng Sang  (Deluxe) v hng Ph thng (Economy).</div>\r\n<div>Trn mi ng bay, Air Mekong phc v sut n min  ph c nhiu c sn ca cc vng min trong c nc. Hng c chnh sch  gi linh hot nhm hng ti nhiu i tng hnh khch v yu cu dch  v khc nhau.</div>\r\n<div><img src="http://dantri.vcmedia.vn/Uploaded/2010/10/09/Airmekong29100101.jpg" border="0" width="450" style="margin: 5px;" /></div>\r\n<div><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Tahoma; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">Air Mekong chnh thc ct cnh v khai thc th trng hng khng ni a Vit Nam</span></div>\r\n<div>Ngy 8/10, Air Mekong  c trao chng ch nh khai thc (AOC) ti Ph Quc, Kin Giang.</div>\r\n<div>V kt qu bc u ca chin dch khuyn mi bay cng Air Mekong  cho mng Thng Long i l, ng V cho bit: mt s ng bay  vt  con s 1.000 ch d kin ban u. Cc mc gi c khch hng t mua  nhiu l mc 400.000 trn ng bay gia TPHCM v Ph Quc, Cn o,  Pleiku,  Lt, Bun M Thut; gi 1,2 triu ng ca hnh trnh t Th   H Ni n Ph Quc; gi 800.000 ng cho khch i gia H Ni -  TPHCM, H Ni -  Lt, H Ni - Ply Cu, H Ni - Bun M Thut.</div>\r\n<div>V 2 chng trnh thu ht gii cng s l khuyn mi gii thiu  hng Deluxe v tng qu mua v qua trung tm phc v khch hng hoc  website ca hng, ng thi thanh ton qua ngn hng. i din Air  Mekong cho bit, do chng trnh khuyn mi kp nn c hng chc nghn  khch la chn thanh ton qua ngn hng.</div>\r\n<div>ng on Quc Vit - Ch tch Hi ng Qun tr Air Mekong, khng  nh: Chng ti quyt tm xy dng Air Mekong thnh hng hng khng  chuyn nghip vi i ng nhn lc di do, giu kinh nghim, lm ch k  thut v cng ngh hng khng hin i; quy trnh tiu chun r rng  p ng quy chun ca Vit Nam v cc nc c ngnh hng khng pht  trin; i my bay hin i v linh hot.</div>\r\n<div>c bit, ngnh hng khng Vit Nam c mc tng trng trn  25%/nm. Air Mekong s dng loi tu bay thng gia Bombardier CRJ vi  thi gian c rt ngn trn cc chuyn bay s tha mn nhng nhu cu  ca x hi hin i. Cc chuyn gia hng khng nhn nh, s tham gia  ca Air Mekong th hin c hi rng m trn th trng hng khng Vit  Nam, nhng t y s cnh tranh trn cc ng bay thng mi s khc  lit hn.</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: right;"><span style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold">Qunh Anh</span></div>', '', 1, 6, 0, 38, '2012-02-03 17:48:22', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-02-03 17:48:22', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 18, '', '', 0, 77, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(262, 'Jetstar Pacifcic: mua 1 v c bay 2 ngi', 'jetstar-pacifcic-mua-1-ve-duoc-bay-2-nguoi', '', 'Hng hng khng gi r Jetstar  Pacific s trin khai bn v gi r ch t 490.000 ng/chng cho 2  ngi v p dng c vi chiu lch u i TP.HCM trong giai on cao  im Tt Nguyn n 2012.\r\n<p><img src="http://dantri4.vcmedia.vn/zBWMWGSUq5Jhg0bdkuZf/Image/2011/10/JPA2011_4b376.jpg" border="0" width="450" align="middle" style="margin: 5px;" /></p>\r\n<span style="font-family: Tahoma; font-size: 10pt;">Hnh khch bay 2 ngi s ch phi tr tin 1 v</span>\r\n<div>Chng trnh bn v r ni a c bit Min ph cho ngi cng  bay trong 3 ngy lin tc (t 00h1 pht ngy 23/12 n ht ngy 25/12),  dnh cho nhm hnh khch i theo cp s chn t 2 ngi tr ln, khi  hnh trong cc giai on 16/1 - 22/1 (ch p dng cho cc chiu bay n  TP.HCM dp cao im Tt Nguyn n 2012), 5/4 - 19/4, 8/5 - 15/5/2012.</div>\r\n<p>i din Jetstar Pacific cho bit, ti a mi ln t ch khng qu 8  ngi (tc nu i 8 ngi th t trong mt booking - PV), 2 ngi cng  bay/chuyn s ch phi tr tin v cho 1 ngi, khng bao gm l ph  sn bay.</p>\r\n<p>Mc gi trn p dng cho ng bay gia TP.HCM -  Nng, 2 ngi  cng bay gia TP.HCM - H Ni, Vinh, Hi Phng ch t 950.000  ng/chng.</p>\r\n<p align="right"><span style="font-weight: bold;">Qunh Anh</span></p>', '', 1, 6, 0, 38, '2012-02-03 18:05:07', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-02-03 18:05:07', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 17, '', '', 0, 67, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(263, 'Vietnam Airlines chnh thc bay thng t H Ni, TP.HCM i Anh quc', 'vietnam-airlines-chinh-thuc-bay-thang-tu-ha-noi-tp-hcm-di-anh-quoc', '', 'Hng hng khng Quc gia Vit Nam  (Vietnam Airlines) s chnh thc khai thc ng bay thng gia H Ni,  TP.HCM i Vng quc Anh t ngy 8/12 ti y vi gi v kh hi c u  i trong giai on khai trng l gn 21 triu ng.\r\n<div><img src="http://dantri4.vcmedia.vn/zBWMWGSUq5Jhg0bdkuZf/Image/2011/11/VietNamAirlines1_1709f.jpg" border="0" width="450" align="middle" style="margin: 5px;" /></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-family: Tahoma; font-size: 10pt;">Vietnam Airlines bay thng t H Ni, TP.HCM i Anh </span></div>\r\n<div>Vi ng bay thng ny, Vietnam Airlines s khai thc  4 chuyn/tun vo cc ngy th 2, th 3, th 5 v th 6 bng my bay  Boeing 777.</div>\r\n<p>Cc chuyn bay xut pht t H Ni v TP.HCM lc 23g30, t Lun n  lc 12g20 (gi a phng) vi thi gian bay khong 12 gi, rt ngn cho  khch hng khong 7h bay so vi hnh trnh bay c 1 im dng.</p>\r\n<p>ng Trnh Hng Quang - Ph Tng Gim c Vietnam Airlines cho bit:  Vic m ng bay thng gia Vit Nam - Vng quc Anh s gip Vietnam  Airlines hon thin hn na sn phm ti Chu u, p ng nhu cu i  li, thc y hp tc u t, thng mi, giao lu vn ha gia Vit Nam  vi Vng quc Anh ni ring v Chu u ni chung; gp phn nng cao  kh nng cnh tranh, hin thc ha chin lc pht trin Vietnam  Airlines tr thnh hng hng khng ln trong khu vc.</p>\r\n<p>c bit, y l ng bay thng trc tip th 8 t Vit Nam do  Vietnam Airlines khai thc ti 4 nc  Chu u (bn cnh Pa-ri,  Phrng-phuc, Mtx-c-va) nng tng s chuyn bay thng hng tun ln 29  chuyn v m rng mng bay quc t ca hng ln ti 48 ng.</p>\r\n<p>D kin, Vietnam Airlines s tng tn sut bay n Vng quc Anh ln 7 chuyn/tun t 2 u H Ni v TP.HCM vo nm 2015.</p>\r\n<p align="right"><span style="font-weight: bold;">Qunh Anh</span></p>', '', 1, 6, 0, 38, '2012-02-03 18:15:37', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-02-03 18:15:37', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 16, '', '', 0, 138, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(264, 'Air Mekong bn v my bay gi r thu ht khch du lch', 'air-mekong-ban-ve-may-bay-gia-re-thu-hut-khach-du-lich', '', 'Hu ht trn cc ng bay thng mi sp khai trng ca Air Mekong, s khch t mua v  vt con s d kin 1.000 ch. Hng ny cho bit s tip tc chin dch khuyn mi bao gm cc mc gi mt chiu.<br />V my bay gi r khuyn mi mt chiu  cc ng bay H Ni  Cn o, Ph Quc (1,2 triu ng); 800.000 ng cho khch i chng H Ni  TP.HCM, H Ni   Lt, H Ni  Pleiku, H Ni  Bun M Thut; 400.000 ng chng H Ni   Nng, cc ng bay t TPHCMinh n Cn o, Ph Quc, Pleiku, Bun M Thut (cc mc gi trn c iu kin v cha bao gm thu, l ph sn bay).<br /><img src="http://vemaybaytet.info/wp-content/uploads/may-bay1.jpg" border="0" alt="Air Mekong bn v my bay gi r thu ht khch du lch" title="Air Mekong bn v my bay gi r thu ht khch du lch" width="447" height="278" /><br />i din hng hng khng Air Mekong cho hay: hu ht trn cc ng bay thng mi sp khai trng ca Air Mekong, s khch t mua v  vt con s 1.000 ch theo d kin ban u v hin nhu cu mua v ca hnh khch vn rt ln. Chng trnh Bay cng Air Mekong cho mng Thng Long i l tip tc ko di n 09/11/2010.<br /><br /> din tin khc, i din Air Mekong cho bit hng ny  hon thnh 16 chuyn bay th n 8 sn bay s khai thc thng mi t ngy 09/10/2010. Trong cc chuyn bay ny, Air Mekong  thc hin y  cc yu cu ca Cc Hng khng Vit Nam v an ton khai thc cng nh thc hnh cng tc phc v hnh khch.<br /><br />Theo nh gi ca Cc Hng Khng Vit Nam, cc chuyn bay th ca Air Mekong  p ng cc yu cu i vi nh khai thc. Hng  hon thnh bc quyt nh  bt u khai thc thng mi tu bay Bombardier CRJ 900 n cc sn bay Ni Bi (H Ni), Tn Sn Nht (TPHCM),  Nng, cng nh cc ng bay bin o n Ph Quc, Cn o v Cao Nguyn n Pleiku, Bun M Thut,  Lt.', '', 1, 6, 0, 38, '2012-02-03 18:28:40', 62, '', '2012-02-03 18:37:13', 62, 62, '2012-02-04 02:54:19', '2012-02-03 18:28:40', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 2, 0, 15, '', '', 0, 67, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(265, 'My bay gi r - cn nm ro thng tin iu kin gia ve', 'may-bay-gia-re-can-nam-ro-thong-tin-dieu-kin-gia-ve', '', 'Ngy cng c nhiu hng hng khng gi r ra i gip hnh khch tit  kim chi ph. Tuy nhin, khng t ngi gp s c, thit hi khi s dng  dch v ny. Gn y, Vn phng Khiu ni ngi tiu dng (NTD), Hi  Bo v quyn li NTD TP.HCM  tip nhn nhiu n khiu ni v dch v  hng khng gi r.<br /><strong>Thng tin mp m</strong><br />ng ng Vinh  Cng khiu ni v chuyn bay t Vit Nam n c ngy 1/2/2009 ca hng  hng khng Air Asia b tr hn bn ngy so vi lch trnh. Chuyn bay  khi hnh t sn bay Tn Sn Nht i Kuala Lumpur (Malaysia) b tr mt  ting. Khi p ti Kuala Lumpur th li l chuyn bay k tip t Kuala  Lumpur bay i c cng ngy v Air Asia chuyn ng i chuyn bay khc vi  ton b chi ph n,  do ng chu (khong 6 triu ng).<br /><br />Ngoi  ra, ng Cng cn khiu ni: trong chuyn bay t c v Vit Nam, ng   ng tin qu cc (hnh l d 5kg) bn c nhng ti sao v Kuala Lumpur  li b pht qu cc ln hai (50  la c/ln) cho chng t Kuala  Lumpur - Vit Nam? ng Cng  ngh Air Asia thanh ton li ton b chi  ph pht sinh ny.<br /><br />ng Trn Ngc Thng - Trng trm Air Asia,  chi nhnh ti TP.HCM, gii thch: "Air Asia l hng hng khng chuyn  ch t mt im khi hnh gc ti mt im n k tip v khng chu  trch nhim cng nh ngha v i vi hnh khch b l chuyn k tip.  Air Asia vn cha cung cp dch v chuyn tip. i vi Air Asia, hnh  khch s phi lm th tc hng khng bao gm c hnh l v th tc nhp  cnh theo tng chng, ti nhng im k tip. Theo , hnh khch phi  cn ti thiu 2,5 - 3 gi cho nhng th tc ny. i vi trng hp ca  ng Cng, Air Asia hon ton khng c trch nhim v ngha v i vi  chi ph n,  ti Kuala Lumpur".<br /><br />Theo ng Thng, Air Asia l nh  chuyn ch theo tng chng, nn vic thu hnh l qu cc cng c p  dng theo tng chng. ng Cng ch ng tin qu cc cho chng t c  v Kuala Lumpur. V vy, t Kuala Lumpur v Vit Nam ng Cng phi  tip tc ng tin qu cc.<br /><br />"Ti khng c nhu cu mua <a title="V gi r">v gi r</a>,  nhng li khng c nhn vin bn v hng dn k  la chn. Mi  thng tin Air Asia ng ti trn website v in trn v in t hon ton  bng ting Anh, gy kh khn cho nhng ngi khng rnh ngoi ng", ng  Cng bc xc.<br /><br />Tng t, ng V ng Nam mua v my bay cho con  l V L Duy i du hc ti c ngy 12/7, l trnh bay ging nh ng  Cng. Chuyn bay khi hnh t sn bay Tn Sn Nht i Kuala Lumpur cng  b hon lin tc 2, 3 ln nn khi em Duy n Kuala Lumpur b tr chuyn  bay k tip i c. Em Duy li phi ng thm 350 RM (tin Malaysia  tng ng 150 USD) mi c b tr bay chuyn m hm sau, chi ph n  ung t tc. ng Nam khiu ni t ngy 20/7 n chiu ngy 6/8, i din  phng v my bay 247E - Ticket (Q.Tn Bnh) vn cha c vn bn tr li  tha ng.<br /><br />i din Vn phng Khiu ni NTD cho bit, phn ln  nhng v khiu ni v hng khng l do thng tin cung cp mp m, khng  r rng gy kh khn cho ngi s dng dch v. Nhiu hng thng tin  hon ton bng ting Anh khng ph hp vi NTD Vit Nam. Trong khi ,  nhn vin li khng hng dn r rng cho khch. L ra, cc im bn v  phi t vn k cho khch hng v cc hn ch ca loi <a title="V my bay gi r">v my bay gi r</a>,  hng dn khch chn cc chuyn bay c gi bay thch hp.<br /><strong><br />Kinh nghim s dng dch v bay gi r</strong><br /><br />i  din mng v my bay trc tuyn vemaybaygiare.vn ca Cng ty c phn  Thanh Nin (TP.HCM), ng Trn Hi Bng cho bit, "My bay gi r thng  ch c mt hng gh chung cho tt c hnh khch, khng c dch v n  ung, c bo. Bn cnh , khi s dng dch v bay gi r, khch hng  khng th hon chuyn bay hay hy v, phi ng thm ph hnh l k gi.  Khi thay i lch bay, khch phi ng ph thay i khong 160.000/v  v mc chnh lch gi v vo thi im i".<br /><br />"Trong trng hp gp  trc trc, tr chuyn bay, khch hng c th hy v ti sn bay v quay  v i l ly li tin hoc gi cho i l bn v  phi hp vi hng  gii quyt s c theo quy nh ca mi hng"  ng Bng hng dn.<br /><br />Theo  ng Bng, hnh khch ch nn mua v gi r khi  cn nhc k k hoch  i v nn t mua v trc 1 - 1,5 thng, nht l nhng hnh trnh c  tn sut bay t. Nn chn chuyn bay vo gi thp im (m) c t ngi  i, gi s r hn t 200.000 - 300.000/v. iu quan trng l trc  khi quyt nh mua v, khch hng nn tm hiu k thng tin v dch v,  yu cu nhn vin bn v t vn k  trnh nhng s c xy ra.<br /><br />Tin thm v <a title="V my bay gi r">v my bay gi r</a> c ng ti ti Bo Dn Tr<br />Hng  hng khng gi r Jetstar Pacific va chnh thc cng b thc hin  chng trnh bn 50.000 v my bay gi r t 250.000 ng. y l t  bn v gi r ln nht ca hng t u nm 2009.<br />Thi gian m bn bt  u t 6h sng ngy 18/2 v kt thc vo lc 23h59 ngy 22/2. V my  bay do h thng my tnh t ng phn phi trn cc chuyn bay c ngy  khi hnh trong giai on t 3/3 n 21/5.<br /><br />c bit, phm vi bn  v ln ny c Jetstar Pacific m rng n tt c cc knh bn, bao  gm: Trang web jetstar.com, cc Phng v, i l ca Jetstar Pacific  trn ton quc v Tng i 19001550 (hoc 08.3 9550 550).<br />Vic thanh ton phi c thc hin ngay ti thi im t ch.<br />Mc gi m bn trn cc tuyn bay nh sau:<br /><br /> \r\n<table style="text-align: center;" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="193">\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Tuyn bay (gia/v)</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="99">\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Gi t</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="193">\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">TPHCM -  Nng</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">TPHCM - Hu</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">H Ni -  Nng</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="99">\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">250.000 VN</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="193">\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">TPHCM - H Ni</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">TPHCM - Hi Phng</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">TPHCM - Vinh</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">H Ni - Cn Th</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="99">\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">500.000 VN</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br />V hn ch bn i vi cc chuyn bay trong thi gian t 28/4 - 3/5/2009.<br /><br />C  cu gi v ca Jetstar Pacific bao gm 3 nhm gi chnh, c phn phi  t thp n cao ti tt c cc knh bn  khch hng la chn.<br />Nhm  gi JetFlex cho php thay i ngy bay min ph, dnh cho nhng hnh  khch cng v c k hoch i li hay thay i; Nhm gi tit kim  JetSaver dnh cho nhng hnh khch n nh k hoch i li  tit kim  chi ph; c bit, vi nhng hnh khch ch mang di 7kg hnh l xch  tay c th la chn loi gi v JetSaver Light  c th tit kim thm  t nht 50.000 ng/chng ni a, 320.000 ng/chng quc t.<br />Phc Hng', '', 1, 6, 0, 38, '2012-02-03 18:37:16', 62, '', '2012-02-04 02:53:49', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-02-03 18:37:16', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 12, 0, 14, '', '', 0, 66, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(266, 'My bay gi r - Gii cn kht v my bay gi r ', 'giai-con-khat-ve-may-bay-gia-re', '', 'i din ca VietJetAir cho bit, tnh n 11h59 pht ngy 11/12/2011 sau khi chng trnh VietJetAir tun khuyn mi: <a title="V my bay">V my bay</a> Ch T 100.000 kt thc,  c 2036 <a title="V gi r">v gi r</a> 100.000 c bn ht v s lng ny c th dao ng do s lng thc thanh ton sau 48h t gi ch thay i.<br /><br />S lng v r ca VietJetAir c bn ch yu thng qua website vietjetair.com v c m t ng ngu nhin trn h thng cho tt c cc ngy trong tun, ty thuc vo tnh trng ca chuyn bay. C ch phn phi v ngu nhin trn h thng  gp phn to c hi bnh ng cho tt c cc khch hng, trnh trng hp cc i l gom v nh  tng xy ra trong cc t khuyn mi ca nhiu hng hng khng trc .<br /><br />ng nh cam kt ca hng l ngy no trong tun khuyn mi cng c gi v r  m bo c hi mua v cho khch hng, theo thng k ca h thng t ch VietJetAir, sau hn 5 gi u tin thc hin chng trnh khuyn mi, 659 <a title="V my bay gi r">v my bay gi r</a> 100,000  c bn. S lng ny tng ln 1237 v 1581 v cho 2 ngy v 4 ngy sau .<br /><br />Do s quan tm ca khch hng c nc trong nhng ngy gia tun khuyn mi tng ln t bin, VietJetAir cng  quyt nh tng s lng v khuyn mi cho sut chng trnh Tun khuyn mi. Cng vi mt s lng v c t ng nh ra trn h thng do mt s khch hng gi ch nhng ht 48 gi khng thanh ton tin mua v, nhng hnh khch c nhu cu mua v khuyn mi thc s  nm bt c c hi trong nhng ngy cui ca chng trnh Tun khuyn mi.<br /><br />Gii p v kh nng VietJetAir m khuyn mi s lng ln v gi c r c th nh hng n cht lng phc v ca hng sau ny hay khng, i din ca VietJetAir khng nh: Vic p dng hnh thc khuyn mi gi v r l nhm mc ch kch thch nhu cu i li bng ng hng khng, mang li cho nhiu ngi c hi c bay vi chi ph thp, mi trng thn thin, vi loi tu bay tin nghi cao,c bit vi gh da m i. iu ny l chin lc pht trin ca VietJetAir.<br /><br />V tt nhin, m bo hiu qu kinh doanh, trn mi chuyn bay ch c mt t l nh s v khuyn mi vi gi c bit thp,hnh khch cng mua v sm th v cng r. Trn mi chuyn bay ca VietJetAir, tt c cc hnh khch u c phc v nh nhau, bt k mua v gi no. Vi gi v cc thp nh vy, lng ngi quan tm cao, lng v trn mi chuyn bay khng nhiu, th t ch qua internet  mua c v khuyn mi c bit cng i hi khch hng phi kin nhn hn.<br /><br /> hn ch tnh trng gm gi ch, cc t khuyn mi ti y ca hng s ch p dng hnh thc thanh ton ngay bng th tn dng.<br /><br /> gim cc chi ph cho khch hng, ngoi vic tch bch cc khon chi ph nh  n ung, hnh l, hnh khch la chn, VietJetAir thc hin vic iu tit gi v theo quy lut th trng v s dng cc bin php nng cao nng sut lao ng, khai thc i my bay mi  gim chi ph xng du, bo dng v tng cht lng chuyn bay cho khch hng.<br /><br />H.', '', 1, 6, 0, 38, '2012-02-03 18:59:50', 62, '', '2012-02-04 02:49:19', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-02-03 18:59:50', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 4, 0, 13, '', '', 0, 65, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(267, 't v gi r i Singapore trc thm nm mi', 'dat-ve-gia-re-di-singapore-truoc-them-nam-moi', '', 'Trong thi gian t 27/01/2011 cho n ht ngy 02/02/2011, khch hng c th t c mc <a title="V gi r">v gi r</a> i Singapore vi gi ch US$0 + thu. Thu thay i ty thuc vo chng bay. V c th c bn ht trc thi im 2/2/2011.<br /><br /> t c v hnh khch phi t v trc ngy 02/02/2011 v c ngy khi hnh ri vo giai an sau:<br /><br />H NI i SINGAPORE: 01/04 n 30/11/2011<br />H CH MINH i SINGAPORE: 15/02/2011  30/06/2011<br />H CH MINH i PERTH: 10/02/2011  30/09/2011.<br /><a title="V gi r">V gi r</a> i Singapore<br /><img src="http://muavere.com/wp-admin/images/hinh-anh-rieng/post/2011/01.2011/di_sing_truocthemnammoi.png" border="0" alt="t v gi r i Singapore trc thm nm mi" title="t v gi r i Singapore trc thm nm mi" width="537" height="85" /><br />Thng tin chi tit cc ng bay khuyn mi.<br /><br />Thng tin chi tit v gi v v ng bay c th xin lin h phng v my bay Vng Trn S hoc in thoi (08)38843306, (08)22128030, 0938456189, 0937416636 , Fax (08)39848698. a ch: 86/936C, L c Th, Phng 6, Qun G Vp, Tp.HCM [xem bn ]. Bn c th lin h ngoi gi qua s my 0938456189 nu cn i gp.<br /><br />Vo thi im ny, Jetstar cng ang tung gi mc gi khuyn mi v cng hp dn cho cc hnh trnh khi hnh trong thng 4/2011, v thng c bn vo cc ngy th su hng tun.<br /><br />ng thi, cc bn hy chun b tinh thn cho mt t khuyn mi vo m giao tha 2011 ha hn s mang n mc gi hp dn cha tng c. Hy ng k nhn tin  tr thnh mt trong nhng ngi u tin bit tin khuyn mi ca chng ti.', '', 1, 6, 0, 38, '2012-02-03 19:13:35', 62, '', '2012-02-04 02:44:48', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-02-03 19:13:35', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 2, 0, 12, '', '', 0, 148, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(268, 'Cch t v gi r Jetstar, thanh ton bng th', 'cach-dat-ve-gia-re-jetstar-thanh-toan-bang-the', '', 'Mua v trc tuyn trn mng s gip bn mua c  v my bay mt cch nhanh chng vi gi r v khng phi tr cc chi  ph trung gian cho cc phng v.\r\n<p>Cch t <a title="V my bay gi r">v gi r</a> <br />Truy cp vo a ch <a href="http://www.jetstar.com/vn/">http://www.jetstar.com/vn/</a> v lm theo cc hng dn sau:</p>\r\n<p><strong>Bc 1: </strong>Tm chuyn bay<strong> <br /><strong>Bc 2: </strong></strong>Chn chuyn bay<strong> <br /><strong>Bc 3: </strong></strong>Hnh khch v thanh ton<strong> <br /><strong>Bc 4: </strong></strong>Xc nhn<strong><strong> <br /></strong></strong></p>\r\n<p><img src="http://www.chudu24.com/f/m/081104/hanh/hinh-anh/sanbay.jpg" border="0" title="Cch t v gi r Jetstar, thanh ton bng th" width="400" height="295" style="border: 0pt none;" /></p>\r\n<p><strong>Bc 1: Tm chuyn bay<strong> <br /></strong></strong></p>\r\n<p>Ty theo nhu cu ca chuyn i, qu khch nhn chn 1 trong cc  "Kh hi" hoc "Mt chiu"</p>\r\n<p>Chn hnh trnh ph hp: chng bay i nhn vo "Khi hnh", chng  bay v nhn vo "n" V d: Bay t TP H Ch Minh n H Ni</p>\r\n<p>Nhn chn "Ngy i" v "Ngy v". Chn s lng ngi ln hoc tr em hoc em b (nu c).</p>\r\n<p>Tip n chn  "Mua v"  gc phi cui mn hnh   <br />V u trang</p>\r\n<p><strong>Bc 2: Chn chuyn bay<strong> <br /></strong></strong></p>\r\n<p>Qu khch c th la chn gi v v thi gian bay cho lt i v lt  v. Ti y c nhiu gi v v thi gian chuyn bay khi hnh  Qu  khch la chn theo nhu cu.</p>\r\n<p>Sau khi  hon tt, chn  "Ti  c v chp nhn cc iu Kin  Gi V v iu Kin Vn Chuyn ca Hng hang khng"  pha di. Chn   "Tip tc".</p>\r\n<p>Qu khch c th c yu cu xc nhn gi nguyn loi gi v  chn hoc thay i la chn thnh loi gi v khc.   <br />V u trang</p>\r\n<p><strong>Bc 3: Hnh khch v thanh ton<strong> <br /></strong></strong></p>\r\n<p>Qu khch cn in y  thng tin hnh khch v thng tin lin lc trong phn "Chi Tit Hnh Khch" v "Chi tit lin lc".</p>\r\n<p>Vic thanh ton c thc hin bng 1 trong 3 hnh thc sau:</p>\r\n<p>- Th tn dng   <br />- Phiu thanh ton    <br />- Nu bn khng c th tn dng, ng lo bn c th <strong>Thanh ton sau</strong> (vic ny rt n gin v tit kim)</p>\r\n<p>Thanh tan bng th tn dng:</p>\r\n<p>Nu Qu khch chn phng thc thanh ton bng Th tn dng, chn   "Th tn dng" Khi thanh ton trc tip qua website, Qu khch hin ch  c th s dng mt s loi th sau y:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>VISA (Credit card v Debit card)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>MASTER (Credit card)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>JCB (Credit card)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>American Express (Credit card)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Lu : vic thanh ton ch c hon tt khi cc loi th trn c  ng k chc nng thanh ton online vi ngn hng pht hnh th.</p>\r\n<p>Qu khch cn in thng tin Th tn dng nh "Loi th" , "S th" ,  "Tn ch th" , "Ngy/thng ht hn th", "S CVC/CVV" . Cc thng tin  th tn dng ca Qu khch s c bo mt v c xc nhn vi ngn  hng pht hnh th.</p>\r\n<p>Sau  nhn "Mua v"</p>\r\n<p>Thanh ton bng phiu thanh ton:</p>\r\n<p>Trong trng hp Qu khch thanh ton bng Phiu Thanh Ton, Qu  khch cn in y  thng tin vo  "M phiu thanh ton" v "S phiu  thanh ton".</p>\r\n<p>Sau  nhn "Thanh ton"   <br /><strong> <br /><strong>Thanh ton sau:</strong></strong></p>\r\n<p>Trong trng hp khng c cc loi th nu trn, hnh khch vn c  th ng k ch v thanh ton bng tin mt ti cc phng v ca Jetstar  hoc cc chi nhnh ca ngn hng Techcombank (vic ny cc k n  gin), ch cn ghi li m t ch sau  ra chi nhnh Techcombank gn  nht chuyn tin nhanh n ti khon ca Pacific. Chn  "Thanh ton  sau" . Thi hn thanh ton s c hin th trn mn hnh  Qu khch  bit thi hn thanh ton v xut v.</p>\r\n<p>Sau  nhn "Thanh ton"   <br />V u trang</p>\r\n<p><strong>Bc 4: Xc nhn</strong></p>\r\n<p>Trong trng hp Thanh ton bng Th Tn dng, mn hnh s hin th  t Xc nhn hnh trnh, t xc nhn hnh trnh ny ch c gi tr khi  lm th tc trn cc chuyn bay ca Pacific Airlines. Ngoi ra, V in  t s c gi v email m Qu khch  cung cp, V in t ny c gi  tr lm th tc ti chnh khi cn.   <br />Trong trng hp Thanh ton  sau, mn hnh s hin th hnh trnh  c xc nhn. Qu khch lu li  M t ch (gm 6 k t)  cung cp cho nhn vin phng v ca Pacific  Airlines v tin hnh thanh ton bng tin mt theo ng thi hn   c quy nh trong bn Xc nhn hnh trnh (24 gi k t thi im t  ch thnh cng  sau thi gian ny, ch  t s t ng hy nu Qu  khch cha thanh ton tin).</p>\r\n<p><strong>Trong trng hp bn gp kh khn v v  thanh ton hoc  khng c th thanh ton, hy lin h (ngay sau khi bn t v xong) vi  phng v <strong>Nam H</strong></strong><strong>ng<strong> ti Th</strong>nh <br />Ph H Ch Minh</strong><strong><strong>,</strong> chng ti s gip bn c c chic v  bng  ng gi m bn t mua. Lin h: 198 Cao<strong> Th</strong></strong><strong>ng<strong>, Ph</strong>ng 12, Qun 10, TP.HCM<strong>. </strong>T<strong> 0933.111.333</strong></strong></p>', '', 1, 6, 0, 38, '2012-02-03 19:19:46', 62, '', '2012-02-04 02:40:53', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-02-03 19:19:46', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 3, 0, 11, '', '', 0, 73, 'robots=\nauthor=');
