(269, 'Hng khng ''au u'' v thi tit cui nm', 'hang-khong-dau-vi-thoi-tiet-cuoi-nam', '', '<img src="http://vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3b/bd/1a/7e/hangkhong.jpg" border="0" style="font-family: Arial, Tahoma, ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 11px; line-height: normal; height: 200px; width: 250px; vertical-align: middle; border-image: initial; padding: 4px; margin: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;" /><strong><br /><br />Tip theo thng tin v vic </strong><a href="http://espc.vn/Suong_mu_khien_nhieu_chuyen_bay_Vietnam_Airlines_bi_huy__news-e3f307dd-d576-4d38-8b7a-b7d40c375292.html" style="padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 5px; padding-left: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 15px; color: #14418f; margin: 0px;"><strong>Vietnam Airlines hy nhiu chuyn bay do tnh hnh thi tit</strong></a><strong>, mt s hng hng khng trong nc nh JetStart, VietJet Air,...cng c th phi hy hoc hon chuyn bay do tnh hnh thi tit</strong> <br /><span style="font-family: Arial, Tahoma, ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 11px; line-height: normal; text-align: justify;"> </span><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; line-height: normal; text-align: justify; background-color: #f4f5f6; font-size: 16px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"><br />Nhiu hnh khch Vietnam Airlines trn chuyn bay 7154 t TP HCM i H Ni ngy 19/1 ca hng ny vn khng qun vic phi  li  Nng nhiu gi do thi tit xu khin my bay khng th p xung sn bay Ni Bi. Vic phi quay li  Nng v nm li  y khin hnh khch bt bnh, cn hng chu khng t thit hi. Trc  2 ngy, my bay ca Jetstar Pacific cng khng th h cnh xung Vinh v sng m.</span>\r\n<p style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; line-height: normal; text-align: justify; background-color: #f4f5f6; font-size: 16px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">Thng k ca Vietnam Airlines cho bit  hon, hy chuyn hng lot  khu vc min Trung trong 3 ngy 16-17-18/1 do thi tit xu sng m dy c, trn my thp khng m bo an ton bay.</p>\r\n<p style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; line-height: normal; text-align: justify; background-color: #f4f5f6; font-size: 16px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">Hng ny cng khuyn co thm, thi tit xu s tip tc nh hng n cc sn bay nh Chu Lai (Qung Nam), ng Hi (Qung Bnh), Ph Bi (Hu), Lin Khng ( Lt), Ct Bi (Hi Phng), Bun Ma Thuc v Pleiku (Gia Lai).</p>\r\n<p style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; line-height: normal; text-align: justify; background-color: #f4f5f6; font-size: 16px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">Tuy cha c thit hi v hon chuyn nhng Vietjet Air cng lo lng v hng khai thc ng bay TP HCM - H Ni vi tn sut ti a, ch mt chuyn b hon s nh hng dy chuyn v gy thit hi ln.</p>\r\n<p style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; line-height: normal; text-align: justify; background-color: #f4f5f6; font-size: 16px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"><br style="font-family: Arial, Tahoma, ''Times New Roman''; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;" />Thit hi ln nht ca hng l b o ln lch trnh, gy chm chuyn dy chuyn. Ngoi ra, nhiu hnh khch sau khi chuyn bay b hon  yu cu hon li tin, khng bay tip. Thng thng, chuyn bay b hy trong ngy nu c bay li vo ngy hm sau cng khng cn nhiu khch."Mi nm giai on t thng 11 n thng 3, t l hon, hy chuyn bay ca hng ti Vinh v thi tit ln n 25%, sng m l mt trong nhng nguyn nhn chnh", i din Vietnam Airlines ti Vinh cho bit.</p>\r\n<p style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; line-height: normal; text-align: justify; background-color: #f4f5f6; font-size: 16px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">i din Vietnam Airlines ti Vinh khng nh, tnh trng trn ang dn c khc phc nht l khi h thng ct h cnh t ng c a vo hot ng ti sn bay Vinh vo thng 11 nm ngoi. Nm nay t l hon, hy chuyn ti sn bay  Vinh  gim hn.</p>\r\n<p style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; line-height: normal; text-align: justify; background-color: #f4f5f6; font-size: 16px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">"Vo ma ng, thi tit khng kh lnh gy kh khn trong vic bay v din bin bt thng, c trong 10 pht th c chuyn h c, chuyn khng, thit hi l rt ln", i din Jetstar Pacific ni.<span style="color: #000000; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">Chuyn bay t Vinh i TP HCM ca hng b hon ngy 17/1 v sng m  gy thit hi ln n 150 triu ng.</span></p>\r\n<p style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; line-height: normal; text-align: justify; background-color: #f4f5f6; font-size: 16px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">Theo mt chuyn gia trong lnh vc hng khng, chuyn bay t TP HCM i H Ni s mt khong 120 triu ng tin nhin liu, nu b hy hay hon, hng khng phi "cn rng" chu khon ny.</p>', '', 1, 6, 0, 38, '2012-02-04 03:37:54', 64, '', '2012-02-04 03:53:48', 64, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-02-04 03:37:54', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 9, 0, 10, '', '', 0, 52, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(270, ' Nng c thm ng bay quc t mi i Hn Quc', 'a-nng-co-them-ng-bay-quc-t-mi-i-han-quc', '', '<img src="http://image.dothi.net/thumbnail/480/san-bay-1_2.jpg?url=Storage/Images/san-bay-1_2.jpg" border="0" style="font-family: Arial, Tahoma, ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 11px; line-height: normal; height: 200px; width: 350px; border-image: initial; padding: 4px; margin: 0px;" /><span style="font-family: Arial, Tahoma, ''Times New Roman''; line-height: normal; text-align: justify;"><br /><br />Sau khi Sn bay Quc t  Nng khnh thnh vo thng 12 nm 2011, sn bay  nng li tip tc n nhn thm ng bay Quc t mi ca Korean Air<br /></span> <span style="font-family: Arial, Tahoma, ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 11px; line-height: normal; text-align: justify;"><br />Ngy 15-1, ng Nguyn Phc Linh, Ph Gim c S VH-TT-DL TP  Nng, cho bit: Sau mt thi gian nghin cu, kho st th trng du lch TP  Nng, Hng hng khng Korean Air (Hn Quc)  quyt nh khai thc thng mi chuyn bay thng t Hn Quc n  Nng.</span>\r\n<p style="font-family: Arial, Tahoma, ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 11px; line-height: normal; text-align: justify; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">K t ngy 19-1-2012, hng ny s chnh thc khai trng chuyn bay trc tip Seoul   Nng vi tn sut 2 chuyn/tun vo cc ngy th nm v ch nht vi my bay Boeing 737-800 v Boeing 373-800.  Nng c c hi kt ni trc tip vi hn 119 thnh ph ln ca hn 39 quc gia trn th gii qua mng li bay rng ln ca Korean Air.</p>', '', 1, 6, 0, 38, '2012-02-04 04:13:10', 64, '', '2012-02-04 04:15:27', 64, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-02-04 04:13:10', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 2, 0, 9, '', '', 0, 40, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(271, 'Kinh doanh hng khng: Min t d', 'kinh-doanh-hang-khong', '', '<div style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; width: 200px; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; float: left; position: relative; color: #000000; line-height: normal; text-align: left;"><img src="http://img-hcm.24hstatic.com:8008/upload/1-2012/images/2012-02-01/1328062265_hang-khong-gia-re1.jpg" border="0" alt="Kinh doanh hng khng: Min t d" width="200" height="200" style="border: 1px initial initial;" />\r\n<div style="font-size: 11px; padding-top: 5px; padding-bottom: 5px; text-align: center; color: #666666;">Th trng HK Vit Nam vn ang trong tnh trng "cu vt cung".</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; float: left; width: 323px; color: #000000; line-height: normal; text-align: left;">\r\n<h1 style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: #1d8a0d; padding-bottom: 5px; margin: 0px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;">Khi nhng hng hng khng t nhn u tin ra i, nhng nh u t ngoi nhy vo nhiu ngi  vui mng cho rng: bu tri  m... Tuy nhin, kinh doanh hng khng tim nng y, c hi y nhng cng tht kh  c mt ch ng.</span></h1>\r\n<div style="font-weight: bold; text-align: justify; padding-right: 10px;">C hi vn l c hi</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; padding-bottom: 10px; color: #000000; line-height: normal; text-align: left;">\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;">\r\n<div>\r\n<p><strong><br /><br /><br /></strong></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p><br /><br />Kt thc 2011, tng th trng hng khng (HK) Vit Nam t 23,6 triu lt khch. Trong  cc hng HK Vit Nam vn chuyn 16,6 triu lt, t t l tng trng 13,6%. Tuy khng t so vi d bo, nhng trong bi cnh kh khn kinh t th  cng l mt s tng trng cha ng nhiu c hi.<br /><br />Cc chuyn gia nhn nh, th trng HK Vit Nam s tip tc tng trng n tng, nm 2015 s t 34-36 triu hnh khch vi tc  tng trng bnh qun l 11-13%; n 2019 s t 52-59 triu hnh khch. Vn ti hng ha s tng ln 850 nghn n 930 nghn tn vo nm 2015 v 1,4-1,6 triu tn vo nm 2019.</p>\r\n<p>Nm bt thi c, mt lot hng HK t nhn c cp php hot ng, nhanh chng tip cn th trng. Ngoi Vietnam Airlines (VNA) v Jetstar Pacific (JP) vn  quen thuc, cc hng HK t nhn gm Indochina Airlines, AirMekong v mi y l Vietjet Air  ct cnh.<br /><br />Tuy vy, d tim nng ln nhng th trng HK vn l "mnh t d" i vi cc hng t nhn. Indochina Airlines  chnh thc khai t, v cn qu sm  Air Mekong, Vietjet Air khng nh c v tr. Trong khi, hn hai nm sau ngy nhn giy php nhng hng HK Tri Thin vn khng th ct cnh v  b "khai t". Cn Jetstar Pacific cha thot khi thua l. Cn nh c VNA vn ng vng trn li th ca mnh nhng kh c th chi b nhng hn ch khi t sut li nhun vn  mc thp.</p>\r\n<p>Vy, kinh doanh HK c l "qu ngt" cho cc doanh nghip. Theo cc chuyn gia,  tr c trong ngnh vn ti HK, i hi cc nh u t phi c tim lc mnh,  cho cuc ua ng trng. Tuy vy, vn cn  nhiu nh u nc ngoi vn coi y l c hi. Bi thc t, th trng HK Vit Nam vn ang trong tnh trng "cu vt cung".</p>\r\n<p>Nu so vi cc nc trong khu vc, HK Vit Nam vn cn  mc  "khim tn". Mi nm Thi Lan trn 60 triu lt khch i my bay, cn  Malaysia mi triu ngi dn c 8 my bay thng mi.  Australia mi triu ngi dn c 15 my bay. Con s ny  Vit Nam l 0,7. VN tt hu v mc  cng cng ha vn ti HK 10 ln so vi Malaysia, 20 ln so vi Australia. Bi vy nn, d c li th ng u cc nc ASEAN nhng nng lc chuyn ch ca HK Vit Nam ch ch ginh c 12% th phn. R rng  l c hi cho cc nh u t.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://img-hcm.24hstatic.com:8008/upload/1-2012/images/2012-02-01/1328062115-hang-khong-gia-re.jpg" border="0" alt="Kinh doanh hng khng: Min t d, Th trng - Tiu dng, hang khong, kinh doanh, gia re, ve may bay, bao" style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial;" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span><em>Indochina airlines  sm ph sn.</em></span></p>\r\n<p><strong>Ca no cho vn ngoi</strong></p>\r\n<p>Nhng trn thc t, ngoi tr Qantas mua li 27% th phn ca Pacific Airlines nm 2007 v i tn thnh JP, n nay vn cha c thm nh u t no thc s tham gia vo lnh vc ny. D nhng nm trc Air Asia hay Singapore Airlines cng tin hnh kh nhiu cuc thng tho nhng khng i n kt qu.</p>\r\n<p>u t nc ngoi vo lnh vc HK cng khng cn xa l nhng  lun l vn  nhy cm ca bt c cc quc gia. T l vn nc ngoi trong mt hng HK vn l ro cn ln nht trong tin trnh m phn "Hip nh Bu tri m" gia M v EU. n nay, M vn gi tng mc u t nc ngoi vo HK ca M l 25%, cn Brasil 20%.... Thc cht ca vn  ny nhm bo h cc hng HK trong nc, gi c quyn li trn cc ng bay ni a. Cn vi cc nh u t, vi t l vn "khim tn" nh vy, khin h khng mn m.<br />Vi Vit Nam, quy nh bn nc ngoi khng chim qu 49% vn iu l i vi hng HK, hoc 49% vn iu l i vi doanh nghip kinh doanh HK chung; mt c nhn hoc php nhn nc ngoi khng chim qu 30% vn iu l. Tuy nhin,cui thng 12/2011 B GTVT  chnh thc trnh Chnh ph d tho Ngh nh thay th Ngh nh s 76, trong  nng vn php nh i vi lp hng HK mi, nhm hn ch tnh trng, sm b khai t nh Indochina Airliines hoc dng giy php  mi gi cc nh u t ngoi.</p>\r\n<p>i vi u t nc ngoi d tho nu hai phng n. Mt l, hng HK c vn u t nc ngoi phi p ng iu kin bn nc ngoi khng chim qu 49% vn iu l. Mt c nhn hoc php nhn nc ngoi khng chim qu 30% vn iu l. Mt c nhn hoc php nhn Vit Nam phi gi phn vn iu l ln nht.</p>\r\n<p>Hai l, hng HK c vn u t nc ngoi phi p ng iu kin bn nc ngoi khng chim qu 30% vn iu l i vi hng HK. Mt c nhn hoc php nhn nc ngoi khng chim qu 20% vn iu l. Mt c nhn hoc php nhn Vit Nam phi gi phn vn iu l ln nht.</p>\r\n<p>Quy nh v chuyn nhng, tng c phn cho nh u t nc ngoi theo hnh thc u t trc tip, d tho quy nh hng HK ch c php thc hin vic chuyn nhng, tng c phn cho nh u t nc ngoi sau hai nm k t ngy bt u khai thc vn chuyn HK, cung cp dch v HK chung.</p>\r\n<p>V vn  ny, mt chuyn gia t VNA cho rng, quy nh vn gp ca nc ngoi chim ti 30% vn iu l nh hin nay l cao hn cc quc gia trn th gii v khng ph hp vi ngnh HK non tr ca Vit Nam.</p>\r\n<p>Vic nh u t nc ngoi nm 30% c phn s c quyn ph quyt vi cc quyt nh ca i hi c ng v s nh hng trc tip ti cc quyt sch ln ca hng HK ni. iu ny cng nh hng tiu cc ti th trng HK ni a, kin ngh sa i t l vn gp xung cn 25% v khng ch mc gp vn ca nh u t nc ngoi l hng HK di 10% vn iu l.</p>\r\n<p>Trong khi , B GTVT cho rng, phng n 1 s gip cc hng HK trong nc tip cn ngun vn u t, khoa hc cng ngh tin tin d dng hn. Tuy nhin, phng n 2 (25%) s hn ch u t nc ngoi vo HK nhng loi tr c quyn ph quyt vi cc quyt nh ca i hi c ng. iu ny s khng gy nh hng tiu cc ti th trng HK ni a vn c bo h  ginh quyn khai thc cho cc hng HK trong nc. Hn ch ti a vic cc doanh nghip thnh lp cc hng HK  hng ti vic bn c phn thu li;  nh u t nc ngoi lng on th trng.</p>\r\n<p>Xung quanh vn  ny, B T php khng nh, vic la chn phng n no l ty thuc vo chnh sch pht trin HK dn dng. Cn phi tr li cu hi: Chng ta cn vn hay mun kim sot hu hiu cc hng HK?</p>\r\n<p>Lnh o mt hng HK ang kinh doanh ti th trng ni a ng tnh vi quan im ny ca B T php. ng ny cho bit, nu cn vn, cn ngun lc khoa hc k thut  h tr cho HK Vit Nam pht trin th nn gi t l vn gp 30% nh hin nay. Cc vn  khc kim sot bng cc quy nh chuyn ngnh. Cn nu  25% th coi nh "ng ca" vi cc nh u t nc ngoi.</p>\r\n<p>Trong hai phng n trn, nhiu chuyn gia hng khng t ra thun theo phng n hai khi cho rng, u t nc ngoi b hn ch nhng s hn ch nh u t nc ngoi nm c c phn chi phi, s dn ti vic mt quyn kim sot hu hiu i vi hng HK ni a. Cho nn, quy nh ny s gip nh u t Vit Nam gi c ting ni, trnh b nh u t nc ngoi gi c phn chi phi ph quyt.</p>\r\n<p>Chng ta cng nhau nh li s vic Coca Cola, cc nh u t nc ngoi  cp trng Coca Cola t tay Vit Nam thng qua hnh thc gp vn lin doanh. y c xem nh mt bi hc kinh nghim xng mu cho pha Vit Nam, c l chnh v th m cho n nay cc doanh nghip Vit Nam lun d chng khi "chi" vi cc nh u t nc ngoi.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '', 1, 6, 0, 38, '2012-02-04 04:19:49', 64, '', '2012-02-04 04:22:53', 64, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-02-04 04:19:49', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 3, 0, 8, '', '', 0, 43, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(272, ' Nng- Lt: tuyn bay c nhiu hn ch', 'da-nang-da-lat-tuyet-bay-co-nhieu-han-che', '', '<div style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; width: 200px; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; float: left; position: relative; color: #000000; line-height: normal; text-align: left;"><img src="http://anh.24h.com.vn:8008/upload/3-2010/images/2010-08-12/1281596766_tuyen-bay.jpg" border="0" alt=" Nng- Lt: tuyn bay c nhiu hn ch" width="200" height="200" style="border: 1px initial initial;" />\r\n<div style="font-size: 11px; padding-top: 5px; padding-bottom: 5px; text-align: center; color: #666666;">Tuyn bay th hin nhiu hn ch.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; float: left; width: 323px; color: #000000; line-height: normal; text-align: left;">\r\n<h1 style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: #1d8a0d; padding-bottom: 5px; margin: 0px;"><span style="text-align: justify; font-size: 11px; color: #000000;">(Tin tuc) - Chiu qua, tin t Vn phng UBND TP  Nng cho hay: ng bay trc tip  Nng -  Lt c a vo khai thc t ngy 30 - 6 - 2010 vi tn sut 4 chuyn/tun bng my bay ATR 72 (65 ch).</span></h1>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; padding-bottom: 10px; color: #000000; line-height: normal; text-align: left;">\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;">\r\n<div>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p><br /><br /><br />Tuy nhin, theo phn nh ca khch hng, cng ty l hnh, tuyn bay ang bc l nhiu hn ch, nh: loi my bay nh, kh nng khai thc du lch hn ch, c bit kh khn cho vic pht ng n cc on khch ln.<br /><br />Mt s chng trnh khuyn mi  c cho bn nhng s lng v khuyn mi m cc doanh nghip l hnh nhn c t Tng Cty Hng khng Vit Nam (VNA) cn qu t. Ngoi ra, cc doanh nghip l hnh cng cha bit k hoch bn v ca VNA, c bit vo thi im vng khch.</p>\r\n<p>UBND TP  Nng  c vn bn  ngh VNA sm c bin php duy tr tt ng bay  Nng -  Lt. C th: tng s v khuyn mi t 20% ln 50%  h tr cc doanh nghip l hnh; thay ATR 72 bng my bay ln hn, ng thi sm thng bo k hoch bn v cho cc doanh nghip du lch.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: right; padding-top: 5px; padding-right: 25px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; font-weight: bold; color: #333333;">(Theo Tin phong)</div>\r\n</div>', '', 1, 6, 0, 38, '2012-02-04 04:22:56', 64, '', '2012-02-04 04:33:48', 64, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-02-04 04:22:56', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 3, 0, 7, '', '', 0, 44, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(273, 'V my bay dp tt: Gii bi ton lch u', 've-may-bay-dp-tt-gii-bai-toan-lch-u', '', '<div style="font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; width: 200px; margin: 0px 15px 5px 0px; float: left; position: relative; color: #000000; line-height: normal; text-align: left;"><img src="http://anh.24h.com.vn:8008/upload/4-2010/images/2010-11-04/1288831976_ve-may-bay.jpg" border="0" alt="V my bay dp tt: Gii bi ton lch u" width="200" height="200" style="border: 1px initial initial;" />\r\n<div style="font-size: 11px; padding-top: 5px; padding-bottom: 5px; text-align: center; color: #666666;">Nhiu  kin lo ngi tng gi trn s khng kim sot c gi v my bay.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; float: left; width: 323px; color: #000000; line-height: normal; text-align: left;">\r\n<h1 style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: #1d8a0d; padding-bottom: 5px; margin: 0px;">V my bay t TP.HCM ra pha Bc dp trc tt gn nh  khng cn. Tuy nhin, cc hng hng khng cho bit h hon ton c th gii quyt c nhu cu lch u nh hin nay nu c tng gi trn.</h1>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; padding-bottom: 10px; color: #000000; line-height: normal; text-align: left;">\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;">\r\n<div>\r\n<p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><br /><br /><br /><br /></p>\r\n<p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"></p>\r\n<p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">Cc hng hng khng cho rng tng gi trn khng ng ngha vi tng gi v v tng gi trn chnh l c tng gi v v gim gi v, tng bin  gia gi cao nht v gi thp nht, c cu phn b ch trn chuyn bay cho cc mc gi v khc nhau s a dng hn.</p>\r\n<p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">Sn sng thu my bay</p>\r\n<p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">ng bay c nhiu hnh khch nht hin nay l TP.HCM - H Ni hin c ba hng hng khng Vietnam Airlines (VNA), Air Mekong (AM), Jetstar Pacific Airlines (JPA) khai thc trung bnh 32-34 chuyn/ngy, tng ng khong 9.000 ch. i din ba hng hng khng ny cho bit hin lng v bay t TP.HCM - H Ni cho khong thi gian trc tt  gn nh khng cn, k c ch thng gia, trong khi  chiu H Ni - TP.HCM cn nhiu ch.</p>\r\n<p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">Chnh v vy, cc hng hng khng ny cho rng nu nng mc gi trn hng ph thng hin nay (1,819 triu ng/v/chiu, cha thu) h hon ton c th tng gi chiu c nhu cu cao  b p chiu bay c t khch nhm cn i doanh thu. Vi mt chiu TP.HCM - H Ni (trc tt) t 100% s gh, chiu cn li ch khong 50% nn rt kh cho hng khi phi tng chuyn, thu thm my bay  p ng nhu cu i li khng bnh thng ca hnh khch.</p>\r\n<p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">Ph tng gim c JPA T Hu Thanh khng nh nu c tng mc gi trn, JPA hon ton c th thu my bay  chu u (lc ny ang l ma ng, c nhiu my bay nm khng) v khai thc ngn trong 2-3 tun trc, sau tt.</p>\r\n<p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">Tht ra, vic thu my bay  p ng nhu cu gia tng bt cht khng mi  th trng VN, bi trc  chnh JPA v VNA tng thu my bay  nc ngoi kinh doanh trong thi gian ngn. Tuy nhin cc hng ny vn cn ch  kin tng gi trn chng bay trn  c k hoch thu my bay, tng chuyn.</p>\r\n<p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">Cha th b gi trn</p>\r\n<p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">Theo thng t 103 ca lin b Ti chnh - Giao thng vn ti, cc hng hng khng c quyt nh gi v trn cc ng bay cnh tranh c t hai hng tr ln khai thc. ng bay TP.HCM - H Ni hin c ba hng hng khng VNA, JPA v AM cng khai thc.</p>\r\n<p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">Tuy c chnh lch v th phn, tn sut (VNA chim nhnh hn 50% chuyn bay) nhng vic c ba hng cng bay mt ng bay r rng l c cnh tranh. Tuy nhin, B GTVT vn cha cho php thc hin thng t 103 v lo ngi khng c cng c can thip khi cc hng tng gi qu .</p>\r\n<p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">Trao i viPV v vn  ny, ng Li Xun Thanh, ph cc trng Cc Hng khng VN, tha nhn vi c th kinh doanh lch u nh dp tt  VN th kh c hng hng khng no p ng c. Tuy nhin, ng Thanh khng nh vn  tng gi trn v ng bay trn trong dp tt ni ring v dp cao im ni chung l vn  nhy cm vi ngi tiu dng nn n v ny cha ng  tng gi trn. Chuyn g s xy ra khi nhu cu i li dp tt bng n v cc hng hng khng nhn c hi ny bt cht ngi tiu dng, y gi ln cao, iu ny s to mt p lc v gi rt ln cho x hi - ng Thanh ni.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '', 1, 6, 0, 38, '2012-02-04 04:34:33', 64, '', '2012-02-04 08:01:35', 64, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-02-04 04:34:33', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 3, 0, 6, '', '', 0, 44, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(276, 'Cu ha bng trc thng  Vit Nam cha kh thi', 'cu-ha-bng-trc-thng-vit-nam-cha-kh-thi', '', '<table style="width: 100%;" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="10"><br /></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div><span style="color: #000080;"><span style="font-size: 13pt;"><strong><br /> </strong></span></span></div>\r\n<table style="width: 150px;" border="0" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" align="left">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div><a id="thumb1" href="http://www.vemaybay24.com/ve-may-bay/air-ticket/uploads/News/pic/1324430142.nv.jpg"><img src="http://www.vemaybay24.com/ve-may-bay/air-ticket/uploads/News/pic/small_1324430142.nv.jpg" border="0" alt="Xem hnh" width="150" /></a></div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center">My bay trc thng tham gia cu h ngi dn  vng l lt. nh: Hng Nguyn.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<strong> Trong khi Ch tch H Ni  ngh trang b trc thng  cu h chy cao  c th i din hng khng v Cc Cnh st phng chy cha chy u cho  rng vic ny cha kh thi v lin quan ti ti chnh, bi , iu  kin bay...</strong>\r\n<p align="justify">Mt ngy sau v chy thp EVN cao  33 tng  ph Ca Bc (H Ni), UBND  H Ni  c cuc hp khn cp vi  lnh o s, ngnh ca thnh ph.  Ln u tin Ch tch H Ni Nguyn  Th Tho  ngh, phi tnh n  vic trang b my bay trc thng  khi  xy chy nh cao tng c th  cu h d dng hn.</p>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;">Ngi ng u  thnh ph t cu hi cho cc lnh o s, ngnh v sao  khng nh n  trc thng qun i v nu trc thng n th thang dy  c th cu nhanh  hn nhng ngi mc kt trn nc nh.<br /><br />Tuy nhin, trao i vi  VnExpress.net, i din pha hng khng v phng chy cha chy u cho  rng vic cu ha, cu h  nh cao tng bng trc thng hin nay l  cha kh thi v khng th thc hin.<br /><br />Theo nh chc trch hng  khng,  m bo cng tc cu h ti cc ta nh cao tng, trc thng  cn tun th iu kin nht nh v mt k thut nh phi c t nht 2  ng c, c th chuyn ch 5-10 ngi lm cng tc cu h... Tuy nhin,  cc dng my bay kiu ny thng rt t, gi cho bn khong 12 triu  USD cho n vi chc triu USD.<br /><br />"Doanh nghip t nhn khng my  mn m trin khai dch v ny v rt tn km v gi tr s dng khng  cao", lnh o ny chia s.  Vit Nam, i bay trc thng ang c  khai thc bi 2 n v l Tng cng ty Bay dch v min Nam, min Bc v  B Quc phng. Nhng c hai i bay ch yu phc v nhu cu m bo an  ninh quc gia ch khng phc v cu h, cu ha.<br /><br />Ngoi vn   kinh ph mua sm my bay, Ph gim c S Cnh st PCCC TP HCM L Tn  Bu cn cho hay, vn  khng lu, quy ch bay, bo dng, i ng phi  cng... cng kh phc tp bi khng phi mua my bay v l dng ngay, c  khi my nm mi s dng n, rt d h hng.<br /><br />ng quan im, i  t Nguyn Vn Ti, Cc ph Cnh st Phng chy cha chy (B Cng an)  cho bit, my bay trc thng cng l mt trong nhng phng tin c s  dng  cha chy nhng vn phi ph thuc vo kinh t t nc. H Ni   cp n kh nng u t trc thng cu h, cu ha, nhng thnh ph  cn phi tnh ti c chi ph bo tr, bo dng, phi cng...<br /><br />Mt  vng mc khc l bi  cho sn bay trc thng. Hin rt t ta nh cao  tng ca Vit Nam c sn bay ring c xy dng trn c s chun mc  v ti trng,  cao v din tch. Trong khi cc nc, cc ta nh ln  thng c sn bay v nu xy ra chy, trc thng c th  trn nc ta  nh bn cnh, t  phun nc dp tt m chy.<br /><br />Vit Nam tng s  dng trc trng  dp tt mt s m chy rng, tuy nhin vi chy ta  nh cao tng trong thnh ph th gp rt nhiu kh khn. V thnh ph b  bao bc bi cc ta nh cao tng, h thng dy cp, ct sng di ng v  nhiu thit b khin my bay hot ng khng an ton.<br /><br />"Bn   thnh ph khng cp nht phn tnh khng,  cao cho php hot ng ca  my bay. Nu phi cu h, cu nn vo m ti, phi cng s khng bit  ng m bay", mt cn b ca Cc Hng khng chia s.<br /><br />Cng theo  cn b ny, cc my bay ch c th cu h cu nn i vi nhng s c l  thin nh chy rng. Vi cc ta nh cao tng c thit k khp kn,  ngun chy khng xc nh, ch thy khi bc cao, nu s dng my bay  trc thng th nc xung ta nh th cng khng hiu qu.<br /><br />"Gi  s im chy  ngang hng ta nh, my bay khng th can thip v n ch  c th bay trn nc, ch khng th bay ngang phun nc vo", anh ny  ni v cho bit thm nh cng cao, chy cng ln th cng lm my bay  khng th treo cao  cu h c ( cao treo c  cu h t l  nghch vi ti trng my bay v nc cha chy).<br /><br />Ngoi nhng l  do trn, mt bt cp khc l th tc php l.  Vit Nam, dch v trc  thng cu h cha c hnh lang php l. My bay lin quan n an ton,  an ninh vng tri nn sau s kin khng b 11/9, Vit Nam v mt s quc  gia cng sit cht hn vn  ny.<br /><br />Theo quy nh hin nay, qun  i qun l vng tri. Mt chuyn bay thng mi th xin php mt 8 gi,  chuyn bay cu nn (lt li, cp cu) phi mt 3 gi. Tt c trng hp  xin cu h, cu nn, cng ty phi bo cho Qun chng phng khng khng  qun, ri mi xin php theo ngnh dc.  hon tt th tc ny mt nhiu  thi gian.<br /><br />Vi nhng bt cp nu trn, nh chc trch hng khng  cho rng  s dng my bay trc thng trong cu h cu nn cc v chy  nh cao tng th cn thit lp mt hng lang php l, c mt i bay  ring, c hun luyn chu o v phi trc 24/24h nh lnh cu ha. Phi  cng phi gii, tinh nhu, c o to chuyn su v phng chy cha  chy. My bay phi c thit k ring phc v cho cng tc ny.</div>\r\n<br /> <br /><br />\r\n<p align="right"><strong>Khut Hng</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="10"><br /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', '', 1, 6, 0, 38, '2012-02-04 08:31:13', 64, '', '2012-02-04 08:34:13', 64, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-02-04 08:31:13', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 2, 0, 3, '', '', 0, 42, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(274, 'Tng gi v my bay l bt kh khng?', 'tng-gia-ve-may-bay-la-bt-kh-khang', '', '<div style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; width: 200px; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; float: left; position: relative; color: #000000; line-height: normal; text-align: left;"><img src="http://img-hcm.24hstatic.com:8008/upload/4-2011/images/2011-12-28/1325062441_ve-may-bay.jpg" border="0" alt="Tng gi v my bay l bt kh khng?" width="200" height="200" style="border: 1px initial initial;" />\r\n<div style="font-size: 11px; padding-top: 5px; padding-bottom: 5px; text-align: center; color: #666666;">ng Thanh cho bit: i vi gi r hay khng gi r th u phi m bo an ton ging nhau.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; float: left; width: 323px; color: #000000; line-height: normal; text-align: left;">\r\n<h1 style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: #1d8a0d; padding-bottom: 5px; margin: 0px;"><span style="text-align: justify; font-size: 11px; color: #000000; ">Xung quanh vic Vietnam Airlines tng gi v my bay, ng Li Xun Thanh, Ph Cc trng Cc hng khng Vit Nam (B GTVT) cho bit: Ti chia s vi vic ny, nhng vic tng gi v c th ni l bt kh khng. Cc Hng khng cng B Ti Chnh, Cc qun l gi  lm vic c na nm nay ri mi a ra quyt nh.</span></h1>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; padding-bottom: 10px; color: #000000; line-height: normal; text-align: left;">\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;">\r\n<div>\r\n<p>ng Li xun Thanh  c cuc trao i vi bo gii:</p>\r\n<p>- Nhiu ngi cho rng, Vietnam Airlines tng gi vo thi im ny l khng hp l khi Tt ang cn k, mi th u i gi, tng thm gnh nng cho ngi tiu dng?</p>\r\n<p>Ti thy c chia s vi vic ny! Nhng vic nng trn khung gi nh nc  tnh tt c nhng yu t cp bch, cp thit  c nhng quyt nh nh vy. Cc Hng khng cng B Ti Chnh, Cc qun l gi  lm vic c na nm nay.</p>\r\n<p><em>- Ni nh ng th vic tng gi l iu bt kh khng?</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://img-hcm.24hstatic.com:8008/upload/4-2011/images/2011-12-28/1325062341-ong-lai-xuan-thanh.jpg" border="0" alt="Tng gi v my bay l bt kh khng?, Th trng - Tiu dng, ve may bay, hang khong, gia gia, kinh te, giam gia, tang gia, bao" style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial;" /><br /><br /><span><em>ng Li Xun Thanh.</em></span></p>\r\n<p>C th ni l bt kh khng! C 2 ch o chung: th nht l phi tnh li nhun kinh doanh cho cc hng hng khng, v ngi ta c lm n tt mi m rng mng li, phc v cng ng tt, nu khng s rt kh khn trong vic pht trin.</p>\r\n<p>Ngoi kinh doanh, ngnh hng khng cn ng gp vo kinh t vng a phng. Nu khng to iu kin thun li cho h, li chnh l nh hng ti cng ng khi nhu cu ca nhiu a phng cn rt ln vi mong mun c ng bay ti qu hng mnh. Thm na, khng phi ton b dn c, cng ng u i my bay.</p>\r\n<p><em>- Vic tng gi v my bay va qua c nh hng ti gi r?</em></p>\r\n<p>Thc ra, gi r cn mun tng hn na,  m bo kinh doanh c bit cc hng hng khng nh ch mi kinh doanh ni a, cha c kinh doanh cc chuyn quc t nh Vietnam Airlines, h mun tng hn na nhng Nh nc c nhng quyt nh v l trnh nht nh.</p>\r\n<p>Vic iu chnh khung trn v khung gi va ri thc s cha p ng c mong mi ca cc hng hng khng, nhng Nh nc phi cn i li ch ca doanh nghip, ca ngi tiu dng.</p>\r\n<p>Nh nc  ra mc trn khung gi cn cc hng ph thuc vo sn phm ca mnh, ph thuc vo phng thc cnh tranh  a ra cc mc gi khc nhau. Mi hng hng khng s c mc gi khc nhau ch khng c nh v h thng gi s mang tnh cnh tranh.</p>\r\n<p><em>- ng nh gi nh th no v phng thc kinh doanh hng khng gi r?</em></p>\r\n<p>Thc ra, gi r l phng thc kinh doanh, khng phi ngu nhin cc nh u t, cc nh kinh doanh ngh ra  mnh thua l. Trn th gii cng c nhiu nc thnh cng vi phng thc hng khng gi r. Khng phi t dng h ngh ra mt phng thc lm n thua l.</p>\r\n<p>Th gii c nhiu loi hnh kinh doanh khc nhau v  l quyn la chn ca mi doanh nghip hng khng.<br /><br />Khng phi Vietnam Airlines l khng c gi r. Khng ai gi l hng hng khng gi cao m ngi ta gi l hng truyn thng v hng truyn thng cng cnh tranh khng km g hng hng khng gi r, ch khc l hng hng khng gi r ch quan tm ti phn khc trung bnh thi.</p>\r\n<p><em>- Phn khc th trng gi r ca hng khng Vit Nam hin nay nh th no?</em></p>\r\n<p>i vi nc mnh th phn khc th trng gi r vn y tim nng.<br /><em><br />- ng nh gi nh th no khi c thm hng hng khng gi r VietJetAir ra i?</em></p>\r\n<p>Vi s c mt ca VietJetAir, chc chn s c s cnh tranh gia cc hng hng khng trong iu kin cc hng c ton quyn chn la k hoch kinh doanh ca mnh.</p>\r\n<p>Trn cc ng bay chnh, chc chn s cnh tranh s rt ln, cc hng cnh tranh rt si ni.</p>\r\n<p><em>- Nu i my bay liu ng c chn gi r?</em></p>\r\n<p>Ti sao khng, gi r c khi cn thi gian mi mua c v gi r. Ti ph trch c an ton, an ninh hng khng nn i vi gi r hay khng r th u phi m bo an ton ging nhau. Ch khc nhau  phng thc kinh doanh, phng thc cnh tranh.</p>\r\n<p><em>-  tng gi v b l, ngoi phng n tng gi v th cn phng n no khc?</em></p>\r\n<p> l quyn li v cng l nhim v ca cc hng hng khng. Mun cnh tranh c phi su st v quyt lit trong vic gim chi ph gi thnh,  l nhng yu cu ht sc ln. c bit, nhng doanh nghip nh nc nh Vietnam Airlines phi c nhng bin php rt c th  gim gi thnh.</p>\r\n<p>C nhiu bin php  gim gi thnh, trong  c qun l, t chc, c cu qun l, cc yu t u vo gi thnh nh vt t, xng du.</p>\r\n<p><em>- Xin cm n ng!</em></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '', 1, 6, 0, 38, '2012-02-04 04:44:59', 64, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-02-04 04:44:59', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 5, '', '', 0, 39, 'robots=\nauthor=');
