(1, 61, 'Getting Started', 'getting-started', '<p>It''s easy to get started creating your website. Knowing some of the basics will help.</p><h3>What is a Content Management System?</h3><p>A content management system is software that allows you to create and manage webpages easily by separating the creation of your content from the mechanics required to present it on the web.</p><p>In this site, the content is stored in a <em>database</em>. The look and feel are created by a <em>template</em>. Joomla! brings together the template and your content to create web pages.</p><h3>Logging in</h3><p>To login to your site use the user name and password that were created as part of the installation process. Once logged-in you will be able to create and edit articles and modify some settings.</p><h3>Creating an article</h3><p>Once you are logged-in, a new menu will be visible. To create a new article, click on the "Submit Article" link on that menu.</p><p>The new article interface gives you a lot of options, but all you need to do is add a title and put something in the content area. To make it easy to find, set the state to published.</p><div>You can edit an existing article by clicking on the edit icon (this only displays to users who have the right to edit).</div><h3>Template, site settings, and modules</h3><p>The look and feel of your site is controlled by a template. You can change the site name, background colour, highlights colour and more by editing the template settings. Click the "Template Settings" in the user menu.</p><p>The boxes around the main content of the site are called modules. You can modify modules on the current page by moving your cursor to the module and clicking the edit link. Always be sure to save and close any module you edit.</p><p>You can change some site settings such as the site name and description by clicking on the "Site Settings" link.</p><p>More advanced options for templates, site settings, modules, and more are available in the site administrator.</p><h3>Site and Administrator</h3><p>Your site actually has two separate sites. The site (also called the front end) is what visitors to your site will see. The administrator (also called the back end) is only used by people managing your site. You can access the administrator by clicking the "Site Administrator" link on the "User Menu" menu (visible once you login) or by adding /administrator to the end of your domain name. The same user name and password are used for both sites.</p><h3>Learn more</h3><p>There is much more to learn about how to use Joomla! to create the web site you envision. You can learn much more at the <a href="https://docs.joomla.org" target="_blank">Joomla! documentation site</a> and on the<a href="http://forum.joomla.org" target="_blank"> Joomla! forums</a>.</p>', '', 1, 2, '2013-11-16 00:00:00', 639, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2013-11-16 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 1, 1, '', '', 1, 22, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(2, 70, 'Khi bng Sanchez ngy mt m nht  Arsenal', 'khi-bong-sanchez-ngay-m-t-m-nh-t-arsenal', '<h2 class="fon33 mt1 sapo" style="margin: 5px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 16px; line-height: 18px; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; color: #5f5f5f;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 5px; color: #ffffff; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.3; font-family: arial; background-color: #1a7900;">Dn tr</span>u ma gii, Arsenal c xem l i bng mt ngi vi s xut sc ca Sanchez nhng  thi im ny, khi ci bng ca tin o ngi Chile ngy mt m nht, Pho th li tr nn ng s hn.</h2>\r\n', '\r\n<p></p>\r\n<div class="fon34 mt3 mr2 fon43 detail-content" style="margin: 15px 10px 9.390625px 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; color: #000000; line-height: 20px !important;">\r\n<p style="margin: 9.1875px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt;"><b style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span lang="EN-US" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">Khi Sanchez tt ngm</span></b></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 9.1875px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">Nhiu ngi t hi rng Alexis Sanchez  bin mt  u trong thi gian qua. K t ln cui cng lp c p vo li Stoke City (ngy 11/1), tin o ngi Chile  khng th xuyn thng mnh li i phng v ch c 1 pha kin to thnh bn.</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 9.1875px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt;"></p>\r\n<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" align="center"><img style="margin: 5px; padding: 0px; border: none; max-width: 465px;" src="http://dantri4.vcmedia.vn/n8vmfhDcg3kQo1febccccccccccccr/Image/2015/01/sanchez-9f076.jpg" alt="Alexis\r\nSanchez tt dc trong thi gian qua" width="455" align="middle" /><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Tahoma; font-size: 10pt;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" />Alexis Sanchez tt dc trong thi gian qua</span><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" /><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" /></div>\r\n<p style="margin: 9.1875px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt;"></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 9.1875px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">Hay ni cch khc, phong  ca Alexis Sanchez  ma gii ny chia lm hai giai on, trc v sau trn u vi Man City (ngy 18/1). Trong giai on 1, tin o ngi Chile  ta sng rc r vi phong  n tng v mt mnh ko Arsenal trn BXH nhng sau , ci bng ca cu th ny tr nn v cng nht nha vi phong  xung dc trm trng.</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 9.1875px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">Mi con s thng k u ch ra thc t . Trc ngy 18/1, Alexis Sanchez ch cn 91,9 pht  t du giy vo 1 bn thng ca Arsenal nhng gi y, con s   ln thnh510 pht.</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 9.1875px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">Tng t, trc , c sau 37,6 pht, tin o ngi Chile li c 1 ln bn ph khung thnh i phng (57,5 pht cho c dt im trng khung thnh) th hin ti, cu th ny mt ti 39,2 pht cho mt c dt im (102 pht cho c bn ph trng khung thnh).</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 9.1875px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">S h tr ca Alexis Sanchez cng gim hn. Trc ngy 18/1, tin o ny mt 33,5 pht  c ng kin to c hi (74 ng kin to sau 2481 pht). Hin ti, Alexis Sanchez phi cn ti 42,5 pht (12 ln kin to sau 510 pht). Do , s ng chuyn thnh bn ca cu th ny cng gim hn (9 so vi 1).</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 9.1875px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt;"></p>\r\n<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" align="center"><img style="margin: 5px; padding: 0px; border: none; max-width: 465px;" src="http://dantri4.vcmedia.vn/n8vmfhDcg3kQo1febccccccccccccr/Image/2015/01/sanchez1-9f076.jpg" alt="Tm hot ng\r\nca Sanchez  b thu hp sau khi Ozil tr li" width="455" align="middle" /><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Tahoma; font-size: 10pt;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" />Tm hot ng ca Sanchez  b thu hp sau khi Ozil tr li</span><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" /><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" /></div>\r\n<p style="margin: 9.1875px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt;"></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 9.1875px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt;"><b style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span lang="EN-US" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">S tr li ca Mesut Ozil trit Sanchez?</span></b></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 9.1875px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">C nhiu nguyn nhn c ch ra  l gii v s tt ngm ca Alexis Sanchez trong giai on 2 ma gii ny. Th nht, tin o ny vn cn b nh hng bi chn thng gn khoeo gp phi u thng 1 (ngh trn gp Aston Villa, Tottenham). Bn cnh , tin o ny cha th quen vi vic phi thi u lin tc (khng ngh ng) trong ma gii u tin thi u  Premier League. Tnh trng ny tng t vi Mesut Ozil  ma gii trc.</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 9.1875px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">Tuy nhin, d mun hay khng cng phi tha nhn rng s tr li ca Mesut Ozil cng nh hng khng nh ti phong  ca Sanchez. Khng phi ngu nhin giai on Ozil tr li v thi u n tng li ng vo thi im m tin o ngi Chile i xung. Ngc li, trong lc tin v ngi c dng thng cng l thi im m Sanchez thng hoa nht.</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 9.1875px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt;"></p>\r\n<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" align="center"><img style="margin: 5px; padding: 0px; border: none; max-width: 465px;" src="http://dantri4.vcmedia.vn/n8vmfhDcg3kQo1febccccccccccccr/Image/2015/01/bandoozil-9f076.jpg" alt="Mesut Ozil\r\nhot ng  khu vc trung tm (bn  nhit trong trn gp Crystal Palace)" width="455" align="middle" /><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Tahoma; font-size: 10pt;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" />Mesut Ozil hot ng  khu vc trung tm (bn  nhit trong trn gp Crystal Palace)</span><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" /><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" /></div>\r\n<p style="margin: 9.1875px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt;"></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 9.1875px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">Ai cng bit, Alexis Sanchez vn l cu th a hot ng t do v rt rng. Do , s xut hin ca Mesut Ozil, trong vai tr s 10,  phn no cn tr tin o ngi Chile. Bn  v s hot ng ca Alexis Sanchez trong trn u vi Stoke (trc khi Ozil tr li) v trn gp Everton gn y  cho thy rng cu cu th ca Barcelona b b buc kh nhiu  cnh tri.</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 9.1875px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">Chnh iu  khin Alexis Sanchez d dng b i phng bt cht v tm nh hng ca cu th ny ng nhin s gim st. Trong trn gp Stoke, Sanchez tung ra 4 c dt im v 5 ng kin to c hi (ghi 2 bn, c 1 ng chuyn thnh bn).  trn gp Everton va qua, tin o ngi Chile ch c 2 c dt im v 2 ng kin to c hi.</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 9.1875px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">D sao, iu ng mng cho Arsenal khi CLB li thi u thng hoa (thng 6/7 trn gn nht  Premier League) trong giai on Alexis Sanchez thi u sa st. iu  cho thy tm nh hng ca ca cu th ny  khng cn  Pho th. Thay vo , h ang bay cao vi phong  xut sc ca Giroud, Ozil.</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 9.1875px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">Mc d vy, iu  khng c ngha rng Arsenal khng cn Alexis Sanchez. Nhng CV i bng ny vn mong ngng ngy tr li ca cu th s 17. Ch nh vy, li chi ca i bng thnh London mi tr nn a dng v kh on nh hn. y l iu quan trng vi Pho th trong cuc ua ginh tp 4  ma gii ny.</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 9.1875px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt;" align="right"><b style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span lang="EN-US" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">H.Long</span></b></p>\r\n</div>', 1, 12, '2015-03-05 01:32:05', 639, '', '2015-03-05 02:12:27', 639, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2015-03-05 01:32:05', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 4, 0, '', '', 1, 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(3, 75, 'Man Utd thng pht cui sau sai lm ca i th', 'man-utd-th-ng-phut-cu-i-sau-sai-l-m-c-a-d-i-th', '<div class="short_intro txt_666" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; color: #444444; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; width: 480.015625px; float: left; text-rendering: geometricprecision;">Ashley Young ghi bn duy nht  pht 89 gip Man Utd nh bi Newcastle vi t s 1-0  vng 28 Ngoi hng Anh.</div>\r\n<div class="short_intro txt_666" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; color: #444444; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; width: 480.015625px; float: left; text-rendering: geometricprecision;">', '</div>\r\n<div class="relative_new" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 5px; width: 480.015625px; float: left; color: #000000; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;">\r\n<ul class="list_news_dot_3x3_300" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; width: 480.015625px; float: left; border: none; color: #666666;">\r\n<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 5px 10px; list-style-type: none; background: url(''http://st.f3.vnecdn.net/responsive/c/v57/images/graphics/bg_dot_gray_3x3.gif'') 0px 6px no-repeat;"><a style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #666666; outline: 1px; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 16px;" title="Van Gaal cho Di Maria mt nm  ha nhp" href="http://thethao.vnexpress.net/tin-tuc/giai-ngoai-hang-anh/van-gaal-cho-di-maria-mot-nam-de-hoa-nhap-3153100.html">Van Gaal cho Di Maria mt nm  ha nhp</a>/<a style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #666666; outline: 1px; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 16px;" title="Shearer ch Van Gaal v Ryan Giggs khng bit cch gip Falcao" href="http://thethao.vnexpress.net/tin-tuc/giai-ngoai-hang-anh/shearer-che-van-gaal-va-ryan-giggs-khong-biet-cach-giup-falcao-3152364.html">Shearer ch Van Gaal v Ryan Giggs khng bit cch gip Falcao</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="fck_detail width_common" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 9.59375px 10px 0px; width: 470.40625px; float: left; overflow: hidden; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal;">\r\n<table class="tplCaption" style="margin: 0px auto 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; width: 470px;" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="3" align="center">\r\n<tbody style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 0;"><img style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 0px; line-height: 0; max-width: 100%; width: 470px;" src="http://m.f1.img.vnecdn.net/2015/03/05/m1-3634-1425508521.jpg" alt="m1-3634-1425508521.jpg" data-width="490" data-pwidth="470.40625" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 0;">\r\n<p class="Image" style="margin: 0px; padding: 10px; line-height: normal; text-rendering: geometricprecision; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; background: #f5f5f5;">Cu th Man Utd n mng sau bn thng  pht 89. nh:<em style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">Reuters.</em></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; text-rendering: geometricprecision;">Pha lp cng ca Ashley Young n sau khi th mn Newcastle Tim Krul chuyn bng ngay vo chn anh trong vng 16m50. Trong tnh hung ny, Tim Krul  b Rooney gy sc p nn khng th ph bng ln trn v gip Young ghi bn n nh chin thng 1-0.</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; text-rendering: geometricprecision;">Ba im trn sn St James Park gip Man Utd tr li  v tr th t trong vng u m nhng i xp sau h nh Liverpool, Southampton v Tottenham u ginh chin thng.</p>\r\n<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;"></div>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; text-rendering: geometricprecision;">Chin thng trc Newcastle mt ln na cho thy Man Utd vn c th ginh kt qu tch cc khi khng t phong  tt. Ngi sao Di Maria trong trn th hai lin tip phi ri sn sm sau khi c mn trnh din nht nha. Trong khi  tin o Falcao thm ch khng c HLV Van Gaal tung vo sn. Thay vo , chin lc gia ngi H Lan s dng Fellaini  cp vi Rooney trn hng cng.</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; text-rendering: geometricprecision;">Man Utd may mn thot pht n ngay u trn khi trng ti b qua tnh hung Smalling phm li vi Riviere trong vng 16m50. n cui hip mt, trng tiAnthony Taylor tip tc b qua tnh hung phn cm gia Jonny Evans v Papiss Cisse. Trung v Man Utd v tin o Newcastle c hnh vi nh nc bt vo nhau sau khi lin tc va chm.</p>\r\n<table class="tplCaption" style="margin: 0px auto 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; width: 470px;" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="3" align="center">\r\n<tbody style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 0;"><img style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 0px; line-height: 0; max-width: 100%; width: 470px;" src="http://m.f1.img.vnecdn.net/2015/03/05/m3-7250-1425509962.jpg" alt="m3-7250-1425509962.jpg" data-width="490" data-pwidth="470.40625" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 0;">\r\n<p class="Image" style="margin: 0px; padding: 10px; line-height: normal; text-rendering: geometricprecision; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; background: #f5f5f5;">De Gea dng tay cn c  cn thnh ca Riviere. nh:<em style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">Reuters.</em></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; text-rendering: geometricprecision;">De Gea mt ln na chi tt  trn ny v to nim tin cho cc ng i. Th thnh Ty Ban Nha cn ph xut sc c dt im cn thnh ca Riviere v c nh u ca trung v Coloccini.</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; text-rendering: geometricprecision;">Pha bn kia, th mn Tim Krul thm ch cn c nhng pha cn ph xut thn hn. Th thnh H Lan c hai pha cu thua lin tip trc nhng pha dt im trong vng 16m50 ca Fellaini v Ashley Young. Tuy nhin n lc ca Tim Krul trong c trn u   i khi anh mc sai lm cui trn khin i nh tht bi.</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; text-rendering: geometricprecision;">Ngay sau bn thng ca Man Utd, Papiss Cisse c c hi g ha cho Newcastle nhng mt ln na De Gea li tr thnh cu tinh khi ngn cn c nh u t c ly hn su mt ca tin o i phng.</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; text-rendering: geometricprecision;">y mi l chin thng th t sau 14 trn sn khch ti Ngoi hng Anh ma ny ca Man Utd.</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; text-rendering: geometricprecision;"></p>\r\n<div class="embed-container" style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px 0px 658.5625px; position: relative; height: 0px; overflow: hidden;"></div>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p class="Normal" style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; text-rendering: geometricprecision; text-align: right;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">Bo Lam</strong></p>\r\n</div>', 1, 12, '2015-03-05 02:13:13', 639, '', '2015-03-05 02:13:37', 639, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2015-03-05 02:13:13', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_pri