(4, 76, 'Arsenal v Liverpool cng thng, gi la cuc ua Top 4', 'arsenal-va-liverpool-cung-th-ng-gi-l-a-cu-c-dua-top-4', '<div class="short_intro txt_666" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; color: #444444; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; font-family: arial; width: 480.015625px; float: left; text-rendering: geometricprecision;">Pho th c chin thng 2-1 trc QPR, trong khi L on  nh bi Burnley 2-0  vng 28 gii Ngoi hng Anh, hm 4/3.</div>\r\n<div class="short_intro txt_666" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; color: #444444; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; font-family: arial; width: 480.015625px; float: left; text-rendering: geometricprecision;">', '</div>\r\n<div class="relative_new" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 5px; width: 480.015625px; float: left; color: #000000; font-family: arial; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;">\r\n<ul class="list_news_dot_3x3_300" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; width: 480.015625px; float: left; border: none; color: #666666;">\r\n<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 5px 10px; list-style-type: none; background: url(''http://st.f3.vnecdn.net/responsive/c/v57/images/graphics/bg_dot_gray_3x3.gif'') 0px 6px no-repeat;"><a style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #666666; outline: 1px; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 16px;" title="Wenger: ''Arsenal cha t b chc v ch Ngoi hng Anh''" href="http://thethao.vnexpress.net/tin-tuc/giai-ngoai-hang-anh/wenger-arsenal-chua-tu-bo-chuc-vo-dich-ngoai-hang-anh-3153322.html">Wenger: ''Arsenal cha t b chc v ch Ngoi hng Anh''</a>/<a style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #666666; outline: 1px; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 16px;" title="HLV Liverpool rng mnh khi ngh ti gi Coutinho" href="http://thethao.vnexpress.net/tin-tuc/giai-ngoai-hang-anh/hlv-liverpool-rung-minh-khi-nghi-toi-gia-coutinho-3151954.html">HLV Liverpool rng mnh khi ngh ti gi Coutinho</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="fck_detail width_common" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 9.59375px 10px 0px; width: 470.40625px; float: left; overflow: hidden; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: arial;">\r\n<table class="tplCaption" style="margin: 0px auto 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; width: 470px;" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="3" align="center">\r\n<tbody style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 0;"><img style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 0px; line-height: 0; max-width: 100%; width: 470px;" src="http://m.f1.img.vnecdn.net/2015/03/05/2652E05C00000578-2979784-image-5748-7115-1425510838.jpg" alt="2652E05C00000578-2979784-image-5748-7115" data-natural-="" data-width="500" data-pwidth="470.40625" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 0;">\r\n<p class="Image" style="margin: 0px; padding: 10px; line-height: normal; text-rendering: geometricprecision; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; background: #f5f5f5;">Giroud  ghi nm bn trong nm trn gn nht. nh:<em style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">KQ.</em></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p class="Normal" style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; text-rendering: geometricprecision;">Ha vo khng kh chung ca cc i bng mnh trong vng u gia tun, c Arsenal v Liverpool u ginh trn ba im trc nhng i bng ang ngp ngh khu vc xung hng. Liverpool trn sn nh c chin thng d dng trc Burnley bng cc pha lp cng ca Jordan Henderson v Daniel Sturridge.</p>\r\n<p class="Normal" style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; text-rendering: geometricprecision;">Arsenal cht vt hn, mi n pht 64 mi c bn m t s, c ghi bi Oliver Giroud. Nm pht sau, Alexis Sanchez nhn i cch bit. n pht 82, ch nh QPR mi c bn rt ngn t s.</p>\r\n<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;"></div>\r\n<p class="Normal" style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; text-rendering: geometricprecision;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">Sau vng 28, th t trn bng im ca by i ng u khng c g thay i. Cuc ua ginh v d Champions League vn y khc lit khi c Man Utd, Liverpool, Arsenal, Tottenham v Southampton u c nguyn c hi. Arsenal hin xp th ba, hn Man Utd mt im v hn Liverpool ba im.</span></p>\r\n<p class="Normal" style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; text-rendering: geometricprecision;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">Trong mt chiu khc, QPR v Burnley hin xp 18 v 19, i din nguy c xung chi  gii hng nht.</span></p>\r\n<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;"></div>\r\n<p class="Normal" style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; text-rendering: geometricprecision;">QPR v Arsenal c mt hip mt kh cn bng, thm ch i ch nh cn tri hn v mt kim sot bng khi cc tin v trung tm chi tt. QPR to ra mt s c hi lm bn, trong  Austin sut m t s t c st ngay st vng cm.</p>\r\n<p class="Normal" style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; text-rendering: geometricprecision;">Pho th chi tt hn sau gi ngh. n pht 64, t mt pha phn cng nhanh, Giroud m t s cho i khch. Sanchez nhn bng khi tin vo vng cm ri chuyn sang tri cho Gibbs. Hu v tri Arsenal quyt nh st ngay, bng p ngi hu v QPR, to c hi cho Giroud dt im gc gn ghi bn.</p>\r\n<p class="Normal" style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; text-rendering: geometricprecision;">Nm pht sau, Sanchez nng t s ln 2-0 t mt n lc c nhn. Anh i bng lt lo trong vng cm, nh bi ba hu v QPR ri dt im  gc hp.</p>\r\n<p class="Normal" style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; text-rendering: geometricprecision;">Dn hai bn cha th lm ngi hm m Arsenal yn tm khi n pht 82, QPR c bn rt ngn t s. Nhng pht cn li Pho th i din vi nguy c b g ha nhng th mn Ospina  chi tt, bo ton thng li.</p>\r\n<table class="tplCaption" style="margin: 0px auto 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; width: 470px;" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="3" align="center">\r\n<tbody style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 0;"><img style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 0px; line-height: 0; max-width: 100%; width: 470px;" src="http://m.f1.img.vnecdn.net/2015/03/05/tag-reuters-9971-1425513253.jpg" alt="tag-reuters-9971-1425513253.jpg" data-natural-="" data-width="500" data-pwidth="470.40625" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 0;">\r\n<p class="Image" style="margin: 0px; padding: 10px; line-height: normal; text-rendering: geometricprecision; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; background: #f5f5f5;">Sturridge ghi bn trong ln tr li v tr chnh thc. nh:<em style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">Reuters.</em></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p class="Normal" style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; text-rendering: geometricprecision;">Liverpool tip tc gi phong  n tng khi nng chui bt bi  Ngoi hng Anh ln con s 12. Tm trn gn nht, h chin thng n by trn. Tnh t ngy u ca nm mi 2015 n nay, i ch sn Anfield c phong  tt nht gii.</p>\r\n<p class="Normal" style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; text-rendering: geometricprecision;">Thi u trn sn nh v ch n tip i c nhiu bt n nh Burnley, Liverpool kim sot trn u v c ba im nh nhng.<em style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">The Kop</em>chim 63% thi gian cm bng, tung ra 20 c dt im, trong  tm ln hng trng khung thnh.</p>\r\n<p class="Normal" style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; text-rendering: geometricprecision;">Henderson tip tc cho thy anh  kh nng thay th vai tr ca ngi n anh Steven Gerrard. Pht 29, tin v ngi Anh tung c st nh ba b  c ly 20 mt, m t s cho i ch nh.</p>\r\n<p class="Normal" style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; text-rendering: geometricprecision;">Sturridge trong ln  chnh c phong  tt. Anh lin tc lm kh hng phng ng Burnley nhng cc c st cui cng u  th mn i khch cn ph. Su pht sau gi ngh, tin o ngi Anh mi c hng nim vui lm bn. Henderson c ng chuyn di chun xc vo vng cm, to c hi cho Sturridge bt cao nh u lm rung li QPR.</p>\r\n<p class="Normal" style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; text-rendering: geometricprecision; text-align: right;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">Hu Nhn</strong></p>\r\n</div>', 1, 12, '2015-03-05 02:14:21', 639, '', '2015-03-05 02:15:35', 639, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2015-03-05 02:14:21', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 3, 0, '', '', 1, 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', '');

