<\\/table>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; text-rendering: geometricprecision;\\">Pha l\\u1eadp c\\u00f4ng c\\u1ee7a Ashley Young \\u0111\\u1ebfn sau khi th\\u1ee7 m\\u00f4n Newcastle Tim Krul chuy\\u1ec1n b\\u00f3ng ngay v\\u00e0o ch\\u00e2n anh trong v\\u00f2ng 16m50. Trong t\\u00ecnh hu\\u1ed1ng n\\u00e0y, Tim Krul \\u0111\\u00e3 b\\u1ecb Rooney g\\u00e2y s\\u1ee9c \\u00e9p n\\u00ean kh\\u00f4ng th\\u1ec3 ph\\u00e1 b\\u00f3ng l\\u00ean tr\\u00ean v\\u00e0 gi\\u00fap Young ghi b\\u00e0n \\u1ea5n \\u0111\\u1ecbnh chi\\u1ebfn th\\u1eafng 1-0.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; text-rendering: geometricprecision;\\">Ba \\u0111i\\u1ec3m tr\\u00ean s\\u00e2n St James Park gi\\u00fap Man Utd tr\\u1ee5 l\\u1ea1i \\u1edf v\\u1ecb tr\\u00ed th\\u1ee9 t\\u01b0 trong v\\u00f2ng \\u0111\\u1ea5u m\\u00e0 nh\\u1eefng \\u0111\\u1ed9i x\\u1ebfp sau h\\u1ecd nh\\u01b0 Liverpool, Southampton v\\u00e0 Tottenham \\u0111\\u1ec1u gi\\u00e0nh chi\\u1ebfn th\\u1eafng.<\\/p>\\r\\n<div style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\\">\\u00a0<\\/div>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; text-rendering: geometricprecision;\\">Chi\\u1ebfn th\\u1eafng tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc Newcastle m\\u1ed9t l\\u1ea7n n\\u1eefa cho th\\u1ea5y Man Utd v\\u1eabn c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 gi\\u00e0nh k\\u1ebft qu\\u1ea3 t\\u00edch c\\u1ef1c khi kh\\u00f4ng \\u0111\\u1ea1t phong \\u0111\\u1ed9 t\\u1ed1t. Ng\\u00f4i sao Di Maria trong tr\\u1eadn th\\u1ee9 hai li\\u00ean ti\\u1ebfp ph\\u1ea3i r\\u1eddi s\\u00e2n s\\u1edbm sau khi c\\u00f3 m\\u00e0n tr\\u00ecnh di\\u1ec5n nh\\u1ea1t nh\\u00f2a. Trong khi \\u0111\\u00f3 ti\\u1ec1n \\u0111\\u1ea1o Falcao th\\u1eadm ch\\u00ed kh\\u00f4ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c HLV Van Gaal tung v\\u00e0o s\\u00e2n. Thay v\\u00e0o \\u0111\\u00f3, chi\\u1ebfn l\\u01b0\\u1ee3c gia ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi H\\u00e0 Lan s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng Fellaini \\u0111\\u00e1 c\\u1eb7p v\\u1edbi Ro