"470.40625\\" \\/><\\/td>\\r\\n<\\/tr>\\r\\n<tr style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\\">\\r\\n<td style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 0;\\">\\r\\n<p class=\\"Image\\" style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px; line-height: normal; text-rendering: geometricprecision; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; background: #f5f5f5;\\">Giroud \\u0111\\u00e3 ghi n\\u0103m b\\u00e0n trong n\\u0103m tr\\u1eadn g\\u1ea7n nh\\u1ea5t. \\u1ea2nh:\\u00a0<em style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\\">KQ.<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/td>\\r\\n<\\/tr>\\r\\n<\\/tbody>\\r\\n<\\/table>\\r\\n<p class=\\"Normal\\" style=\\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; text-rendering: geometricprecision;\\">H\\u00f2a v\\u00e0o kh\\u00f4ng kh\\u00ed chung c\\u1ee7a c\\u00e1c \\u0111\\u1ed9i b\\u00f3ng m\\u1ea1nh trong v\\u00f2ng \\u0111\\u1ea5u gi\\u1eefa tu\\u1ea7n, c\\u1ea3 Arsenal v\\u00e0 Liverpool \\u0111\\u1ec1u gi\\u00e0nh tr\\u1ecdn ba \\u0111i\\u1ec3m tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc nh\\u1eefng \\u0111\\u1ed9i b\\u00f3ng \\u0111ang ng\\u1ea5p ngh\\u00e9 khu v\\u1ef1c xu\\u1ed1ng h\\u1ea1ng. Liverpool tr\\u00ean s\\u00e2n nh\\u00e0 c\\u00f3 chi\\u1ebfn th\\u1eafng d\\u1ec5 d\\u00e0ng tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc Burnley b\\u1eb1ng c\\u00e1c pha l\\u1eadp c\\u00f4ng c\\u1ee7a Jordan Henderson v\\u00e0 Daniel Sturridge.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"Normal\\" style=\\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; text-rendering: geometricprecision;\\">Arsenal ch\\u1eadt v\\u1eadt h\\u01a1n, m\\u00e3i \\u0111\\u1ebfn ph\\u00fat 64 m\\u1edbi c\\u00f3 b\\u00e0n m\\u1edf t\\u1ef7 s\\u1ed1, \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ghi b\\u1edfi Oliver Giroud. N\\u0103m ph\\u00fat sau, Alexis Sanchez nh\\u00e2n \\u0111\\u00f4i c\\u00e1ch bi\\u1ec7t. \\u0110\\u1ebfn ph\\u00fat 82, ch\\u1ee7 nh\\u00e0 QPR m\\u1edbi c\\u00f3 b\\u00e0n r\\u00fat ng\\u1eafn t\\u1ef7 s\\u1ed1.<\\/p>\\r\\n<div style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\\">\\u00a0<\\/div>\\r\\n<p class=\\"Normal\\" style=\\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; text-rendering: geometricprecision;\\"><span style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\\">Sau v\\u00f2ng 28, th\\u1ee9 t\\u1ef1 tr\\u00ean b\\u1ea3ng \\u0111i\\u1ec3m c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ea3y \\u0111\\u1ed9i \\u0111\\u1ee9ng \\u0111\\u1ea7u kh\\u00f4ng c\\u00f3 g\\u00ec thay \\u0111\\u1ed5i. Cu\\u1ed9c \\u0111ua gi\\u00e0nh v\\u00e9 d\\u1ef1 Champions League v\\u1eabn \\u0111\\u1ea7y kh\\u1ed1c li\\u1ec7t khi c\\u1ea3 Man Utd, Liverpool, Arsenal, Tottenham v\\u00e0 Southampton \\u0111\\u1ec1u c\\u00f3 nguy\\u00ean c\\u01a1 h\\u1ed9i. Arsenal hi\\u1ec7n x\\u1ebfp th\\u1ee9 ba, h\\u01a1n Man Utd m\\u1ed9t \\u0111i\\u1ec3m v\\u00e0 h\\u01a1n Liverpool ba \\u0111i\\u1ec3m.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"Normal\\" style=\\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; text-rendering: geometricprecision;\\"><span style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\\">Trong m\\u1ed9t chi\\u1ec1u kh\\u00e1c, QPR v\\u00e0 Burnley hi\\u1ec7n x\\u1ebfp 18 v\\u00e0 19, \\u0111\\u1ed1i di\\u1ec7n nguy c\\u01a1 xu\\u1ed1ng ch\\u01a1i \\u1edf gi\\u1ea3i h\\u1ea1ng nh\\u1ea5t.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<div style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\\">\\u00a0<\\/div>\\r\\n<p class=\\"Normal\\" style=\\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; text-rendering: geometricprecision;\\">QPR v\\u00e0 Arsenal c\\u00f3 m\\u1ed9t hi\\u1ec7p m\\u1ed9t kh\\u00e1 c\\u00e2n b\\u1eb1ng, th\\u1eadm ch\\u00ed \\u0111\\u1ed9i ch\\u1ee7 nh\\u00e0 c\\u00f2n tr\\u1ed9i h\\u01a1n v\\u1ec1 m\\u1eb7t ki\\u1ec3m so\\u00e1t b\\u00f3ng khi c\\u00e1c ti\\u1ec1n v\\u1ec7 trung t\\u00e2m ch\\u01a1i t\\u1ed1t. QPR t\\u1ea1o ra m\\u1ed9t s\\u1ed1 c\\u01a1 h\\u1ed9i l\\u00e0m b\\u00e0n, trong \\u0111\\u00f3 Austin su\\u00fdt m\\u1edf t\\u1ef7 s\\u1ed1 t\\u1eeb c\\u00fa s\\u00fat ngay s\\u00e1t v\\u00f2ng c\\u1ea5m.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"Normal\\" style=\\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; text-rendering: geometricprecision;\\">Ph\\u00e1o th\\u1ee7 ch\\u01a1i t\\u1ed1t h\\u01a1n sau gi\\u1edd ngh\\u1ec9. \\u0110\\u1ebfn ph\\u00fat 64, t\\u1eeb m\\u1ed9t pha ph\\u1ea3n c\\u00f4ng nhanh, Giroud m\\u1edf t\\u1ef7 s\\u1ed1 cho \\u0111\\u1ed9i kh\\u00e1ch. Sanchez nh\\u1eadn b\\u00f3ng khi ti\\u1ebfn v\\u00e0o v\\u00f2ng c\\u1ea5m r\\u1ed3i chuy\\u1ec1n sang tr\\u00e1i cho Gibbs. H\\u1eadu v\\u1ec7 tr\\u00e1i Arsenal quy\\u1ebft \\u0111\\u1ecbnh s\\u00fat ngay, b\\u00f3ng \\u0111\\u1eadp ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi h\\u1eadu v\\u1ec7 QPR, t\\u1ea1o c\\u01a1 h\\u1ed9i cho Giroud d\\u1ee9t \\u0111i\\u1ec3m g\\u00f3c g\\u1ea7n ghi b\\u00e0n.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"Normal\\" style=\\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; text-rendering: geometricprecision;\\">N\\u0103m ph\\u00fat sau, Sanchez n\\u00e2ng t\\u1ef7 s\\u1ed1 l\\u00ean 2-0 t\\u1eeb m\\u1ed9t n\\u1ed7 l\\u1ef1c c\\u00e1 nh\\u00e2n. Anh \\u0111i b\\u00f3ng l\\u1eaft l\\u00e9o trong v\\u00f2ng c\\u1ea5m, \\u0111\\u00e1nh b\\u1ea1i ba h\\u1eadu v\\u1ec7 QPR r\\u1ed3i d\\u1ee9t \\u0111i\\u1ec3m \\u1edf g\\u00f3c h\\u1eb9p.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"Normal\\" style=\\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; text-rendering: geometricprecision;\\">D\\u1eabn hai b\\u00e0n ch\\u01b0a th\\u1ec3 l\\u00e0m ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi h\\u00e2m m\\u1ed9 Arsenal y\\u00ean t\\u00e2m khi \\u0111\\u1ebfn ph\\u00fat 82, QPR c\\u00f3 b\\u00e0n r\\u00fat ng\\u1eafn t\\u1ef7 s\\u1ed1. Nh\\u1eefng ph\\u00fat c\\u00f2n l\\u1ea1i Ph\\u00e1o th\\u1ee7 \\u0111\\u1ed1i di\\u1ec7n v\\u1edbi nguy c\\u01a1 b\\u1ecb g\\u1ee1 h\\u00f2a nh\\u01b0ng th\\u1ee7 m\\u00f4n Ospina \\u0111\\u00e3 ch\\u01a1i t\\u1ed1t, b\\u1ea3o to\\u00e0n th\\u1eafng l\\u1ee3i.<\\/p>\\r\\n<table class=\\"tplCaption\\" style=\\"margin: 0px auto 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; width: 470px;\\" border=\\"0\\" cellspacing=\\"0\\" cellpadding=\\"3\\" align=\\"center\\">\\r\\n<tbody style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\\">\\r\\n<tr style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\\">\\r\\n<td style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0