(205, 'Jetstar Pacific v VietJet Air ua bn v gi r', 'jetstar-pacific-va-vietjet-air-ua-ban-ve-gia-re', '', 'Trong khi Jetstar Pacific tung ra  lot v  mc gi 650.000 ng/chng khi hnh dp u nm 2012 th  VietJet Air li tch cc bn v gi r hng tun vi mc gi ch  100.000 ng/chng ni a.\r\n<div>t bn v gi r ca Jetstar  Pacific bt u t ngy 9/12 n ht ngy 12/12 trn cc ng bay gia  TP.HCM v H Ni, Hi Phng, Vinh vi mc 650.000 ng/chng.</div>\r\n<div><br /><img src="http://dantri4.vcmedia.vn/zBWMWGSUq5Jhg0bdkuZf/Image/2011/11/JPA_243a9.jpg" border="0" /><br /><span style="font-family: Tahoma; font-size: 10pt;">Jetstar Pacific bn v gi r bayu nm 2012</span></div>\r\n<div>V do h thng my tnh t ng phn phi trn Internet, ti trang web bn v <a href="http://www.jetstar.com/">http://www.jetstar.com/</a> (khng p dng bn ti cc i l ca Jetstar Pacific) i vi cc  chuyn bay c ngy khi hnh trong giai on t 4/4 - 19/4/2012. Hnh  khch c th ng k v thanh ton trc tuyn bng cc loi th tn  dng, ghi n hoc thanh ton bng tin mt ti trn 1.100 im giao dch  bu in trn ton quc, ngn hng  c chp thun.</div>\r\n<p>Cng trong giai on ny, Jetstar Group cng thc hin t bn v my  bay quc t gia Tp.H Ch Minh v Singapore t 450.000 ng/chng,  gia H Ni v Singapore t 750 nghn ng/chng, p dng cho cc chuyn  bay khi hnh t 11/4/2012 n 23/5/2012. i vi vi v my bay quc  t ny ch p dng i vi hnh thc thanh ton trc tuyn bng th tn  dng Visa, Master Card.</p>\r\n<p>Khng chu km cnh, "tn binh" VietJet Air cng "chi tri'' khi  trin khai tun khuyn mi v my bay 100.000 ng c m bn t ngy  5/12 n ht ngy 11/12 p dng trn tuyn H Ni - TP. HCM v ngc,  khi hnh trong giai on t 25/12/2011 - 30/4/2012.</p>\r\n<div><img src="http://dantri4.vcmedia.vn/zBWMWGSUq5Jhg0bdkuZf/Image/2011/10/VJA2011_9a4a9.jpg" border="0" /></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-family: Tahoma; font-size: 10pt;">VietJet Air bn v 100.000 ng/chng</span></div>\r\n<p>Theo i din VietJet Air, do nhu cu mua v gi r ln, VietJetAir   quyt nh tng s lng v khuyn mi, s lng v r ny s c m  t ng ngu nhin trn h thng theo cc ngy, ty thuc vo tnh  trng ca chuyn bay. Tnh n thi im 3h chiu ngy 7/12/2011,  c  1581 v khuyn mi  c xut bn v gi ch hp l. Tuy nhin, hin  c tnh trng 1 s khch hng gi ch nhng ht 48 gi khng thanh ton  tin mua v, s v ny s c t ng nh ra trn h thng.</p>\r\n<p>c bit, VietJetAir s thc hin cc chuyn bay gia TP.HCM - H Ni t ngy 25/12/2011.</p>\r\n<p align="right"><span style="font-weight: bold;">Qunh Anh</span></p>', '', 1, 6, 0, 38, '2012-02-02 06:10:10', 62, '', '2012-02-02 06:12:56', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-02-02 06:10:10', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 2, 0, 67, '', '', 0, 35, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(210, 'Jetstar Pacific tip tc bn v my bay gi r trn ton mng', 'jetstar-pacific-tiep-tuc-ban-ve-may-bay-gia-re-tren-toan-mang', '', 'Bt u t 14h n 23h59 hm nay  (27/5), hng hng khng gi r Jetstar Pacific s tip tc thc hin t  bn v my bay gi r c bit trn ton mng vi mc gi t 350.000  ng/chng i vi cc chuyn bay khi hnh trong giai on t 7/9 -  5/10.\r\n<div>Mc gi 350.000  ng/chng c p dng cho cc ng bay gia TP.HCM -  Nng v gia  TP.HCM - Hu, i vi cc ng bay gia TP.HCM - H Ni v gia TP.HCM -  Hi Phng c gi t 700.000 ng/chng.</div>\r\n<div><img src="http://dantri4.vcmedia.vn/zBWMWGSUq5Jhg0bdkuZf/Image/2011/05/JPA20111_52ceb.jpg" border="0" width="450" align="middle" style="margin: 5px;" /></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-family: Tahoma; font-size: 10pt;">Jetstar Pacific bn v my bay gi r trong ngy27/5</span></div>\r\n<p>y l t m bn v gi r c m rng ti tt c cc knh bn, bao  gm: mua v ti cc phng v v i l ca Jetstar Pacific trn ton  quc; cc hnh thc ng k ti <a href="http://www.jetstar.com/">http://www.jetstar.com/</a> v thanh ton trc tuyn bng cc loi th tn dng, th ghi n v  Internet Banking  c chp nhn thanh ton, hoc tng i 19001550.</p>\r\n<p>c bit, k t 17/5 Jetstar Pacific  thc hin vic chuyn i v  m rng h thng gi v, chnh sch thng mi theo phng thc mi,  to iu kin cho hnh khch t la chn v xy dng chi ph i li ty  theo nhu cu thc t.</p>\r\n<p>Ngoi vic c nhiu mc gi v c phn phi t thp n cao, hnh  khch s bt u la chn chuyn bay vi mc gi c bn thp nht hin  c trn h thng (loi v Starter) bao gm ch ngi v 7kg hnh l xch  tay  tit kim.</p>\r\n<p>Hnh khch cng c th ty nhu cu c th la chn hnh l k gi vi  mc cn linh hot 15, 20, 25, 30, 35, 40 kg, hoc la chn thm gi  dch v gia tng khc  c cc iu kin ph hp nh: c php thay  i ngy, c hon v, c la chn ch ngi trn my bay.</p>\r\n<p align="right"><span style="font-weight: bold;">Qunh Anh</span></p>', '', 1, 6, 0, 38, '2012-02-02 06:28:33', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-02-02 06:28:33', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=