(212, 'Jetstar Pacific tung ra 50.000 v my bay gi r', 'jetstar-pacific-tung-ra-50000-ve-may-bay-gia-re', '', 'Hng hng khng gi r Jetstar  Pacific va chnh thc cng b thc hin chng trnh bn 50.000 v my  bay gi r t 250.000 ng. y l t bn v gi r ln nht ca hng  t u nm 2009.\r\n<div>Thi gian m bn bt u t6h  sng ngy 18/2 v kt thc vo lc 23h59ngy 22/2. V my bay do h  thng my tnh t ng phn phi trn cc chuyn bay c ngy khi hnh  trong giai on t 3/3 n 21/5.<img src="http://www.namhung.us/images/plg_imagesized/210-jpa20111_52ceb.jpg" border="0" alt="Pacific tung 50000 v my bay gi r" title="Pacific tung 50000 ve may bay gia re" width="400" height="300" style="border: 0pt none;" /></div>\r\n<div>c bit, phm vi bn v ln ny c Jetstar Pacific m rng n  tt c cc knh bn, bao gm: Trang web jetstar.com, cc Phng v, i  l ca Jetstar Pacific trn ton quc v Tng i 19001550 (hoc 08.3  9550 550).</div>\r\n<div>Vic thanh ton phi c thc hin ngay ti thi im t ch.</div>\r\n<div>Mc gi m bn trn cc tuyn bay nh sau:</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<table style="text-align: center;" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="193">\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Tuyn bay (gia/v)</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="99">\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Gi t</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="193">\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">TPHCM -  Nng</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">TPHCM - Hu</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">H Ni -  Nng</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="99">\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">250.000 VN</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="193">\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">TPHCM - H Ni</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">TPHCM - Hi Phng</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">TPHCM - Vinh</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">H Ni - Cn Th </span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="99">\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">500.</span><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">000 VN</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>V hn ch bn i vi cc chuyn bay trong thi gian t 28/4- 3/5/2009.</div>\r\n<div>C cu gi v ca Jetstar Pacific bao gm 3 nhm gi chnh, c  phn phi t thp n cao ti tt c cc knh bn  khch hng la  chn.</div>\r\n<div>Nhm gi JetFlex cho php thay i ngy bay min ph, dnh cho  nhng hnh khch cng v c k hoch i li hay thay i; Nhm gi tit  kim JetSaver dnh cho nhng hnh khch n nh k hoch i li  tit  kim chi ph; c bit, vi nhng hnh khch ch mang di 7kg hnh l  xch tay c th la chn loi gi v JetSaver Light  c th tit kim  thm t nht 50.000 ng/chng ni a, 320.000 ng/chng quc t.</div>\r\n<div><span style="font-weight: bold;">Phc Hng</span></div>', '', 1, 6, 0, 38, '2012-02-02 06:31:23', 62, '', '2012-02-02 06:34:43', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-02-02 06:31:23', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 2, 0, 63, '', '', 0, 31, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(206, 'Jetstar Pacific v VietJet Air ua bn v gi r', 'jetstar-pacific-va-vietjet-air-ua-ban-ve-gia-re', '', 'Trong khi Jetstar Pacific tung ra  lot v  mc gi 650.000 ng/chng khi hnh dp u nm 2012 th  VietJet Air li tch cc bn v gi r hng tun vi mc gi ch  100.000 ng/chng ni a.\r\n<div>t bn v gi r ca Jetstar  Pacific bt u t ngy 9/12 n ht ngy 12/12 trn cc ng bay gia  TP.HCM v H Ni, Hi Phng, Vinh vi mc 650.000 ng/chng.</div>\r\n<div><br /><img src="http://dantri4.vcmedia.vn/zBWMWGSUq5Jhg0bdkuZf/Image/2011/11/JPA_243a9.jpg" border="0" /><br /><span style="font-family: Tahoma; font-size: 10pt;">Jetstar Pacific bn v gi r bayu nm 2012</span></div>\r\n<div>V do h thng my tnh t ng phn phi trn Internet, ti trang web bn v <a href="http://www.jetstar.com/">http://www.jetstar.com/</a> (khng p dng bn ti cc i l ca Jetstar Pacific) i vi cc  chuyn bay c ngy khi hnh trong giai on t 4/4 - 19/4/2012. Hnh  khch c th ng k v thanh ton trc tuyn bng cc loi th tn  dng, ghi n hoc thanh ton bng tin mt ti trn 1.100 im giao dch  bu in trn ton quc, ngn hng  c chp thun.</div>\r\n<p>Cng trong giai on ny, Jetstar Group cng thc hin t bn v my  bay quc t gia Tp.H Ch Minh v Singapore t 450.000 ng/chng,  gia H Ni v Singapore t 750 nghn ng/chng, p dng cho cc chuyn  bay khi hnh t 11/4/2012 n 23/5/2012. i vi vi v my bay quc  t ny ch p dng i vi hnh thc thanh ton trc tuyn bng th tn  dng Visa, Master Card.</p>\r\n<p>Khng chu km cnh, "tn binh" VietJet Air cng "chi tri'' khi  trin khai tun khuyn mi v my bay 100.000 ng c m bn t ngy  5/12 n ht ngy 11/12 p dng trn tuyn H Ni - TP. HCM v ngc,  khi hnh trong giai on t 25/12/2011 - 30/4/2012.</p>\r\n<div><img src="http://dantri4.vcmedia.vn/zBWMWGSUq5Jhg0bdkuZf/Image/2011/10/VJA2011_9a4a9.jpg" border="0" /></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-family: Tahoma; font-size: 10pt;">VietJet Air bn v 100.000 ng/chng</span></div>\r\n<p>Theo i din VietJet Air, do nhu cu mua v gi r ln, VietJetAir   quyt nh tng s lng v khuyn mi, s lng v r ny s c m  t ng ngu nhin trn h thng theo cc ngy, ty thuc vo tnh  trng ca chuyn bay. Tnh n thi im 3h chiu ngy 7/12/2011,  c  1581 v khuyn mi  c xut bn v gi ch hp l. Tuy nhin, hin  c tnh trng 1 s khch hng gi ch nhng ht 48 gi khng thanh ton  tin mua v, s v ny s c t ng nh ra trn h thng.</p>\r\n<p>c bit, VietJetAir s thc hin cc chuyn bay gia TP.HCM - H Ni t ngy 25/12/2011.</p>\r\n<p align="right"><span style="font-weight: bold;">Qunh Anh</span></p>', '', 1, 6, 0, 59, '2012-02-02 06:10:10', 62, '', '2012-02-02 06:12:56', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-02-02 06:10:10', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 0, 0, 7, '', '', 0, 709, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(43, 'Air Mekong cng b m ng bay Tp. H Ch Minh - Quy Nhn - Tp. H Ch Minh', 'airmekong-sgnuhsgn', '', '<p><span style="border-collapse: collapse; font-family: verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; color: #000000; line-height: normal;"> </span></p>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><span style="font-size: small;">Ngy 7/5/2011, ti khch sn Royal Hotel &amp; Healthcare Resort QuiNhon, TP Quy Nhn, tnh Bnh nh, UBND tnh Bnh inh phi hp vi Cng ty c phn hng khng Mekong (Air Mekong) t chc L cng b chnh thc M ng bay TP H Ch Minh- Qui Nhn ca hng hng khng Air Mekong. Tham d L cng b c i din lnh o Kim ton Nh nc, Ngn hng u t v Pht trin Vit nam, Tng cng ty cm cng hng khng min trung cng nhiu doanh nghip, cc s ban ngnh thuc tnh Bnh nh. y l hng hng khng th hai sau Vietnam Airline c mt ti Bnh nh.</span></span></div>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Verdana;"> </span></p>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: small;">Theo , t ngy 1/6/2011, Air Mekong s chnh thc khai trng ng bay mi Thnh ph H Ch Minh - Quy Nhn, nng tng s ng bay ni a m Air Mekong khai thc ln 11 ng bay.<br />Air Mekong khi ng kinh doanh vn chuyn t ngy 9/10/2010, ng vo dp i l 1000 nm Thng Long. Ngay t u, Air Mekong c nh v l mt Hng hng khng truyn thng vi hai hng dch v cung cp l hng Ph thng (Economy) v hng Deluxe. Air Mekong s dng 4 my bay phn lc hin i Bombardier CRJ 900 trn cc ng bay c ng bng ngn, nh mt minh chng cho s cam kt v cht lng, dch v ca Hng vi khch hng l Air Mekong mun mang mt sn phm cht lng cao  phc v cho phn khc khch hng m cc Hng hng khng hin nay cha p ng .<br />My bay Bombardier CRJ 900 c trang b hai ng c phn lc, tc  bay 800 km n 900 km mt gi, vi  cao bay ln n 13.000 m. S dng dch v bay ca Air Mekong, khch hng s c cm nhn nhng u th vt tri so vi vic bay trn nhng my bay trang b ng c cnh qut nh: thi gian bay rt ngn c ti 35%, khng b rung sc mnh do bay cao, khng phi bay qua cc vng my gy nhiu ng ln, gh ngi c b tr rng ri hn</span></div>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Verdana;"> </span></p>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: small;">Hin ti, Air Mekong ang thc hin t 32 n 35 chuyn bay mi ngy, trn ba nhm ng bay chnh: Nhm ng bay trc ni lin hai trung tm kinh t H Ni v Thnh ph H Ch Minh; Nhm ng bay bin o ti Ph Quc, Cn o; Nhm ng bay cao nguyn ti ba im n l Pleiku,  Lt v Bun Ma Thut.<br />Trc , ngy 28/4/2011, Air Mekong cng  chnh thc khai trng ng bay thng H Ni  Ph Quc, y l ng bay thng di nht Vit Nam v duy nht do Air Mekong khai thc tnh n thi im hin ti. ng bay ny ch ko di hn 2 gi, tit kim ti 50% thi gian so vi hnh trnh phi ni chuyn qua Thnh ph H Ch Minh.<br />Sau 7 thng i vo hot ng, Air Mekong  thc hin c hn 5.200 chuyn bay an ton. Vi lch bay linh hot, t l ng gi cao, lun t trn 92%, Air Mekong ngy cng c khch hng tin cy v tr thnh s la chn ti u cho nhiu hnh trnh bng ng hng khng.</span></div>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Verdana;"> </span></p>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: small;">Thnh ph Quy Nhn l mt trong 7  th loi mt trc thuc tnh ca Vit Nam, l trung tm kinh t, chnh tr, vn ha, khoa hc k thut v du lch ca Bnh nh v cc tnh min Trung. Quy Nhn c bit n vi nhiu danh lam thng cnh ni ting nh Thp i, Cha Long Khnh, Cha Sn Long, Gnh Rng Tin Sa, Cu Th Ni, bin Quy Hav c bit l khu di tch lch s v ngi Anh hng dn tc Quang Trung  Nguyn Hu; vi cc mn n c sn rt ring nh bnh trng nc da, bnh t l gai, nem ch Huyn v mm rut c ng Quy Nhn vi hng v thm ngon c bit. Bn cnh , Bnh nh vi tim lc kinh t ang ngy cng ln mnh nh li th v ngun ti nguyn thin nhin di do, tim nng kinh t bin ln, c bit trong lnh vc du lch v nui trng hi sn, pht trin ngnh ch bin g xut khu v khai thc cc khong sn qu (granite, titan, vng). Vic tham gia khai thc ng bay Thnh ph H Ch Minh  Quy Nhn ca Air Mekong s lm gim p lc v giao lu qua li gia Bnh nh v cc tnh ln cn vi trung tm kinh t ln nht ca c nc, gp phn thc y s pht trin kinh t, x hi, chnh tr ca c khu vc ny.</span></div>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Verdana;"> </span></p>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: small;"> to iu kin thun li cho khch hng, va qua Air Mekong  m rng h thng bn v thng qua vic k kt hp tc vi Tng cng ty Bu chnh Vit Nam (VNPost), v Ngn hng u t v Pht trin Vit Nam (BIDV) cho php khch hng c th mua v hoc thanh ton tin v my bay Air Mekong ti hn 18.000 bu cc ca VNPost v tt c cc im giao dch ca BIDV trn ton quc, song song vi vic t ch v mua v qua website, qua Call center, qua phng v v ti tt c cc i l bn v my bay Air Mekong hin c.<br />Trong thi gian ti, Air Mekong s nghin cu  sm a vo khai thc m ng bay H ni-Qui Nhn-H ni, chnh thc khp kn tuyn giao thng ng khng gia Bnh nh v tnh Nam trung b vi 2 trung tm kinh t ln nht ca c nc- H ni v TP H Ch Minh.</span></div>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Verdana;"> </span></p>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: small;">Mc tiu ca Air Mekong l mang li cho khch hng cc chuyn bay<strong>An ton  Tin cy  Tin ch  ng gi</strong>.<br />Air Mekong bt u bn v tuyn bay Thnh ph H Ch Minh  Quy Nhn t ngy 15/5/2011. Mi chi tit xin vui lng lin h: 0838752008</span></div>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p></p>', '', 1, 1, 0, 1, '2011-06-16 00:00:00', 62, '', '2011-05-16 06:14:34', 63, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-06-16 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 12, 0, 2, 'Uncategorized, Uncategorized, Example Pages and Menu Links', '', 0, 142, 'robots=\nauthor='),
