(51, 'AA airlines', 'aa-airlines', '', '<p><img src="http://vemaybaytructuyen.com/images/stories/promotions/aa.jpg" border="0" alt="aa" width="202" height="76" /></p>\r\n<div id="yui_3_2_0_3_130458135948561">\r\n<p id="yui_3_2_0_3_130458135948560" class="yiv1237093241MsoNormal">THE BEST WAY TO THE U.S FROM VIETNAM\r\n', '\r\n</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><br /><img src="http://vemaybaytructuyen.com/images/stories/promotions/a-a.jpg" border="0" alt="a-a" width="610" height="733" /></p>', 1, 4, 0, 34, '2010-11-12 09:38:53', 62, '', '2011-05-14 16:00:09', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2010-11-12 09:38:53', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 1, '', '', 0, 44, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(208, 'Hng khng Vit Nam: Ai ct cnh, ai l hn?', 'hang-khong-viet-nam-ai-cat-canh-ai-lo-hen', '', 'Nhiu hng hng khng ang try trt  tm "k sinh nhai" trn th trng ni a. Hng khng Vit Nam c thm  nhng ci tn mi, nhng ai ct cnh, ai l hn l cu hi ch thi  gian tr li.\r\n<p align="left"><span style="font-weight: bold;">Nng chuyn AOC</span></p>\r\n<p>c nhn nhn l th trng hp dn, nhng ti Vit Namhin ch c  Vietnam Airlines, Jetstar Pacific, Air Mekong v Vasco khai thc cc  chuyn bay ch khch. Hy vng ct cnh hoc bay tr li ca cc hng  hng khc trong lnh vc ny vn cn kh xa xi.</p>\r\n<div>Cng ty c phn Hng khng ng Dng (VP) xin tm ngng khai thc  bay do kh khn trong hot ng sn xut kinh doanh t thng 10/2009 v   3 ln b Cc Hng khng Vit Nam gi vn bn thu hi thng quyn  bay, yu cu bo co tin trnh thc hin vic xin cp Giy chng nhn  ngi khai thc tu bay (AOC) v d kin k hoch khai thc tr li.</div>\r\n<div><img src="http://dantri4.vcmedia.vn/zBWMWGSUq5Jhg0bdkuZf/Image/2011/05/Hangkhong2011_31a86.jpg" border="0" width="450" align="middle" style="margin: 5px;" /></div>\r\n<div>Khi mt thng quyn bay, hot ng khai thc vn  chuyn hng khng dng li 2 nm tng ng vi thi gian khng c cp  AOC th VP khng  kh nng duy tr Giy php kinh doanh vn chuyn  hng khng.</div>\r\n<p>Tuy nhin,  to mi iu kin cho VP, B GTVT  kin ngh Th  tng Chnh ph xem xt, chp thun vic xin gia hn ca VP vi iu  kin VP phi i chiu v thanh ton y  cc khon n cho cc nh  cung cp dch v trc ngy 30/6/2011.</p>\r\n<p>Th nhng thi gian cht hn hon tt nhng iu kin cn v    c ct cnh dnh cho VP  qua t lu nn vic hng ny tip tc xin  gia hn v duy tr giy php kinh doanh vn chuyn hng khng l v cng  kh khn.</p>\r\n<p>Trong khi , Hng hng khng ca nhc s H Dng - Indochina  Airlines   n ln Th tng, B GTVT v Cc Hng khng Vit Nam t  u nm xin gia hn vic rt giy php bay nhm thc hin ti c cu ti  chnh, tm nh u t, c ng mi v khi phc hot ng bay. Nhng  n thi im ny Indochina Airlines vn cha c tn hiu lc quan  thuyt phc vicc gia hn. Chung s phn vi Indochina Airlines,  Tri Thin Airlines cng v nhng kh khn ti chnh m phi l hn  ct cnh.</p>\r\n<div>ng V Huy Cng - Trng ban Kinh doanh Vn ti hng khng, Cc  Hng khng Vit Nam cho bit: Cho n thi im ny, Indochina Airlines  v Tri Thin Airlines... khng c du hiu s  nng lc tham gia  khai thc th trng theo quy nh ca php lut.</div>\r\n<p>Trc tnh hnh thc t ca cc hng hng khng ni trn, lnh o  Cc Hng khng Vit Nam cho rng s chun b cha tht s ng mc v  thi  lc quan hi qu ca cc hng hng khng chnh l nguyn nhn  khin h phi iu chnh k hoch tham gia th trng.</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-weight: bold;">Mnh t mu m  th trng ngch</span></p>\r\n<p>Trong bi cnh th trng kinh doanh hng khng c nhng chung v vn  ti khch v hng ha th mi y Cc Hng khng mi y  cp giy  php kinh doanh vn chuyn hng khng chung cho Cng ty CP Hng khng  lng dng Ngi sao Vit (Vietstar Airlines). Vietstar s khai thc   th trng ngch - bay du lch, tham quan ngm cnh, phc v lnh vc  gii tr, biu din; bay cp cu, quay phim, chp nh...</p>\r\n<p>So vi th trng chung nh vn chuyn hnh khch, hng ha th khai  thc  th trng ngch nyc yu t thun li gip Vietstar Airlines  tm kim th phn.</p>\r\n<p>L gii v nhng thun li ca th trng ngch, ng V Huy Cng cho  hay: Vietstar Airlines s khai thc bng tu bay cnh bng  th trng  ngch nn s c nhng thun li ch yu v khai thc gia cc sn bay  theo nhng ng hng khng hin c nn s khng gp kh khn khi xin  php bay v thc hin php bay. Ngoi ra, trong th trng ny t c  cnh tranh vn chuyn v nhu cu i li ca thng gia; vn chuyn cp  cu trong nc v t Vit Nam i cc nc trong khu vc.</p>\r\n<p>Vietstar Airlines c th l hng hng khng duy nht kinh doanh v  p ng c nhu cu vn chuyn thng mi du lch ti th trng ngch   Vit Nam trong nhiu nm sp ti - ng Cng nhn nh.</p>\r\n<p>Ni nh vy th th trng ngch ch thc l mnh t mu m m  Vietstar Airlines s c quyn nm gi th phn khai thc kinh doanh  vn chuyn.</p>\r\n<p>Sp ti, th trng hng khng ni a d kin s si ng hn khi  cho n s tham gia khai thc ca VietJet Airlines - hng hng khng t  nhn u tin c cp php bay nhng vn cha mt ln ct cnh. K  hoch bay ca VietJet Airlines  c Cc Hng khng thng qua, hng  ny s bt u khai thc trn th trng ni a t qu 4/2011.</p>\r\n<p>Hin VietJet Airlines ang hon tt cc th tc cui cng  c  gii chc ngnh hng khng Vit Nam cp chng ch Nh khai thc tu bay  (AOC) - mt trong nhng iu kin quan trng khi khai thc bay thng  mi.</p>\r\n<p>c bit, VietJet Airlines c cp php thnh lp nm 2007 nhng   4 ln phi l hn ct cnh v l do ti chnh. y cng l hng hng  khng t nhn duy nht ti Vit Nam cho ti thi im ny c thng  quyn bay quc t.</p>\r\n<p align="right"><span style="font-weight: bold;">Qunh Anh</span></p>', '', 1, 6, 0, 38, '2012-02-02 06:21:22', 62, '', '2012-02-02 06:23:49', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-02-02 06:21:22', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 2, 0, 66, '', '', 0, 37, 'robots=\nauthor='),
