(66, 'Th tc lm Visa', 'thu-tuc-lam-visa', '', '<p>VISA DU LCH Th tc lm visa du lch hin nay rt n gin v khng  mt nhiu thi gian. Thm ch, ngi Vit Nam i du lch n mt s nc  khng cn lm visa. Ngoi ra, cc i l du lch cng sn sng cung cp  dch v lm visa cho khch du lch, d nhin l phi thm mt cht ph  ph.<br /> <br />Th tc lm visa<br />Thng thng, ngi Vit Nam i du lch nc  ngoi u phi c visa. Th tc lm visa khc nhau vi mi quc gia, do   bn phi lin h trc tip vi i s qun nc  ti Vit Nam   c hng dn c th, chi tit cng nh mc ph lm visa. Tuy nhin,  nhn chung, bn s phi in vo n xin cp visa (mu n c th khc  nhau vi mi nc), cung cp cc thng tin sau:<br /><br />* H tn y  v a ch lin lc ca ngi thn ti Vit Nam<br />* Thi gian v l do ri khi Vit Nam.<br />* Phng tin i bng g.<br /><br />i n u khng cn visa?<br /><br />*  Ngi Vit Nam khi i du lch trong vng 30 ngy n cc nc sau y  khng cn c visa: Thi Lan, Phi-lip-pin, Malaixia, Xingapo, Innxia,  Lo v Campuchia.<br />* Nu c th ABTC (th i li doanh nhn APEC) s  c min th thc xut nhp cnh, c lm th tc nhp cnh  khu vc  ring, c li i ring, c min th tc ng k lu tr, c nhp  xut cnh nhiu ln trong cc nn kinh t thnh vin APEC tham gia ABTC  v lu tr vi thi gian ti a l 60 ngy trong mi ln nhp cnh.<br />*  Ngi Vit Nam nu mang h chiu ngoi giao hoc h chiu cng v cn  gi tr s c min visa khi n Nht Bn trong thi hn khng qu 90  ngy.</p>', '', 1, 5, 0, 37, '2011-05-14 09:04:13', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-05-14 09:04:13', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 2, '', '', 0, 0, 'robots=\nauthor='),
