(114, 'Hm nay, Jetstar Pacific tip tc bn v 350.000 ng/chng', 'hom-nay-jetstar-pacific-tip-tc-ban-ve-350000-ngchng', '', '<div></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2><a href="http://vemaybaytructuyen.com/index.php/tin-tc/tin-hang-khong/265-hom-nay-jetstar-pacific-tip-tc-ban-ve-350000-ngchng"> </a>Hm nay, Jetstar Pacific tip tc bn v 350.000 ng/chng</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Bt u t 14 - 17h hm nay (3/6), hng hng khng gi r Jetstar Pacific tip tc bn v my bay gi r t 350.000 ng/chng cho cc chuyn bay khi hnh t ngy 5/10 n ngy 1/11/2011. </strong>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://vemaybaytructuyen.com/images/stories/banner_fff_575x265_vn.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p>C th, v my bay do h thng t ng phn phi ti trang web ca hng bt u t 14h - 17h, trn cc chuyn bay khi hnh trong giai on t 5/10 n 1/11/2011.</p>\r\n<p>Cng trong giai on ny, v my bay gi r trn chng TP.HCM - H Ni c tung ra  mc 700.000 ng/chng.</p>\r\n<p>y l loi v Starter bao gm ch ngi trn chuyn bay v 7kg hnh l xch tay. Hnh khch cng c th ty theo nhu cu la chn hnh l k gi vi mc cn linh hot 15, 20, 25, 30, 35, 40 kg, hoc la chn thm gi dch v gia tng khc  c cc iu kin ph hp nh: thay i ngy, c hon v, c la chn ch ngi trn my bay</p>\r\n<p>Chng trnh gim gi ny ch p dng cho nhng hnh khch ng k trang web bn v <a href="http://www.jetstar.com/">http://www.jetstar.com/</a> v thanh ton trc tuyn bng cc loi th ngn hng  c chp thun.</p>', '', 1, 11, 0, 44, '2011-06-04 04:30:12', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-06-04 04:30:12', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 23, '', '', 0, 0, 'robots=\nauthor='),
