(104, 'Gi trn tng, hng khng vn duy tr cc mc v gi r', 'gia-tran-tang-hang-khong-van-duy-tri-cac-muc-ve-gia-re', '', '<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong>Cng vi gi xng du, gi in v nhiu gi hng ha thit yu khc, gi v my bay cng rp rnh tng t sau ngy 27/4. Tuy nhin, cc hng s vn duy tr cc mc v gi r  tng kh nng cnh tranh. </strong></span></p>\r\n<table style="width: 100%;" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td height="18">\r\n<table style="width: 1px;" align="left" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<table style="width: 1px;" align="left" border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><img src="http://images.vnmedia.vn/images_upload/2011/vnm_2011_345346.jpg" border="0" /></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p align="justify"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Quyt nh mi ca B Ti chnh v khung gi cc vn chuyn hnh khch hng v ph thng trn cc ng bay ni a cn v th c quyn  chnh thc c hiu lc t ngy 27/4. Theo , gi trn trn cc ng bay s tng ln ti hn 20% so vi mc hin nay.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">C th, i vi ng bay c c ly di 300km, mc gi cao nht l 863.636 ng/v (mc c l 682.000 ng); c ly t 300km n di 500km, mc cao nht l 1.100.000 ng/v (mc b&nbsp;&nbsp; c l 864.000 ng); ng bay c c ly t 500km n di 850km gi 1.481.818 ng/v (mc c l 1.182.000 ng) ;  c ly t 850km n di 1.000km, mc gi l 1.909.091 ng/v; c ly t 1.000km n di 1.280km l 2.227.273 ng/v v mc gi cho c ly t 1.280km tr ln ln ti 2.727.273 ng/v. Trong khi theo quy nh trc , th ng bay t 850km tr ln u c mc gi trn l 1.819.000 ng.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Cc mc gi ni trn cha bao gm thu&nbsp;VAT v cc loi ph khc. Nh vy nu tnh thm c thu VAT 10%, gi v my bay mt chiu tuyn H Ni - Ph Quc (ng bay di nht) c th ln n 3 triu ng.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">i din cc hng hng khng nh Vietnam Airlines, Jetstar Pacific u cho bit hng ang chun b cho k hoch tng gi v my bay v s sm cng b trong thi gian ti. Tuy nhin, c hai hng u s vn c cc mc gi a dng theo nhiu tiu chun khc nhau  ph hp vi mi khch hng. Cc hng v gi r s hu nh khng tng hoc ch tng cht t.</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Theo i din ca hng hng khng Jetstar, vi chnh sch l hng khng gi r nn hng lun c rt nhiu loi mc gi khc nhau, tu thuc theo thi gian t v, chng trnh khuyn mi khc nhau. Cc mc gi di gi trn chim n 90%, do vy, d gi v c tng th hng khch c nhu cu mua v gi r vn c nhiu c hi  la chn mc v ph hp vi mnh.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">i din Cc Hng khng cho bit, t cui nm 2010, cc hng hng khng  nhiu ln  ngh tng mc trn gi v my bay, thm ch c hng  ngh tng ti 60%. Theo phn tch ca&nbsp;cc hng hng khng, khong 70% chi ph ca ngnh hng khng phi tr bng ngoi t: Mua nhin liu, thu tu bay, thu phi cng... V th khi USD iu chnh lp tc chi ph gi thnh i ln.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Mi y, tr li phng vn ca bo Tui tr, ng Lu Thanh Bnh, Cc ph Cc Hng khng Vit Nam cho bit, gi xng du th gii hin nay  hn mc 105 USD/thng, nhng theo ng Bnh, nu gi xng du th gii gim, c quan qun l nh nc cng s iu chnh gim gi v my bay trn c s gim st cht ch vic ng k gi ca cc hng hng khng  m bo quyn li ca ngi tiu dng.</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', '', 1, 11, 0, 44, '2011-05-14 09:22:04', 62, '', '2011-06-04 05:22:58', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-05-14 09:22:04', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 2, 0, 3, '', '', 0, 120, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(105, 'Hng khng p dng ph ph thu nhin liu', 'hnag-khong-ap-dung-phi-phu-thu-nhien-lieu', '', '<p><strong>Gi du th gii lun bin ng theo chiu hng tng do tnh hnh bt n ti mt s khu vc ti trung ng  khin cc hng hng khng phi p dng v tng ph ph thu nhin liu vo gi v my bay. </strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table class="sgtoimageleft" style="width: 229px; height: 171px;" align="left" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img class="sgtoimageleft_popup" src="http://www.thesaigontimes.vn/Uploads/Articles/52766/e0841_airasiaonline_200.jpg" border="0" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="sgtoimageleft">AirAsia thng bo p dng ph ph thu nhin liu vo gi v my bay t ngy 3-5 - nh: Mng Bnh</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Ngy 3-5, AirAsia bt u p dng tr li khon ph ph nhin liu cho tt c cc ng bay ni a v quc t, sau hn 2 nm tp on hng khng gi r ny b ph ph xng du t gi v my bay.</p>\r\n<p>AirAsia cho rng hng phi p dng ph ph thu xng du do gi nhin liu my bay  tng cao, vt hn 140  la M/thng. Mc gi ny cao hn nhiu so vi thi im cui nm 2008 khi hng b ph ph thu nhin liu v gi du th gii lc  gim mnh, c lc xung gn 30  la M/thng do khng hong ti chnh ton cu.</p>\r\n<p>AirAsia thng bo hng s p dng mc ph thu nhin liu 10 ringit (gn 70.000 ng) cho cc chuyn bay c gi bay t hn 2 ting, 20 ringit cho cc chuyn bay t 2 n 3 ting, 30 ringit cho cc chuyn bay di hn 3 ting, v t 50-90 ringit cho cc chuyn bay di do AirAsia X thc hin t Kuala Lumpur n chu  v chu u.</p>\r\n<p>AirAsia v cc hng thnh vin l Thai AirAsia v Indonesia AirAsia ang thc hin cc chuyn bay t Kuala Lumpur (Malaysia), Bangkok (Thi Lan) v Jakarta (Indonesia) n Vit Nam, vi cc chuyn bay gia H Ni - Kuala Lumpur v TPHCM - Jakarta c gi bay hn 2 ting.</p>\r\n<p>AirAsia l hng hng khng thc hin cc chuyn bay quc t n Vit Nam mi nht cng b p dng ph ph thu nhin liu. Trc , cc hng hng khng truyn thng nh Singapore Airlines, Thai Airways, Malaysia Airlines, Jetstar Airways cng  cng b p dng v iu chnh tng mc ph ny nh l mt trong cc bin php i ph vi gi nhin liu tng cao.</p>\r\n<p>Theo Reuters, vo thng 4 va qua, hng hng khng Singapore Airlines cng b tng thm mc ph thu nhiu liu t 4-32  la M ty thuc vo  di ca mi chng v hng gh, p dng cho cc v my bay xut sau ngy 21-4 ca hng v SilkAir do gi nhin liu  tng hn 30% k t u nm n nay.</p>\r\n<p>Hng hng khng Thai Airways cng p dng mc ph xng du mi t 28  la M/chng cho cc v bn ra cch nay hn mt thng. y l mc thp nht m hng p dng cho cc chuyn bay c thi gian bay di 2 ting, gm cc chuyn bay gia Bangkok v TPHCM v H Ni.</p>\r\n<p>Trong ln gp bo ch tai TPHCM vo thng 4-2011, Gim c ca Malaysia Airlines ti Vit Nam, ng Zuraidi Saisi cho bit vic p dng ph ph thu xng du l mt bin php bt buc m cc hng hng khng phi p dng trc tnh hnh gi du th gii tng mnh khin gi xng my bay tng theo. Tuy nhin, ng khng cho bit c th mc ph ph nhin liu m hng ang p dng cho cc chuyn bay gia Kuala Lumpur v Vit Nam.</p>\r\n<p>Theo Hip hi vn ti hng khng quc t IATA, gi nhin liu my bay  t 140,2  la M/thng tnh n thi im ngy 22-4-2011, tng 3,5% so vi thng trc  v 47,7% so vi cng k ca nm 2010.</p>', '', 1, 11, 0, 44, '2011-05-14 09:20:23', 62, '', '2011-06-04 05:21:24', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-05-14 09:20:23', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 7, '', '', 0, 132, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(106, 'Vietnam Airlines tng gi v my bay ni a', 'vietnam-airlines-tng-gia-ve-may-bay-ni-a', '', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class="jv-box-inset"></div>\r\n<p><strong>Hng hng khng Quc gia Vit Nam (Vietnam Airlines) cho bit, s bt u tng gi v my bay ni a theo khung gi trn mi t ngy 16/5 </strong></p>\r\n<div class="fon31 mt1">Cc mc gi mi c xy dng trn c s khung gi cc vn chuyn chia theo gii hn 6 c ly  ng bay ni a theo khung gi trn theo quy nh ca B Ti chnh v nhng mc gi thp hn.</div>\r\n<div class="fon34 mt3 mr2 fon43">Trong , ng bay H Ni - TP.HCM c mc gi trn 2.227.000 ng (cha gm thu VAT v ph ph) nhng hnh khch c th tm mua c v gi thp nht l 1.050.000 ng (cha bao gm thu VAT v ph ph). Tuy nhin, chnh sch gi mi ny s c Vietnam Airlines p dng a dng v linh hot ty vo tnh hnh th trng v thi im kinh doanh.</div>\r\n<div class="fon34 mt3 mr2 fon43"><img src="http://dantri.vcmedia.vn/Uploaded/2011/05/11/Vietnam-Airlines2011.jpg" align="middle" border="0" width="450" /></div>\r\n<div class="fon34 mt3 mr2 fon43">Vietnam Airlines tng gi v my bay t ngy 16/5</div>\r\n<p class="fon34 mt3 mr2 fon43">Bn cnh mc gi trn theo quy nh, Vietnam Airlines s a ra th trng nhng mc gi mang tnh cnh tranh cao, c khi thp hn gi trn cho php n hn 50% nhm gip hnh khch c nhiu la chn.</p>\r\n<p class="fon34 mt3 mr2 fon43">Trc , 2 hng hng khng Jetstar Pacific v Air Mekong cng  chnh thc tng gi v my bay theo khung gi trn mi.</p>\r\n<div class="fon34 mt3 mr2 fon43">Theo Quyt nh tng gi trn v my bay ca B Ti chnh, mc gi v trn 2.227.273 ng p dng cho cc chuyn bay t 1.000 km n di 1.280 km; 863.636 ng cho cc ng bay di 300 km; 1.100.000 ng cho ng bay t 300 km n di 500 km; 1.481.818 ng cho ng bay t 500 km n di 850 km; 1.909.091 ng cho ng bay t 850 km n di 1.000 km; 2.727.273 ng cho ng bay t 1.280 km tr ln (cc mc gi v ny cha bao gm thu VAT v ph ph).</div>', '', 1, 11, 0, 44, '2011-05-14 09:11:58', 62, '', '2011-06-04 05:20:40', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-05-14 09:11:58', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\n