(131, 'iu kin 2', 'iu-kin-2', '', '<h2>Vietnam Airlines: mc tiu tr thnh hng hng khng 4 sao</h2>\r\n<table border="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div><img src="http://giavemaybayre.com.vn/stores/images/news/eda_t1297181180_1Mow.jpg" alt="" width="150" /></div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>Ph Tng Gim c Tng Cng ty Hng khng Vit Nam (Vietnam Airlines) Trnh Hng Quang cho bit, mt trong nhng nhim v trng tm ca hng trong nm nay l tip tc nng cao cht lng dch v, p ng ngy cng tt hn nhu cu ca hnh khch.</p>\r\n<img data-mce-type="system-readmore" id="system-readmore" src="plugins/editors/jce/tiny_mce/plugins/article/img/trans.gif" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><span style="display: block; margin-bottom: 6px;"> </span></p>\r\n<div>Thi gian qua, <a title="v my bay, v my bay gi r, t v my bay, lin h mua v" href="http://giavemaybayre.com.vn/" target="_blank">Vietnam Airlines</a>  u t mnh vo nng cao cht lng phc v thng qua vic t chc <a title="v my bay, v my bay gi r, t v my bay, lin h mua v" href="http://giavemaybayre.com.vn/" target="_blank">bn v in t</a>, lm th tc chuyn bay qua mng internet... Mc tiu ca hng  ra l tr thnh hng <a title="v my bay, v my bay gi r, t v my bay, lin h mua v" href="http://giavemaybayre.com.vn/" target="_blank">hng khng</a> t tiu chun "4 sao", n nm 2020, l mt trong s 10 hng hng khng c a chung nht chu  v cht lng dch v hnh khch. Ti khu vc ng Nam , Vietnam Airlines phn u l hng ln th 2 khu vc vo nm 2020.  hin thc ha mc tiu, ngoi vic nng cao cht lng, Tng Cng ty cn tip tc thc hin  n hin i ha i bay v d kin n nm 2020 s c 163 chic hin i nh Boeing 787, Airbuss A350; m rng mng ng bay ti 65 im trn khp th gii... Hin, Vietnam Airlines ang s hu i bay gm 70 chic vi  tui khai thc trung bnh 6,5 nm.</div>', '', 1, 8, 0, 51, '2011-06-29 09:35:06', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-06-29 09:35:06', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vo