(200, 'My bay mi ca ch tch Tp on Ha Pht', 'may-bay-moi-cua-chu-tich-tap-doan-hoa-phat', '', '<div>Chic trc thng mi EC 155B1 ca  Ch tch Tp on Ha Pht  chnh thc c mt ti Vit Nam thay th  chic trc thng c  c bn.<a href="http://dantri.com.vn/c76/s76-532763/Mua-may-bay-rieng-la-sang-suot-hieu-qua.htm"><strong></strong></a><a href="http://dantri.com.vn/c76/s76-389142/Chu-tich-tap-doan-Hoa-Phat-sam-may-bay-rieng.htm"><strong></strong></a></div>\r\n<p>Cng nh chic my bay trc y  ca Ch tch Tp on Ha Pht Trn nh Long, chic my bay mi ang  u  v tr sn  ca ga trc thng Gia Lm do Cng ty bay dch v  min Bc qun l.</p>\r\n<div>\r\n<div><img src="http://dantri4.vcmedia.vn/F5PTk2fd0dyFcSMai7us/Image/2011/12/malaysia/maybay1026122011_5ac19.jpg" border="0" width="470" align="middle" style="margin: 5px;" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><span style="font-family: Tahoma; font-size: 10pt;">Chic trc thng mi  c a vo s dng phc v cho cng viccua Tp on Ha Pht (nh chp ti H Giang ngy 26/12/2011)</span></div>\r\n<div>ng Trn Tun Dng  Tng gim c Tp on Ha Pht cho bit:  Vic thay th chic my bay c cng l  to iu kin thun li hn  trong cng vic ca tp on.</div>\r\n<p>in hnh nh vic nu dng chic my bay c bay t H Ni n H  Giang th phi ngh gia chng ti Yn Bi  tip nhin liu. Trong khi  , vi my bay mi c th bay thng, thm ch cn bay thng t H Ni  n  Nng m khng phi ngh gia chng. My bay mi cng ch c  nhiu ngi hn (12 ch) v c h s an ton cao hn</p>\r\n<p>Bn thn cn b ca cng ty bay dch v min Bc phi tha nhn my  bay t nhn duy nht thuc s hu ca Ch tch Tp on Ha Pht ang  t ti y thuc loi my trc thng rt hin i tnh n thi im  ny.</p>\r\n<p>Cn chic trc thng c  c bn li cho chnh n v m ng Long   mua trc y trc y v ang tm thi c  ti ga trc thng  Gia Lm.</p>\r\n<div>Di y l cn cnh ca chic my bay mi trong hnh trnh t H  Ni ti H Giang  mt trong nhng a phng c m khai thc tinh qung  do Tp on lm ch u t.</div>\r\n<div><img src="http://dantri4.vcmedia.vn/F5PTk2fd0dyFcSMai7us/Image/2011/12/malaysia/maybay126122011_a72ee.jpg" border="0" width="470" align="middle" style="margin: 5px;" /></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-family: Tahoma; font-size: 10pt;">L tip nhn tu bay trc thng mi ti Ga trc thng Gia Lm (nh t liu)</span></div>\r\n<span style="font-family: Tahoma; font-size: 10pt;">\r\n<div><img src="http://dantri4.vcmedia.vn/F5PTk2fd0dyFcSMai7us/Image/2011/12/malaysia/maybay226122011_cf70e.jpg" border="0" width="470" align="middle" style="margin: 5px;" /></div>\r\n<div><img src="http://dantri4.vcmedia.vn/F5PTk2fd0dyFcSMai7us/Image/2011/12/malaysia/maybay826122011_bef11.jpg" border="0" width="470" align="middle" style="margin: 5px;" /></div>\r\n<div>Chic trc thng ny thuc mu EC 155B1</div>\r\n<div><img src="http://dantri4.vcmedia.vn/F5PTk2fd0dyFcSMai7us/Image/2011/12/malaysia/maybay726122011_0c250.jpg" border="0" width="470" align="middle" style="margin: 5px;" /></div>\r\n<div>Khoang li ca my bay</div>\r\n<div><img src="http://dantri4.vcmedia.vn/F5PTk2fd0dyFcSMai7us/Image/2011/12/malaysia/maybay926112011_bba58.jpg" border="0" width="470" align="middle" style="margin: 5px;" /></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-family: Tahoma; font-size: 10pt;">Phi cng trong t thchun b </span></div>\r\n<span style="font-family: Tahoma; font-size: 10pt;">\r\n<div><img src="http://dantri4.vcmedia.vn/F5PTk2fd0dyFcSMai7us/Image/2011/12/malaysia/maybay526122011_882b8.jpg" border="0" width="470" align="middle" style="margin: 5px;" /></div>\r\n<div><img src="http://dantri4.vcmedia.vn/F5PTk2fd0dyFcSMai7us/Image/2011/12/malaysia/maybay626122011_346ac.jpg" border="0" width="470" align="middle" style="margin: 5px;" /></div>\r\n<div>Phi cng khng qun kim tra ln cui vic chp hnh cc quy nhv an ton ca tt c mi ngi trn my bay</div>\r\n<div><img src="http://dantri4.vcmedia.vn/F5PTk2fd0dyFcSMai7us/Image/2011/12/malaysia/maybay426122011_88d5c.jpg" border="0" width="420" align="middle" style="margin: 5px;" /></div>\r\n<div>Chic my bay c ca Ch tch tp on Ha Pht vn ang nm ti Ga trc thng Gia Lm cho d n gi ng khng cns hu.</div>\r\n<p align="right"><span style="font-weight: bold;">Lan Hng</span></p>\r\n</span></span>', '', 1, 6, 0, 38, '2012-02-02 05:36:42', 62, '', '2012-02-02 05:45:23', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-02-02 05:36:42', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 3, 0, 72, '', '', 0, 36, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(201, 'ng on Nguyn c: Mua my bay ring l mt vic lm sng sut, hiu qu"', 'ong-doan-nguyen-duc-mua-may-bay-rieng-la-sang-suot-va-hieu-qua', '', 'Mua my bay ring l sng sut, hiu qu  Cch y hn ba nm, ng on Nguyn c, Ch  tch tp on Hong Anh Gia Lai (HAGL) l ngi u tin b hn 8 triu  USD mua chic Beechcraft King Air 350, do hng Raytheon Aircraft (M)  sn xut.<br /> Khng ch c vy, ng c cn mi Anh hng lc lng v trang Nguyn Thnh Trung, nguyn Ph Tng G Vietnam Airlines (VNA) li. <br /><img src="http://dantri4.vcmedia.vn/Ic3EyFHpPWFvMJOJFocc/Image/2011/10/129796400_b90a0.jpg" border="0" width="400" height="300" /><br /><br /> ng on Nguyn c xung sn bay Pleiku trong chuyn bay u tin.<br />Sau ba nm i chuyn  c, ng on Nguyn c tm s: Mua my bay ring l mt vic lm sng  sut, hiu qu, hon ton khng xa x. Ti khng chi ngng hay hng  th nh nhiu ngi ngh. Nhiu ngi hi ti mua my bay ri sao khng  mua du thuyn, ti tr li: Ngi ta sm du thuyn  hng th, cn ti  sm my bay  lm n. Ti cha bao gi s dng my bay cho vic i du  lch.\r\n<p>ng c cng cho bit,  do c th cng vic, ng i li nh con thoi, bt k ngy m. 12 gi  m ng c cn  Ving Chn (Lo) nhng sng hm sau ng c th ch tr  cuc hp ti H Ni. Nu khng c my bay ring, iu ny l khng th.</p>\r\n<p>C my bay ring, ti  tit kim c thi gian, lm c nhiu vic, d dng tip cn c  nhiu d n ln. My bay cng to nn hnh nh tt cho ti trong thng  trng. Hnh nh, khi i my bay ring lm vic vi i tc, nht l i  tc nc ngoi, cng vic cng c thun li hn, ng c chia s.</p>\r\n<p>Tuy nhin,  c c  nhng thun li y, mi thng ng c phi chi ph cho lng phi cng,  xng du, sn bi ln n hn 30.000 USD.</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p align="right">Theo L Thnh Tm</p>', '', 1, 6, 0, 38, '2012-02-02 05:53:11', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-02-02 05:53:11', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 71, '', '', 0, 38, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(202, 'Ch tch tp on Ha Pht sm my bay ring', 'chu-tich-tap-doan-hoa-phat-sam-may-bay-rieng', '', '<div>S tin 17,42 t ng l chi ph ban  u m Ch tch HQT Tp on Ha Pht  b ra  sm my bay ring  cho mnh do nhu cu cng vic. c bit, chic my bay trong tng lai  ny s ch yu phc v cho hot ng khai thc m trong nc.<img src="http://dantri4.vcmedia.vn/F5PTk2fd0dyFcSMai7us/Image/2011/12/malaysia/maybay126122011_a72ee.jpg" border="0" alt="My bay ring ch tch Tp on Ha PHt" title="My bay ch tch Tp on Ha PHt" width="470" height="276" /></div>\r\n<p>Trc i hi c ng thng nin  nm 2010, Ch tch HQT Tp on Ha Pht Trn nh Long cho bit  b  ra khon chi 17,42 t ng l s tin ban u  mua my bay ring.</p>\r\n<p>Ton b s tin t mua bn, thu phi cng, sn bay, cc chi ph lin  quan n hot ng bay u do c nhn ng Long chi tr phc v cho cng  vic nhng hp ng mua bn ny c k kt thng qua Tp on Ha  Pht.</p>\r\n<p>Hin ti, thng v mua bn my bay vn ang trong qu trnh thng  tho hp ng nn chic my bay vn cha v n Vit Nam. Thng tin t  Tp on Ha Pht cng cho bit, y s l my bay tm thp, ln thng,  bay ni a c dng  phc v ch yu cho hot ng khai thc m.</p>\r\n<p>Nh vy, tnh n nay, ng Trn nh Long l ngi th hai ti Vit  Nam cng khai s hu my bay ring (thng tin c th v loi my bay  hin cha c tit l - PV). Trc , ng ch Hong Anh Gia Lai - on  Nguyn c l ngi u tin  Vit Nam sm phi c ring Beechcraft  King Air 350 tr gi 5,1 triu USD.</p>\r\n<p>Trao i vi mt lnh o cc Hng Khng Vit Nam, my bay khi v n  Vit Nam s phi c C quan tiu chun an ton bay kim tra k thut.  Nu t yu cu v k thut, quy trnh sa cha, bo dng v nhn s  th s c cp cc chng ch an ton.</p>\r\n<p>Theo Lut Hng khng dn dng Vit Nam nm 2006, my bay ng k mang  quc tch Vit Nam phi c  cc iu kin: Cha c quc tch ca bt  k quc gia no hoc  xa quc tch nc ngoi; c giy t hp php  chng minh v s hu my bay; ph hp tiu chun k thut do c quan nh  nc c thm quyn quy nh hoc cng nhn; my bay thuc s hu ca t  chc, c nhn Vit Nam v do t chc, c nhn Vit Nam khai thc phi  ng k mang quc tch Vit Nam. B Giao thng vn ti l ni cp giy  chng nhn ng k quc tch my bay.</p>\r\n<p>Bn cnh , my bay ch c php khai thc trong vng tri Vit Nam  khi c giy chng nhn  iu kin bay cn hiu lc do B Giao thng  Vn ti cp hoc cng nhn. Ngi khai thc my bay l c nhn khng  c php khai thc my bay v mc ch thng mi</p>\r\n<p>Lnh o ny cng nhn mnh: bt c mt my bay no trc khi bay ln  tri th phi m bo an ton v khai thc v an ninh quc phng. Theo  , ngoi vic b cm bay qua cc khu vc nhy cm, lin quan n an  ninh quc phng tu bay cng phi c giy php nu mun bay qua vng  tri c cc hot ng t chc l hi hay s kin c yu cu hn ch.</p>\r\n<p align="right"><span style="font-weight: bold;">Lan Hng</span></p>', '', 1, 6, 0, 38, '2012-02-02 05:58:52', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-02-02 05:58:52', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 70, '', '', 0, 37, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(203, 'Cc hng hng khng ua nhau khuyn mi u Xun', 'cac-hang-hang-khong-dua-nhau-hut-khach-dau-xuan', '', 'Trong khi vic i li ca nhiu  ngi trn cc chng cao im sau Tt ang kh khn th VietJetAir  "tung" ra chng trnh khuyn mi ni a. Jetstar Group cng quan tm  n cc i tng hnh khch l lu hc sinh, sinh vin i du hc nc  ngoi  bn v gi r.<br />\r\n<div><a href="http://dantri.com.vn/c76/s76-561163/Gia-re-Vietet-hut-khach-tu-xe-khach.htm"><strong></strong></a></div>\r\n<p align="left">VietJet Air vatung  chng trnh khuyn mi vi gi v 590.000/chng TP.HCM i H Ni v  ngc li, khi hnh t ngy 01/3 - 25/4. Theo , chng trnh p dng  t v v mua v trc tuyn qua website ca hng ch trong vng 48 gi  t 12h ngy 2/2 n 11h59 ngy 4/2.</p>\r\n<div><img src="http://dantri4.vcmedia.vn/zBWMWGSUq5Jhg0bdkuZf/Image/2011/10/VJA2011_9a4a9.jpg" border="0" /><br /><span style="font-family: Tahoma; font-size: 10pt;">VietJetAir "tung" khuyn mi u Xun</span></div>\r\n<p>Trc , VietJetAir cng  tung ra chng trnh khuyn mi v Tt gi t 250.000 t H Ni i TP.HCM.</p>\r\n<p>Cng trong dp u Xun, nhng hnh khch i du hc, du lch, thm  thn s c c hi mua v my bay gi r t Vit Nam i Singapore, Hng  Kng, Malaysia, Philippines, New Zealand, c thng qua chng trnh  khuyn mi u xun ca cc hng hng khng trong Jetstar Group.</p>\r\n<p>Chng trnh c m bn bt u t nay cho n 23h59 pht ngy 3/2,  v do h thng my tnh t ng phn phi ti trang website ca hng  ny.</p>\r\n<p>Theo , mc gi m bn trn ng bay trong khu vc gia TP.HCM -  Singapore t 488.888 ng/chng, gia H Ni - Singapore t 1.188.888  ng/chng, v gi v trn ng bay gia TP.HCM - Kuala Lumpur  (Malaysia) t 812.588 ng/chng. V my bay t H Ni i Auckland (New  Zealand) c Jetstar Group m bn t 6.137.134 ng/chng, gia TP.HCM -  Auckland t 5.437.134 ng chng. Mc gi trn p dng cho chuyn bay  khi hnh trong cc giai on 20/3 - 3/ 4, 11/4 - 23/5, 26/6 - 7/8.</p>\r\n<p>i vi cc ng bay n c khi hnh t 17/4 - 23/5 v 17/7 -  7/8/2012 c gi t t 4.882.472 ng chng gia TP.HCM - Melbourne (c),  H Ni - Melbourne t 5.582.472 ng.</p>\r\n<p>Ring ng bay n Indonesia c m trn cc chuyn bay trong giai  on t 11/4 - 23/5 vi gi v 1.136.289 ng/chng gia TP.HCM -  Jakarta, H Ni - Jakarta t 1.836.289 ng chng; ng bay gia H Ni  - Hng Kng t 2.483.690 ng/chng trn cc chuyn bay t 26/6 -  7/8/2012.</p>\r\n<p align="right"><span style="font-weight: bold;">Qunh Anh</span></p>', '', 1, 6, 0, 38, '2012-02-02 06:03:24', 62, '', '2012-02-02 06:05:32', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-02-02 06:03:24', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 2, 0, 69, '', '', 0, 38, 'robots=\nauthor='),
