(228, 'Gp c gi 8X c Tt l i "pht"', 'gap-co-gai-8x-c-tet-la-di-phuot', '', 'Gp c gi 8X c Tt l i "pht"  C gi tr y la chn dch chuyn trong dp Tt  khng phi bi c khng coi trng s sum hp gia nh m v mun i   c bit nhng iu mi m nh mt cch nh du bc ngot  ngha  trong thi khc bc sang nm mi.\r\n<p>u  xun, tnh c gi cun nht k hnh trnh ca Nguyn Phng Tho - mt  c gi gia 8x, sinh ra vi ln ln  H Ni,  tt nghip H M thut  Cng nghip -  ri bt gp rt nhiu a danh, s kin cng nhng cm  xc v rt nhiu kinh nghim ca c khi k v nhng chuyn i trong ma  xun.</p>\r\n<p>Cui thng Chp nm  2007, Phng Tho thc hin chuyn xa nh u tin trong dp Tt khi  cng m nhy  t, xut pht t H Ni, vo ca khu Cu Treo (H Tnh)  qua Lo ri sang Thi Lan.</p>\r\n<p>Ban u, mc ch ca  chuyn i ch l thm hi h hng. Nhng do trc trc lch trnh trung  chuyn, khi thi khc giao tha ca Tt Vit Nam gn im, Phng Tho  v m chn ng li trong mt nh ngh nh, nm np mnh gia mt thnh  ph xinh xn trn t Thi...</p>\r\n<p>K t , Tt no  Phng Tho cng c nhng chuyn i. Nht k hnh trnh ca ngi l  hnh tr ny ngy mt dy ln. Chuyn ngn nht 5 ngy, di nht 10  ngy.  l nhng m n giao tha v nm mi tng bng ti mt qung  trng trn t nc cha thp Campuchia; l chiu nhng ngy cui nm  tri i trn sng Hng  thnh ph thing Varanasi, vnh Bengan vng  Cancutta, Bc n; l ngy c tit tri ma gi rt ci la ln nh ni  cao 4.000km c Khm vng Vn Nam, Trung Quc; l m tnh lng ngi  tu xuyn qua nhng cnh rng sinh thi hoang s vng Sri Lanca...</p>\r\n<img src="http://dantri4.vcmedia.vn/y0V2Vnsx49nhQPv7HdH/Image/2012/01/tayba2811112_f4f6c.jpg" border="0" alt="Gp c gi 8X c Tt l i &quot;pht&quot;" title="Gap co gai 8X c Tet la di phuot" width="400" height="273" />Phng Tho (ngoi cng bn phi) trong chuyn i n \r\n<p>Sau mi chuyn i v,  Phng Tho thng lao vo kim tin v dnh dm. Khi c khong trn  di chc triu ng cng vi nhng c hi n, vi nhng l do hp l   thuyt phc, c c s tin tng, to iu kin ca gia nh... c  li vc bal ra i..</p>\r\n<p>Do mi thc hin cc  chuyn i, ngi l hnh ny gp kh khn khi chun b  c, tm hiu  thng tin v ni n, gp vn  v sc kho... V sau, quen dn, mi  th tr nn chuyn nghip, thun li hn. C thng ln mng tm thng  tin shop  chuyn dng, v my bay gi r, nhng trang web chuyn dnh  cho dn du lch bi trn th gii...</p>\r\n<p>Trc mi hnh trnh,  Tho tp trung vo vic thit k plan (k hoch). y l vic quan trng  nht. C plan chnh v plan nhp  d tr phng n thay th.    phi c chi tit v t nc tham quan (tng thnh ph, khch sn,  phng tin i li, tng a danh, di tch...), thi gian i, s dng  tng dch v, s tin tiu trong tng ngy...</p>\r\n<p>C gi tr y la chn  dch chuyn trong dp Tt khng phi l bi c khng coi trng s sum  hp, qun t gia nh, khng thch  nh n Tt c truyn Vit Nam...  Mnh  n Tt  nh t b n ln. Mnh vn thch khng kh Tt trong  gia nh.</p>\r\n<p>Tuy nhin, y cng l  dp ngh di ngy v nu may mn r c c, t c v my bay gi  r th i c rt nhiu th v. i  c nhn, c nghe nhng iu mi  m nh mt cch nh du nhng bc ngot  ngha trong thi khc bc  sang nm mi...</p>\r\n<p>V kt qu, trong mi  hnh trnh ma xun, c  tri qua nhng ngy t lo lng cho bn thn,  hc cch tn trng, ho mnh cng vi nhng ngi trong nhm, hc c  cch tr chuyn vi ngi xa l mt cch ci m hn... c bit, mi ln  t chn n mt a danh mi l ln c c tip xc vi mt vn kin  thc mi vi nhiu khc bit.</p>\r\n<p>Khng s dng t duy  ca nhng ngi thch pht  trng men,  lt lt qua qua v  nhng vng t m mnh n, c lun bit cch tn dng nhng c hi   tm ti, quan st ri cm cm nhn, thu tm trong khun hnh ca my  nh, np vo kho tri thc ca mnh nhng g thuc i sng, ngi dn,  phong cnh, vn ho c trng...</p>\r\n<p>V nh  Thi, c c  c du n v nim tin, s thn thin, chn thnh;  Lo l nhng g k  quan v s cht phc;  n  l nhng g thuc v quc o, l chnh  tr si ng, l tt thy nhng ngc nhin, huyn b;  Sri Lanca l  nhng con ngi cc k d thng, nng hu v thin nhin th bao la,  phng khong... Nh nhng dch chuyn m c ln ln, trng thnh v v  cng t tin, giu c.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><strong>Theo Sc khe/ Dn Vit</strong></p>', '', 1, 6, 0, 38, '2012-02-02 12:07:14', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-02-02 12:07:14', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 49, '', '', 0, 42, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(229, 'Cch mi mua v my bay gi r ti Vit Nam', 'cach-moi-mua-ve-may-bay-gia-re-tai-viet-nam', '', 'Hng hng khng gi r Jetstar Pacific quyt nh tung ra cch thc mua v mi, nhiu gi sn phm nh l  khch hng t quyt nh mc chi tr chi ph i li da trn nhu cu thc t. <br />Cch thc ng k v mi c Jetstar trin khai ti trang web bn v Jetstar.com. Theo , hnh khch c nhu cu s bt u chn chuyn bay vi mc gi c bn thp nht hin c trn h thng bao gm ch ngi v 7kg hnh l xch tay. Sau , ty nhu cu, c th chn hnh l k gi theo nhu cu vi cc mc: 15, 20, 25, 30, 35, 40 kg, hoc c th la chn thm gi dch v gia tng km cc iu kin linh hot nh: c php thay i ngy, c hon v, c la chn ch ngi trn my bay.v.v.\r\n<div id="content">\r\n<div style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 13px;"><img src="http://image.tin247.com/vietnamnet/110518120741-368-168.jpg" border="0" alt="Cch mi mua v my bay gi r ti Vit Nam " /></span></div>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Trong mi h s t ch nu c nhiu ngi i cng nhau, mi hnh khch c th chn mc cn khc nhau. Ti a mi khch c chn ti a 40kg hnh l k gi. H thng bn v ca Jetstar Pacific cng cho php hnh khch c chn ng k thm s cn hnh l pht sinh nhng tng cng khng vt qu 40kg. Khch ng k sm s nhn c mc ph r hn so vi ti sn bay.<br /><br />y l hnh thc mua v gip hnh khch c th t xy dng cho mnh gi v ph hp vi ngn sch v nhu cu ca c nhn. Ngay khi chuyn i sang m hnh gi r, Jetstar Pacific tch chi ph sut n ra khi gi v. Ch tnh ring nm 2010, khch bay ca hng ny tit kim c khong trn 100 t ng. Theo thng k, ch c khong 5% tng s khch c nhu cu s dng sut n trn my bay, ch yu tp trung vo cc chuyn bay tra v ti.<br /><br />Trong thng co bo ch pht i ngy 17/5, Jetstar Pacific cho bit, 3 loi gi v mi c tn gi Starter, Starter Plus v Starter Max s thay th cho 3 loi gi v Jetsaver Light, Jetsaver v Jetflex hin ti ang p dng. Cc mc gi v my bay tip tc c phn phi t thp n cao.</p>\r\n<div style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 13px;"><img src="http://image.tin247.com/vietnamnet/110518120741-844-443.jpg" border="0" alt="Cch mi mua v my bay gi r ti Vit Nam " /></span></div>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 13px;">Chia  s vi bo ch, ng T Hu Thanh - Ph Tng Gim c Thng mi Jetstar  Pacific cho bit: S thay i ny s gip khch hng tip cn thm  cch thc mua v mi tit kim hn, st vi nhu cu hn so vi cch mua  v trn gi theo kiu truyn thng trc y."<br /><br />"Chng ti k</span> vng<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 13px;"> s i mi sn phm ny s tip tc gp phn tit kim chi ph i li cho khch hng v x hi" - ng Thanh ni. <br /><br />Jetstar  Pacific cng khuyn co hnh khch nn tm hiu k iu kin ca mi  loi sn phm  c la chn ph hp v tit kim nht theo nhu cu ca  mnh. Trong th</span>i gian<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 13px;"> chuyn i, nu c cc pht sinh, hnh khch c th lin lc vi  Jetstar Pacific qua a ch email ykienkhachhang@jetstarpacific.com.vn,  hoc lin hn vi tng i 19001550 hot ng 24/7  c h tr. <br /><br />Theo ng Thanh, i vi nhng hnh khch  mua v s vn c bo m cc quyn li v iu kin v nh trc y. </span></p>\r\n<div style="text-align: right;"><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 13px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 13px;">Nguyn Phan </span></strong></span></div>\r\n</div>', '', 1, 6, 0, 38, '2012-02-02 12:12:10', 62, '', '2012-02-02 12:15:48', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-02-02 12:12:10', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 2, 0, 48, '', '', 0, 35, 'robots=\nauthor='),
