(232, 'Tha gh thiu v trn my bay t Nht Bn v Vit Nam', 'thua-ghe-thieu-ve-tren-may-bay-tu-nhat-ban-ve-viet-nam', '', 'Tr v t t nc Nht Bn, mt s c gi cho bit trn chuyn bay ca Vietnam Airlines cn trng kh nhiu ch. Trong khi thc t, hnh khch phi cht vt lm mi mua c mt tm v  bay.<br /><br />c gi Nng Vng Phi tham gia chuyn bay t Nht Bn v Vit Nam ngy 16/3 va qua phn nh on cng tc ca anh c 19 ngi tham gia chng trnh o to ca mt t chc ti Nht Bn. Kha hc d kin ko di t ngy 7/3 n ngy 18/3, nhng do thm ha sng thn v ng t, pha Nht ng  cho on Vit Nam v trc 3 ngy so vi d kin. Ton b v my bay ca on 19 ngi u c mua kh hi t lc i, do vy h phi thay i li lch trnh bay  v sm hn d nh.<br /><br />"Chng ti thc s vui mnh trc thng tin Vietnam Airlines thng bo s dng my bay loi to  h tr ngi Vit Nam ra khi nc Nht v qu tht trong bi cnh lon lc, ai cng mun v nh", anh Phi cho bit.<br /><br />Th nhng, vic i v khng d dng cht no. on cng tc ca anh phi lin h v Vit Nam. i l tn tnh gip  song thng tin m on cng tc anh nhn c l tnh hnh khan v. Ban u i l ch c 7 v cho c on 19 ngi. n tra 16/3, on nhn thng tin c tng cng 14 v hng ph thng, 4 ngi phi nng v ln hng thng gia. V n st gi bay, ngi cui cng cng c v  bay.<br /><br />C on tham gia chuyn bay VN953, khi hnh vo lc 19h00 gi a phng, v d kin h cnh xung sn bay Vit Nam lc 2h15 ngy 17/3. Nhng khi ln n my bay, mi ngi ng ngng thy ch hai phn ba gh c khch, cn li l ch  trng.<br /><br />"Cm gic ca ti, v mt s anh ch trong on lc  rt bc xc... Ti sao chng ti rt kh khn  mua c v, c 4 ngi phi tng ln hng C th c n mt phn gh trng hng K vn cn m chng ti khng th mua? Mt bao cng sc, lo lng", anh Phi bc xc k li.<br />Vietnam Airlines<img src="http://image.tin247.com/vnexpress/110319105319-932-600.jpg" border="0" alt="Tha gh thiu v trn my bay t Nht Bn v Vit Nam" title="thua ghe thieu ve tren may bay tu nhat ban ve viet nam" width="484" height="324" /><br />Hnh khch cho bit nhiu ch trn my bay cn nhiu ch trng d trc  mua v kh khn. nh minh ha: Hong H<br /><br />Nhng ngy qua, theo phn nh ca nhiu i l bn v my bay  H Ni, do lng ngi Vit  Nht Bn v nc qu ng nn v trn cc chuyn bay ny thc s rt cng thng. Vietnam Airlines thng bo gim mt na gi v cho cc chuyn bay t Nht Bn v Vit Nam. Th nhng,  s hu c tm v u i ny theo cc i l l khng d dng cht no v hu ht cc chuyn bay u kn.<br /><br />Trc tnh trng ny, anh Phi cng nhiu c gi  t cu hi rng liu Vietnam Airlines  thc s h tr hnh khch mt cch tt nht? Hng s qun l nh th no vi i l bn v ca mnh  hnh khch ri vo cnh cht vt mua v, trong khi hng li bay vi 1/3 gh trng?<br /><br />Trao i vi VnExpress.net i din Vietnam Airlines khng nh vic hnh khch kh mua v trong nhng ngy qua hon ton c tht do qu nhiu ngi Vit, tp trung vo Tokyo c nhu cu v nc . Hin s ngi Vit sng quanh khu vc Th  Nht Bn l hn 10.000 ngi, trong khi mi chuyn bay ca Vietnam Airlines ti a ch ch c 300 ngi, nu s dng my bay Boeing 777.<br /><br />Vic mt s chuyn bay c s lng gh trng nhiu theo i din Vietnam Airlines l do hnh khch khng thu xp c phng tin  ra sn bay. Thng thng, t trng khch ngi Nht trn cc chuyn bay v Vit Nam chim phn ln, khong 80-90%. ng t xy ra khin nh ca b sp, ng x, giao thng nh tr, h thng thng tin lin lc b ct t hoc gin on. iu ny  khin hnh khch c v nhng khng th ln my bay. Do , vic c nhiu ch trng trn my bay c th xut pht t cc nguyn nhn. V d hnh khch thay i k hoch m khng thng bo hoc mun thng bo nhng khng th v t lin lc. Mt tnh hung khc c th xy ra l v giao thng nh tr nn hnh khch khng thu xp c phng tin  ra sn bay.<br /><br />Cng khng loi tr kh nng hnh khch nm trong vng b nh hng nng n bi ng t v i khi, tnh hung thng tm xy ra, h c th mt tch, i din Vietnam Airlines ni.<br /><br />i din Vietnam Airlines cng cho bit nhiu chuyn ca hng thi gian gn y s khch c v m khng ln my bay din ra kh ph bin. "Thm ch c chuyn s ngi b ch ln ti trn 140 ngi.  l cha k tnh trng hy ch nhiu t c 2 u Vit Nam v Nht Bn", v i din ny ni.<br /><br />Theo ng, tnh trng b ch ny cng khin hng nh hng nghim trng n hot ng sn xut kinh doanh. Trong khi ,  h tr hnh khch v nc, hng vn duy tr u n lch bay, s dng my bay to hn v cng thc hin gim gi v.<br /><br />\r\n<div style="text-align: right;"><strong>Hng Anh</strong></div>', '', 1, 6, 0, 38, '2012-02-02 12:20:27', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-02-02 12:20:27', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 46, '', '', 0, 39, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(233, 'ua nhau mua v my bay trc 16/5', 'dua-nhau-mua-ve-may-bay-truoc-16-5', '', 'Quyt nh tng gi v my bay t 16/5 ca hng hng khng quc gia Vit Nam (Vietnam Airlines) c cng b trc gn 1 tun  khin nhiu ngi i t mua v my trc ngy ny  tranh th mc gi r.<br /><img src="http://image.tin247.com/vnmedia/110513220554-539-530.jpg" border="0" alt="ua nhau mua v my bay trc 16/5" title="dua nhau mua ve may bay truoc 16-5" width="320" height="235" /><br />c bit, gi v p dng t ngy 16/5 (th hai tun ti) s tng khong 20% so vi mc gi hin hnh. Tuy nhin, nu t v v thanh ton trc ngy 16/5, khch hng c th vn c hng mc gi hin ti cho nhng chuyn bay trong vng 1 nm ti. Hn na, vi mc gi v ph thng, khch hng c th i ngy bay min ph. V th, khng t ngi tranh th c hi t mua v my bay cho nhng k ngh trong nm.<br /><br />Anh Dng, mt phng vin ti H Ni cho bit :Ngh h hng nm, gia nh u t chc i du lch cng bn b, to c hi cho bn tr giao lu v ngh ngi. c c thng tin sp tng gi v, ti quyt nh chn ngy lun v t v my bay trc  vn c hng gi c.<br /><br />Ch Linh, mt nhn vin ngn hng cng c  kin tng t v ch cn chia s kinh nghim :Mc d, cc hng u tuyn b s vn cn hng v gi r  khch hng chn la, nhng d sao, v gi r cng c nhng iu kin cht ch km theo. Chng hn nh khng c php i ngy bay, phi bay vo nhng chuyn sm hoc mun V vy, t trc t gi vi gi v ph thng vi cc iu kin la chn thoi mi theo ti vn li hn.<br /><br />Mt nhn vin ca i l v my bay cho bit, t khi c quyt nh tng khung gi trn ca B Ti chnh cch y 2 tun, s lng khch t mua v trc tng mnh. Khng ch cc c nhn, cc cng ty du lch cng tranh th m kh nhiu v trc hn tng gi. Hin, vic t ch trn cc tuyn bay ng khch nh H Ni   Nng, H Ni  Nha Trang trong vi tun ti l kh kh khn, c bit l vi nhng nhm khch ng. <br /><br />Trc , 2 hng hng khng ni a l Jetstar Pacific v Air Mekong cng thng bo k hoch tng gi v my bay theo khung trn. Tuy nhin, mc gi mi c p dng ngay khi cng b. C th, hng hng khng gi r Jestar Pacific chnh thc tng gi v my bay t 7/5 theo mc trn mi l 22%. Mc gi cao nht c iu chnh l 2.450.000 ng/chng, thp nht l khong 900.000 ng/chng.<br /><br />Vic gi v my bay cng l nguyn nhn chnh khin nhiu cng ty du lch rc rch tng gi tour. Hin Vietravel l cng ty du lch ln u tin cho bit s tng 5% gi tt c cc tour t ma h nm nay. Nhiu cng ty khc cho bit c th s tng gn tng ng vi mc tng ca gi v my bay.<br /><br />Theo cc cng ty du lch, do tc ng ca gi c tng, c bit l gi v my bay tng nn nu khng tng gi th kh duy tr c li nhun. Tuy nhin, pha cc hng hng khng li cho rng d gi tng nhng trn thc t cc cng ty du lch c nhiu thun li khi mua v, chng hn nh mua theo on, mua trc ngy bay rt xa v rt t khi h phi mua v my bay vi gi ng trn. Do vy, kh c th ni, gi tour tng l do gi v my bay tng.<br /><br /><br />Dng An', '', 1, 6, 0, 38, '2012-02-02 12:23:16', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-02-02 12:23:16', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 45, '', '', 0, 38, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(234, 'Sp khai trng ng bay thng di nht Vit Nam', 'sap-khai-truong-duong-bay-thang-dai-nhat-viet-nam', '', 'Ngy 28/4 ti y, Hng hng khng Air Mekong s chnh thc ct cnh bay thng chng H Ni - Ph Quc. y l hng u tin khai thc ng bay thng di nht Vit Nam t H Ni n Ph Quc khng chuyn chuyn qua TP.HCM.<br /><img src="http://image.tin247.com/vnmedia/110421225834-590-339.jpg" border="0" alt="Sp khai trng ng bay thng di nht Vit Nam" title="Sp khai trng ng bay thng di nht Vit Nam" width="293" height="235" /><br />Theo ng on Quc Vit, Ch tch Cng ty TNHH u t Pht trin Sn xut H Long (Tp on BIM)  cng ty m ca hng hng khng Air Mekong, vi ng bay mi ny, khong cch v a l v thi gian s c rt ngn ng k, thun tin cho du khch pha Bc n vi mt trong nhng vng bin o xa xi nht ca T Quc.<br /><br />Theo lnh o Cc Hng khng Vit Nam, o ngc Ph Quc t nhiu nm nay vn lun l im n l tng nhng kh thc hin i vi du khch pha Bc. Do nm tn cc Nam xa xi, ng bay qu di, chi ph cao, nn nhng chuyn i ti Ph Quc kh rc ri cho hnh khch.<br /><br />Thng thng, cc chuyn bay bt u t H Ni u phi dng ti TP.HCM  chuyn chuyn. Hnh khch s mt khong mt thi gian kh di  chuyn sang my bay c nh mi c th ti Ph Quc. Khi chuyn chuyn, vic mua v t TPHCM i Ph Quc cng khng h n gin. i khi, hnh khch khng th c ch trn chuyn bay ra o ngay trong ngy m phi i chuyn bay tip theo vo ngy hm sau.<br /><br />Sn bay Ph Quc d mi c nng cp t u nhng nm 2000 nhng ch c mt ng bay nh v rt ngn, thch hp cho loi my bay c nh, my bay cnh qut. Trong khi , t H Ni n Ph Quc li l chng bay di nht trong cc tuyn ng bay ni a. Cc my bay nh khng th  nhin liu cng nh  an ton  thc hin mt chng bay di n th. V vy vic hnh khch phi chuyn hai chuyn t my bay ln H Ni - TPHCM sang my bay nh t TPHCM - Ph Quc l rt bt tin v mt thi gian.<br /><br />D kin, thi gian bay H Ni n Ph Quc l 2h30pht. Cc chuyn bay hng ngy xut pht t H Ni lc 6h sng v hnh trnh Ph Quc tr v H Ni h cnh lc 12h40 vi 2 hng dch v: hng Deluxe v hng Economy, trong  gi v hng Economy l 2.273.000 ng (cha bao gm thu v ph).<br /><br />Trn ng bay ny, Air Mekong khai thc i bay Bombadier - CRJ 900 vi 90 ch ngi cho php bay khng cn dng,  tip nhin liu. CRJ 900 c th dng  v ct cnh ti tt c cc ng bay kh, cc sn bay nh ca Vit Nam, trong  c Ph Quc. <br />', '', 1, 6, 0, 38, '2012-02-02 12:27:00', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-02-02 12:27:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 44, '', '', 0, 39, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(235, 'Khi mua v my bay qua bu in gi s tit kim hn', 'khi-mua-ve-may-bay-qua-buu-dien-se-tiet-kiem-hon', '', ' c th gip khch hng tip cn c v my bay mt cch thun tin nht, thi gian va qua hai Hng hng khng Jetstar Pacific v Air Mekong  chnh thc k kt v trin khai phng thc bn v qua bu in.<br /><img src="http://image.tin247.com/vnmedia/110418152551-495-29.jpg" border="0" alt="Khi mua v my bay qua bu in gi s tit kim hn" title="Khi mua v my bay qua bu in gi s tit kim hn" width="314" height="233" /><br />Mi y, Hng hng khng Air Mekong  thc hin k hoch m rng mng li phn phi bng hp ng hp tc chin lc vi Tp on Bu chnh Vin thng Vit Nam (VNPT).<br /><br />Theo , Cng ty TNHHH u t pht trin Sn xut H Long (BIM Group), cng ty m ca Hng hng khng tr Air Mekong va qua  chnh thc t quan h hp tc chin lc vi Tng cng ty Bu chnh Vit Nam (VNPost).<br /><br />C th, VNPost s cho php BIM Group t chc h thng phn phi v my bay in t ca Air Mekong qua 18.000 bu cc v im phc v ca nh cung cp dch v bu chnh ln nht Vit Nam thng qua hnh thc i l bn v, bao gm c thanh ton tin t v in t ti bu cc.<br /><br />Nh vy, khch hng khi mua v my bay ca Air Mekong c th thanh ton tin v my bay trn ton b h thng bu in trn c nc.<br /><br />Trc , Hng hng khng gi r Jetstar Pacific cng  trin khai 1.100 im giao dch ti bu in, m nhim chc nng thu h tin mt t khch hng  ng k t ch v my bay ti Jetstar.com hoc in thoi n tng i 19001550 (hoc 08.39550550).<br /><br />Vi hnh thc ny, hnh khch  cc vng xa, nng thn cng c th d dng mua v my bay gi r ca Jetstar Pacific m khng phi tn thi gian di chuyn n cc im bn v  cc thnh ph ln nh trc y.<br /><br />Thay v phi n cc phng v  trung tm, thnh ph ln  mua v my bay, khch hng ch cn ng k qua in thoi tng i ca Jetstar Pacific hoc qua internet v n im bu in gn nht ti 64 tnh thnh ca Vit Nam l c th thanh ton. iu ny khng ch tit kim ng k thi gian cho hnh khch, m cn gim chi ph x hi ng k. c bit, vic trin khai hnh thc ny cn gip Jetstar Pacific a sn phm ca mnh n gn vi cng ng khch hng, c bit l nhng i tng s dng v my bay tit kim theo m hnh hng khng gi r m Jetstar Pacific ang kinh doanh, i din Jetstar Pacific cho hay.<br /><br />Vic m rng mng li bn v trong c nc, l mt trong nhng kh khn ban u m hng vn chuyn mi no cng gp phi. V vy, vic tn dng c s h tng ca VNPT hay nhng i tc khc  nhanh chng m rng h thng phn phi l mt gii php chin lc tt, gip khch hng c th tip cn dch v mt cch d dng v thun tin nht, i din ca Air Mekong cho bit. <br />', '', 1, 6, 0, 38, '2012-02-02 12:29:58', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-02-02 12:29:58', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 43, '', '', 0, 37, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(236, 'Mua v my bay bng th ni a BIDV', 'mua-ve-may-bay-bang-the-noi-dia-bidv', '', 'Khch hng ang s dng th ni a ca BIDV c th t v my bay ti trang web http://www.vietnamairlines.com/ v thc hin thanh ton ti h thng ATM ca BIDV  63 tnh thnh trong c nc.<br /><img src="http://image.tin247.com/vnexpress/110406134211-891-889.jpg" border="0" alt="Mua v my bay bng th ni a BIDV" title="Mua v my bay bng th ni a BIDV" width="450" height="286" /><br />y l chng trnh do ngn hng u t v Pht trin Vit Nam (BIDV), Cng ty c phn Dch v Th Smartlink v Vietnam Airlines phi hp trin khai dnh cho khch hng ang s dng th ni a ca BIDV. Dch v thanh ton v my bay qua ATM p dng cho tt c cc ch th ghi n ni a ca BIDV nh BIDV Harmony, BIDV eTrans, BIDV Moving, BIDV Power, eTrans 365+, Vn Dm.<br />Mua v my bay bng th ni a BIDV<br /><br /> giao dch, khch hng ch cn thc hin theo ba bc:<br /><br />Bc 1: Vo trang web ca Vietnam Airlines v ng k mua v my bay bng th ni a ca BIDV.<br /><br />Bc 2: Thc hin thanh ton bng cch nhp m ch do Vietnam Airlines cung cp v la chn thanh ton ti ATM ca BIDV.<br /><br />Bc 3: Nhn v my bay qua e-mail (v in t).<br /><br />Khch hng khi s dng dch v, tnh nng thanh ton ti ATM  c ngn hng BIDV kch hot sn s khng cn thc hin thm bt c th tc ng k no ti ngn hng. c bit, BIDV cng p dng chnh sch min ph cho dch v thanh ton mi ny.<br /><br />(Ngun: Smartlink)', '', 1, 6, 0, 38, '2012-02-02 12:32:24', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-02-02 12:32:24', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 42, '', '', 0, 38, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(237, 'Chnh ph bo lnh cho VNA mua 30 my bay mi', 'chinh-phu-bao-lanh-cho-vna-mua-30-may-bay-moi', '', 'Hng Hng khng Quc gia Vit Nam (Vietnam Airlines) s c Chnh ph bo lnh cho cc giao dch thu, mua hn 30 my bay A321-200 khai thc trong giai on t nm 2011 n ht 2015.<br /><img src="http://image.tin247.com/vnmedia/110502112342-279-299.jpg" border="0" alt="Chnh ph bo lnh cho VNA mua 30 my bay mi" title="Chnh ph bo lnh cho VNA mua 30 my bay mi" width="300" height="240" /><br />Th tng  c vn bn ng  v vic bo lnh cc giao dch thu mua 8 my bay A321-200 ca VNA. ng thi, Vietnam Airlines cng c duyt phng n mua 26 my bay A321-200 trong giai on t nm 2011 n 2015. D kin vo cui nm nay, VNA m ng bay thng t Vit Nam i Anh Quc v M.<br /><br />Vietnam Airlines ang y mnh tin trnh c phn ha. Mi y, B Giao thng Vn ti cng bo co Th tng v c ch u thu thu t vn quc t  c phn ho Hng. Trc , VNA   xut gi gi thu t vn ny l gn 3,9 triu USD. Vietnam Airlines cng  ngh chn 9 nh thu quc t c  iu kin vo danh sch mi thu.<br /><br />\r\n<div style="text-align: right;"><strong>DDDN</strong></div>', '', 1, 6, 0, 38, '2012-02-02 12:35:11', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-02-02 12:35:11', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 41, '', '', 0, 38, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(238, 'S tng gi, nhiu ngi vi mua v my bay', 'so-tang-gia-nhieu-nguoi-voi-mua-ve-may-bay', '', 'Thng tin gi v my bay c th tng ti 22,7% khin nhiu ngi c nhu cu i li bng ng hng khng  tranh th mua v  tch tr.<br /><img src="http://image.tin247.com/vnexpress/110413232925-418-159.jpg" border="0" alt="S tng gi, nhiu ngi vi mua v my bay" title="S tng gi, nhiu ngi vi mua v my bay" width="420" height="281" /><br />Theo k hoch, gia thng 7, c gia nh ch Huyn  TP HCM s bay ra H Ni. Mc ch chnh ca chuyn i l cho 2 cu con trai ngh h v tranh th v thm ng b  H Nam.<br />S tng gi, nhiu ngi vi mua v my bay<br />Gi v my bay d kin s tng thm 22,7%. nh: Hong H.<br /><br />Cch y mt tun, ch  ra i l bn v quen thuc  t 4 tm v kh hi cho c nh. Ch cho bit, thng 7 khng phi l t cao im v cng khng c s kin hay l hi no quan trng nn v my bay khng khan him. "Ti mua v my bay sm l  trnh t tng gi v sp ti", ch gii thch.<br /><br />"t trc s chn c gi bay hp l li c th trnh mua phi dp gi v my bay tng. Thi bui kh khn tit kim c ng no hay ng y", ch Huyn tm s.<br /><br />Anh Phan Sn  Ty Sn, H Ni cng va yu cu nhn vin t trc cho 7 tm v kh hi chng H Ni -  Nng v H Ni - TP HCM  s dng cho t nay n ht thng 9. Anh Sn c 2 chi nhnh cng ty ti Si Gn v  Nng nn thng xuyn i li trn 2 tuyn bay ny. "Ti t v my bay trc v bit rng kiu g gi cng s tng", anh Sn ni.<br /><br />Anh cho rng, gi v my bay tng 22,7% l mc kh cao. "Theo ti tm hiu th 22,7% l mc trung bnh. Nu phn ra tng chng th cc chuyn bay trn trc chnh trong  c H Ni - TP HCM hay  Nng s c t l tng cao hn", anh Sn phn tch. Vi 7 tm v kh hi, anh Sn nhm tnh tit kim c vi triu ng, nu gi v my bay tng.<br /><br />Ngun tin t cc hng hng khng Vietnam Airlines, Jetstar Pacific v Air Mekong cho hay chuyn hnh khch i mua v my bay sm v lo tng gi l c tht. Ch tnh ring chuyn bay kh hi H Ni - TP HCM  c vi nghn khch hng ng k trc vo cc thi im thng 7, thng 8 ti. Thm ch, mt s chuyn bay dp Tt cng  c khch ng k mua v.<br /><br />Mt cn b ca Vietnam Airlines cng tit l chuyn  "xi" bn b, ngi thn tranh th mua v my bay trc  tit kim thi gian, chi ph. ng ny cho rng nu mua ngay by gi cho cc chuyn bay sp ti chc chn s tit kim c t nht 20% nu phng n tng gi v my bay c quyt trong thng 4.<br /><br />u tun trc, B Ti chnh  tip nhn phng n tng gi v my bay do pha B Giao thng Vn ti - n v trc tip qun l cc hng hng khng gi sang. Theo d kin, gi v my bay s tng trung bnh 22,7%. B Ti chnh ang tin hnh ly  kin mt s n v c lin quan v d kin ban hnh, p dng ngay cui thng 4 ny.<br /><br />Hin nay, gi cao nht  bao gm c thu v ph vi chng bay nm trong c ly 1.280 km tr ln l H Ni - Cn Th v H Ni - Ph Quc l 2,5 triu ng. Chng H Ni - TP HCM nm trong c ly 850 km tr ln l 2,03 triu ng. Cc chng bay cn li c gi trn t 682.000 ng n 1,182 triu ng.<br /><br />\r\n<div style="text-align: right;"><strong>Hng Anh</strong></div>', '', 1, 6, 0, 38, '2012-02-02 12:39:28', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-02-02 12:39:28', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 40, '', '', 0, 35, 'robots=\nauthor=');
