(243, 'u nm 2011, mua v my bay ch 300.000 VN/chng', 'dau-nam-2011-mua-ve-may-bay-chi-300-ngan', '', 'Hng hng khng gi r Jetstar Pacific va thng bo s thc hin chng trnh bn v r trn cc ng bay ni a Vit Nam vi mc gi t 300.000 ng/chng.<br /><br />Chng trnh khuyn mi u nm mi ca Jetstar Pacific km theo thng ip tip tc mang li c hi c bay cho ngy cng nhiu khch hng ti Vit Nam.<br /><br />Theo , v my bay s c m bn trong 3 ngy lin tc, bt u t 0 gi 1 pht ngy th Su, 7/1 n 23 gi 59 pht ngy 09/01/2011.<br /><img src="http://image.tin247.com/vietnamnet/110107085701-387-60.jpg" border="0" alt="u nm 2011, mua v my bay ch 300.000 VN/chng" title="u nm 2011, mua v my bay ch 300.000 VN/chng" width="480" height="322" /><br />Ngy cng nhiu ngi c c hi c bay vi hng khng gi r<br />V do h thng my tnh t ng phn phi ti trang web bn v ca Jetstar Pacific (www.jetstar.com), trn cc chuyn bay c ngy khi hnh trong cc giai on 5/4 - 25/4/2011 v 5/5 - 15/5/2011.<br /><br />C th:<br /><br />Chng trnh p dng cho nhng hnh khch ng k v thanh ton trc tuyn ti www.jetstar.com bng cc loi th tn dng v th ghi n ni a  c chp nhn thanh ton. Bao gm: Th tn dng Visa, Master Card, JCB, Amex do cc ngn hng trong nc v quc t pht hnh; Th ghi n ni a - ATM ca cc ngn hng Vietcombank, Vietinbank, ng , VIB, HD Bank.<br />Hoc thanh ton trc tuyn qua dch v eBanking ca cc ngn hng Techcombank, ng , Tin Phong Bank.<br /><br />u nm 2011, mua v my bay ch 300.000 VN/chng<br /><br />Gi v nu trn l loi JetSaver Light dnh cho nhng khch hng ch mang 7kg hnh l xch tay (kch thc tiu chun: 23cm chiu rng, 34cm chiu cao, 48cm chiu di), cha bao gm thu, ph v cc khon ph thu nu c.<br /><br />Nhng ngi c nhu cu mang nhiu hn hnh l xch tay c th la chn loi v JetSaver lun hin th song song trn h thng, vi mc gi ch cao hn JetSaver Light nu trn 65.000ng/chng  c tiu chun 20kg hnh l k gi v 7 kg hnh l xch tay min ph.<br /><br />t bn v r ln ny khng p dng ti ti cc Phng v v i l ca Jetstar Pacific v cc hnh thc thanh ton sau.<br />Jetstar Pacific ang khai thc trn 42 chuyn bay ni a Vit Nam mi ngy bng i my bay 7 chic, gm Airbus A320 v Boeing 737-400. Hin i bay ca hng ny cng ang ln lt c mang sang Singapore bo dng  phc v Tt Tn Mo sp ti.<br /><br />\r\n<div style="text-align: right;"><strong>Nguyn Phan </strong></div>', '', 1, 6, 0, 38, '2012-02-02 12:51:19', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-02-02 12:51:19', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 35, '', '', 0, 37, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(244, 'Pht v tro lu sn v my bay r ca gii tr ', 'phuot-va-trao-luu-san-va-may-bay-gia-re-cua-gioi-tre', '', 'Mt b phn gii tr ang say m vi khi nim pht v khng ngn ngi tranh th thi gian  sn nhng chic v r cho chuyn i ca mnh.<br /><br />Pht qua cc din n<br /><br />Trc y, mt b phn gii tr tn dng nhng ngy ngh cui tun, t t chc cc chuyn i gn bng tu ha hoc xe  t. Trn cc din n du lch, thng xut hin cc dng tin nhn gia nh em ang chun b i du lch, ai bit  u v r, phng r ch gip.<br /><br />K t khi ti Vit Nam xut hin hng khng gi r, trn cc din n ny li xut hin nhng dng thng tin trao i v v my bay gi r v kinh nghim mua v.<br /><br /><img src="http://image.tin247.com/vietnamnet/110101061223-106-918.jpg" border="0" alt="Pht v tro lu sn v my bay r ca gii tr " title="Pht v tro lu sn v my bay r ca gii tr " width="257" height="400" /><br />Cc din n lun xut hin nhng nhm t vn "sn" v r<br />Lt qua trang webtretho, thng xuyn c cu hi ai c kinh nghim t v gi r, nht l t khi em bit Jetstar Pacific c chng trnh khuyn mi gi v ch 150k, nhng ch bit khi no mi book. V cng cc ph, thu dch v th khong bao nhiu h, c nh gip em vi nh, em cm nhiu nhiu . Thnh vin ln ting v sau  l nhng thnh vin khc bt u t vn. Sau khi t v thnh cng, thnh vin ny khng qun thng bo v cm n mi ngi.<br /><br />Anh Tun, thnh vin ca mt nhm pht cho bit rng cc bn ca anh thng t chc i du lch vo nhng ngy ngh l, hoc cui tun. Nhu cu ca bn mnh l c n ni cn n, v vy min l tit kim thi gian, v cng tit kim c nhiu chi ph i li cng tt. Bn tr ny cho bit, nu nhm c 5 ngi, tit kim 100 nghn/v my bay th nhm cng  c 500 nghn,  cho mt ba n tm c ti im du lch.<br /><br />Sn v r, tro lu mi<br /><br />Mi khi c chng trnh khuyn mi ca cc hng hng khng, ni bn tn nhiu nht thng l cc din n ca gii tr. C nhiu bn vui mng v  sn thnh cng c v r, cng c bn tht vng. Thng mi khi c v r, nhm bn em chia nhau ra  cng trao i trn mng v phn cng ng k. Bn no ng k c th thng bo  mi ngi bit, nhng ngi khng ng k c th nh ngm ngi vi mc gi cao hn mt cht  bay cng nhm. Cng c khi nhm phn cng bn no sn gii nht  ph trch lun phn t v my bay, anh Tun ni.<br /><br />Trao i vi chng ti, i din truyn thng Jetstar Pacfic cho bit, v my bay gi r lun c hng phn phi trn trang web bn v (www.jetstar.com) theo chng trnh gi r hng ngy. Ngoi ra, cc chng trnh bn v r cng thng c thc hin ty tng thi im  kch thch nhu cu i li. Khch hng mua c v gi r thng l nhng ngi am hiu cng ngh thng tin v s dng thnh tho internet.<br /><br />Cc hng hng khng thng khuyn khch hng nn ln k hoch i li sm, khng nn t ch qu ng ngi cng lc, v lm quen vi cch thc mua v r trc khi ng k. Tuy nhin, mi nhm pht li c nhng chiu khc nhau v h tn dng ti a kinh nghim ca mnh  dnh c tm v r mt cch nhanh nht.<br /><br />Tht th v khi i du lch vi gi v ch bng xe , anh nh - mt chuyn gia cng ngh thng tin v l ngi thch du lch chia s. Mi ln sn c v r, mnh li thng bo cho bn b bit  chia vui v hng dn h ng k  cng i du lch.<br /><br />Lm th no  mua v gi r<br /><br />V my bay gi r thng ch phn phi trn internet, cha bao gm cc khon thu, dch v khc. Cc khon dch v ca hng khng gi r cng kh phong ph, bao gm c bo him du lch, ngay n cc hnh thc thanh ton cng c ph khc nhau ty theo la chn. V vy,  tit kim ti a chi ph, nhng ngi mua v cn tm hiu k trc khi quyt nh.<br /><br />Ti Vit Nam, Jetstar Pacific l hng hng khng duy nht hot ng theo m hnh gi r. K t khi chuyn i, hng ny thng xuyn m rng cc tin ch thanh ton qua internet.<br /><br />Pht v tro lu sn v my bay r ca gii tr 2010<br />Ngy cng nhiu gii tr sn v r  i du lch<br />Bn cnh vic ng k v mua v ti cc phng v, i l chnh theo phng thc truyn thng. Hin nay, khch cng c th ng k trc tip ti www.jetstar.com v thanh ton trc tuyn bng cc loi th tn dng ph bin nh Visa, Master Card, JCB, AMEX do cc ngn hng trong nc v quc t pht hnh, hoc th ghi n ni a (ATM) ca Vietcombank, Vietinbank, Ngn hng ng , HD Bank, VIB, dch v ngn hng in t F@st I-Bank ca Techcombank.<br /><br />i vi nhng khch hng khng dng th, c th la chn ng k thanh ton sau v ra thanh ton ti cc im giao dch ca Techcombank hoc trn 1.100 im giao dch bu in (VNPT) trn ton quc.<br /><br />Mt s chng trnh bn v r c bit thng ch p dng i vi hnh thc thanh ton trc tuyn.  c th thanh ton, ch th cn phi ng k chc nng thanh ton trc tuyn vi ngn hng pht hnh trc khi mua v.<br /><br />Cng c thanh ton ch l yu t cn. Thi quen, kinh nghim, v k nng s dng internet l nhng yu t quan trng to nn s thnh cng trong vic mua v. i din Jetstar Pacific cng cho bit,  to thm s tin li cho sn chi sn v r, Jetstar Pacific va ng dng thm tin ch Cng c tm kim v gi r ti www.jetstar.com. Ngi mua v ch cn nhp chut vo biu tng ca cng c ny v chn ngy d kin, h thng s hin th mc gi r nht trong 1 thng, trc 15 ngy v sau 15 ngy ca ngy cn tm.<br /><br />S pht trin ca cng ngh thng tin  v ang to thm nhiu tin ch, ng dng cho cc lnh vc trong x hi. iu c th d dng nhn thy l mua v my bay gi y khng cn l iu qu kh khn vi nhiu ngi.<br /><br /> Nguyn Phan', '', 1, 6, 0, 38, '2012-02-02 12:53:58', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-02-02 12:53:58', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 34, '', '', 0, 37, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(245, 'V my bay Tt vn cn', 've-may-bay-tet-van-con', '', 'Chng H Ni - TP HCM dp Tt ca Vietnam Airlines nu khch hng chp nhn bay vo cc gi mun hoc sng sm vn c th mua c. Jestar vn cn v cho chng TP HCM - H Ni.<br /><br />Cch y 2 thng, hu ht cc ch trn chuyn bay tuyn TP HCM i Hu v Quy Nhn ca Vietnam Airlines, khi hnh vo ngy 26-27 thng chp (m lch) v chiu ngc li mng 5 Tt  c khch hng t mua. Hin ti, hai chng bay ny cn rt t v. Ring ng bay H Ni - TP HCM nu khch hng chp nhn bay vo cc gi mun hoc sng sm vn c th mua c v.<br /><img src="http://image.tin247.com/vnexpress/101106150021-827-901.jpg" border="0" alt="V my bay Tt vn cn" title="V my bay Tt vn cn" width="450" height="306" /><br />Hnh khch phi t mua sm mi c c v my bay vi lch trnh hp l. nh: Hong H.<br /><br />Ngun tin t Hng hng khng gi r Jetstar Pacific cho bit tnh n ngy 29/10, cc chuyn bay t TP HCM i Vinh, Hu, Hi Phng khi hnh trong cc ngy 26/1 n 2/2/2011  gn kn ch.  chiu ngc li, v  bn ht trn cc chuyn bay Hu - TP HCM khi hnh t ngy 6 n 13/2/2011; Hi Phng - TP HCM khi hnh t ngy 6 n 8/2/2011.<br /><br />Ring hai ng bay TP HCM -  Nng v TP HCM - H Ni c tn sut khai thc kh cao vi 8 chuyn v 22 chuyn mi ngy nn Jetstar Pacific vn cn v.<br /><br /> p ng nhu cu i li ca hnh khch, Hng hng khng Quc gia Vit Nam (Vietnam Airlines) va cng b tng chuyn trn cac ng bay c d bo l cng thng vo cao im Tt Nguyn n t ngy 15 thng Chp n ngy 17 thng Ging. Theo Vietnam Airlines, giai on Tt, nhu cu i li ca hnh khch trn cc chng TP HCM - H Ni v TP HCM -  Nng s tng khong 20%. Do , tm thi, hng c k hoch tng 21-28% s gh trn cc ng bay ny.<br /><br />C th, trn chng bay H Ni - TP HCM - H Ni, Vietnam Airlines s tng khong 7.300 gh mi ngy cho mt chiu bay. Cn chng TP HCM -  Nng - TP HCM tng 28% so vi nm ngoi, tng ng vi 3.200 gh mi ngy cho mt chiu bay. Cc chng bay khc nh Quy Nhn, Hu, Vinh, Hi Phng, Ph Quc... Vietnam Airlines ang ln k hoch tng chuyn cn c theo nhu cu thc t ca th trng.<br /><br />Trong khi , cc hng hng khng khc c tuyn bay ni a nh Jetstar Pacific, Vasco v Air Mek