(247, 'Chiu nay, bn v my bay gi t 350.000 ng', 'chieu-nay-ve-may-bay-gia-tu-350000-dong', '', '- Hng hng khng gi r Jetstar Pacific thng bo tip tc thc hin chng trnh bn v my bay gi r c bit vo ngy hm nay, 20/5/2011 trn cc trc ng bay gia TP.HCM  H Ni v gia H Ni   Nng.<br /><img src="http://image.tin247.com/vnmedia/110520110207-556-354.jpg" border="0" alt="Chiu nay, bn v my bay gi t 350.000 ng" title="Chiu nay, bn v my bay gi t 350.000 ng" width="320" height="240" /><br />Theo , bt u t 14 gi n 17 gi ngy mai (20/5), v my bay s c m bn ti trang web www.jetstar.com vi mc gi t 350 nghn ng gia H Ni   Nng, t 700 nghn ng gia TP.HCM  H Ni.<br /><br />Chng trnh ln ny tip tc p dng cho nhng hnh khch c k hoch i li sm  tit kim chi ph i li, c ngy khi hnh trong giai on t 7/9 n 5/10/2011.<br /><br />Gi v nu trn l loi v Starter vi ch ngi trn my bay v 7kg hnh l xch tay. Hnh khch cng c th ng k mua thm s cn (kg) hnh l k gi theo cc mc 15, 20, 25, 30, 35, 40kg v cc gi iu kin linh hot ngay thi im ng k ti www.jetstar.com.<br /><br /> Vic thanh ton phi c thc hin trc tuyn bng cc loi th tn dng v th ghi n ni a  c chp nhn thanh ton (bao gm: Th tn dng Visa, Master Card, JCB, Amex do cc ngn hng trong nc v quc t pht hnh; Th ghi n ni a - ATM ca cc ngn hng Vietcombank, Vietinbank, ng , VIB, HD Bank.). Hoc thanh ton trc tuyn qua dch v eBanking ca cc ngn hng Techcombank, ng , Tin Phong Bank. <br /><br />Tuy nhin, chng trnh bn v ny khng p dng ti cc Phng v v i l ca Jetstar.<br /><br />Dng An', '', 1, 6, 0, 38, '2012-02-02 13:02:00', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-02-02 13:02:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 31, '', '', 0, 41, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(248, 'VietJet Air bn v 100.000 ng chiu H Ni - TP HCM', 'vietjet-air-ban-ve-100000-dong-chieu-ha-noi-tp-hcm', '', 'Va cng b bt u bay chuyn u tin vo ngy 25/12, hng hng khng gi r VietJet hm nay  thng bo bn mt s v chng TP HCM - H Ni c 100.000 ng. Chng trnh bn n ht ngy 11/12.<br /><br />Chng trnh khuyn mi p dng cho cc chuyn bay khi hnh t ngy 25/12 n 30/4/2012 (c c giai on Tt) vi gi 100.000 ng mi v mt chiu chng TP HCM - H Ni.<br /><img src="http://image.tin247.com/vnexpress/111205170451-43-136.jpg" border="0" alt="VietJet Air bn v 100.000 ng chiu H Ni - TP HCM" title="VietJet Air bn v 100.000 ng chiu H Ni - TP HCM" width="490" height="263" /><br />VietJetAir khuyn mi 100.000 ng v my bay. nh: VietJetAir<br /><br />"Trong tun khuyn mi t nay n 11/12, mi ngy s c mt s v 100.000 ng c tung ra", i din VietJetAir cho bit. Tuy nhin, hng t chi cung cp thng tin s c bao nhiu v 100.000 ng c bn trong mt tun k trn.<br /><br />Khch hng c th mua v v thanh ton bng th tn dng, bng tin mt ti cc phng v, i l... ca VietJetAir.<br /><br />VietJetAir s thc hin cc chuyn bay gia TP HCM v H Ni bt u t ngy 25/12.<br /><br />Kin Cng', '', 1, 6, 0, 38, '2012-02-02 13:04:20', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-02-02 13:04:20', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 30, '', '', 0, 37, 'robots=\nauthor='),
