(275, 'Cc chiu thc u c v my bay', 'cac-chieu-thc-u-c-ve-may-bay', '', '<div style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; width: 200px; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; float: left; position: relative; color: #000000; line-height: normal; text-align: left;"><img src="http://img-hcm.24hstatic.com:8008/upload/4-2011/images/2011-12-21/1324430386_ve-may-bay1.jpg" border="0" alt="Cc chiu thc u c v my bay" width="200" height="200" style="border: 1px initial initial;" />\r\n<div style="font-size: 11px; padding-top: 5px; padding-bottom: 5px; text-align: center; color: #666666;">Lng hnh khch trong dp tt tng cao nn c tnh trng i l u c gom v  tng doanh thu.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; float: left; width: 323px; color: #000000; line-height: normal; text-align: left;">\r\n<h1 style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: #1d8a0d; padding-bottom: 5px; margin: 0px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;">Cc Hng khng  c ch o cc hng hng khng kim tra cht vic bn v  cc i l, trnh tnh trng u c v.</span></h1>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify; padding-bottom: 5px;"></div>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify; padding-right: 10px;">ng V Huy Cng, Trng phng Vn ti - Cc Hng khng, cho hay Cc  c ch o cc hng hng khng lp k hoch kim tra cht vic bn v  cc i l, trnh tnh trng u c gom v  bn gi cao. Cc hng cng  thng nht s pht tht nng cc i l c vi phm.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; padding-bottom: 10px; color: #000000; line-height: normal; text-align: left;">\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;">\r\n<div>\r\n<p><br /><strong>Chng ngn  ht sch v</strong></p>\r\n<p>Anh L Minh Tun, ch mt i l bn v my bay cp 1, cho bit khc vi mi nm, thi im cui nm nay cc i l ang lm vo tnh trng ht v  bn. Cc chng ng di nh TP.HCM - H Ni ch cn rt t v, cn chng ngn th hu nh cc hng u  ht v. Nguyn nhn mt phn do khch hng t v trc tip qua mng, phn na l do hin nay Vietnam Airlines bn v thnh tng t vi s lng t, cc i l khng th nm c hng bn ra bao nhiu v.</p>\r\n<p>Anh Tun cho bit i l ca anh thc hin nghim tc vic bn v, tuy nhin vn c tnh trng mt s i l, c th l i l cp 1 vn u c gom v  tng doanh thu t tt. Cc i l ch yu gom v ca cc hng gi r Jetstar v Air Mekong. Ring Vietnam Airlines quy nh khng c i tn hnh khch t v cho nn cc i l khng gom v c. Trong trng hp i tn c th lch trnh, gi bay s thay i, ring vi v dp tt nu i tn s b di chuyn bay ra sau tt.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cc chiu thc u c</strong></p>\r\n<p>Anh L., ngi tng bn v my bay cho mt i l cp 1, tit l: Chiu thng dng nht m i l s dng u c gom v l lp danh sch khch hng o vi  h tn khng trng lp  t ch trc. Sau , i l s t mua v trn h thng. Khi khch hng vo h thng s thy v  bn ht, hi i l th s nhn c cu tr li i loi nh khng bit c cn khng hoc l ht v ri phi t ch. Khi y khch hng s  tn v s in thoi li khi no c v th i l s gi.</p>\r\n<p>Cc i l thng m loi v hng ph thng v loi v ny cho php khch hng c i chuyn, i hnh trnh v c hy vi iu kin phi chu mt t ph.</p>\r\n<p>V pha khch hng, mun mua c v phi chu ph 200.000-300.000 ng. Ph ny gi l ph book ch. Trong khi nm ht tt n, khch hng no m chng ng  iu kin ny  c v v qu n tt. Cng c khi i l ni ch cn v hng thng gia v i l hng dn khch phi tr gi cao hn  mua v hng ny. Th nhng khi ln my bay, thc t l khch ch ngi gh hng thng - anh L. bt m thm.</p>\r\n<p>Chiu th hai m cc i l thc hin  cnh tranh trong dp tt l rnh v trn mng. Vo nhng ngy cao im ca ma v tt, nhn vin ca i l thay nhau tc trc  theo di trn mng bn v. Nhng v m khch hng  ng k ch, sau 48 ting m khch khng thanh ton tin th mng t ng hy v. Sut v ny s c mng t ng y ra, i l no nhanh tay th chp c.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://img-hcm.24hstatic.com:8008/upload/4-2011/images/2011-12-21/1324430317-ve-may-bay2.jpg" border="0" alt="Cc chiu thc u c v my bay, Th trng - Tiu dng, ve may bay, gia ve, khuyen mai, hang khong, dau co, bao" style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial;" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span><em>Lng hnh khch trong dp tt tng cao nn c tnh trng i l u c gom v  tng doanh thu.</em></span></p>\r\n<p><strong>Hng chy ua  ht khch</strong></p>\r\n<p>B Nguyn Th Thanh Dung, ph trch PR ca VietJetAir, cho bit hng va kt thc chng trnh khuyn mi 2.000 v my bay ch vi gi 10.000 ng/lt. Khi chng trnh ny m ra, ch trong vng 5 ting  c hn 50.000 lt truy cp vo website. Hin ti hng ang khuyn mi gi r cho tuyn TP.HCM - H Ni v ngc li ch 900.000 ng/v, TP.HCM -  Nng ch 455.000 ng/v.</p>\r\n<p>B Dung cho bit thm, hnh khch trn mi chuyn bay ca VietJetAir s c phc v nh nhau, bt k mua v gi no. Khch hng nn ln k hoch i li sm, v c ch gi v ca hng l mua cng xa chuyn bay gi cng r. Ti y, cc chng trnh khuyn mi ln ca hng s ch yu p dng cho phng thc mua v qua mng v thanh ton ngay bng th Visa hoc Master Card. Cch lm ny s to cng bng cho mi khch hng, khuyn khch thanh ton khng dng tin mt v hn ch nn gom gi v.</p>\r\n<p>i din ca Air Mekong cho bit trong giai on cui nm 2011 v n tt Nhm Thn, lch bay ca hng tng thm 25% s chuyn bay, tng thm trn 25.000 ch trong giai on t ngy 23-12-2011 n 5-2-2012. Air Mekong tng 20.000 ch trn chuyn bay tuyn H Ni - TP.HCM v cc ng bay gia TP.HCM i Quy Nhn, Bun Ma Thut, Pleiku cng nh trn ng bay ni Vinh vi cc tnh Ty Nguyn.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '', 1, 6, 0, 38, '2012-02-04 04:59:42', 64, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-02-04 04:59:42', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 4, '', '', 0, 37, 'robots=\nauthor='),
